	(1,NULL,'Who we are','<p>The web site was established in January 2018. We are a specialist recruitment platform and helping job seekers to find jobs in Cambodia and employers to hire the best talented person for the job. We know that finding a good job or a good candidate is not easy and it can be one of the most important and biggest challenges companies or candidate face. Often the cost of hiring can be overwhelming while results are disappointing. We are here to provide a free of charge service to companies and job seeker. Companies can post their job on our web site with free cost and job seeker can post their CV on our web site with free cost too.</p>','2020-05-25 15:20:44','2020-05-26 11:43:25'),
	(3,NULL,'Job Submission','<p>You can submit us your job advertising docs or resume via job@paysjob.com or paysjob@gmail.com</p>','2020-05-26 11:55:34','2020-05-26 14:33:46'),
	(4,NULL,'Phone','<p>If you need our service, you can contact us via +(855-70) 900 928 / +(855-97) 807 73 73</p>','2020-05-26 11:58:44','2020-05-26 11:59:41'),
