; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">ពិនិត្យគាំទ្រ និងរាយការណ៍រាល់ការបំពេញបេសកកម្មការងារតាមសាខា</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">ការរៀបចំរបាយការណ៍ និងរាយការណ៍ជូនថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ&nbsp;&nbsp; ឬជានិស្សិតកំពង់សិក្សាឆ្នាំទី៤ ផ្នែកគណនេយ្យ គ្រប់គ្រងរដ្ឋបាល ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ&nbsp;&nbsp; មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់&nbsp; ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់&nbsp; សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office (Word &amp; Excel) Internet &amp; Email.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','07/15/2018',0,9,3,5,9,'English','2018-05-02 04:20:05','2020-06-01 11:00:21'),
	(43,15,'Deputy Director of Branch Audit Department','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist the VP &amp; Director of Branch Audit Department for preparing the annual internal audit strategy and operational plan.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Participant in designing and developing and/or updating the audit programs guides for branch audit staff to implements in order to meet the new established system and products &amp; services;</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Lead the branch audit staff to execute the auditing on the finance, deposit &amp; transfer transactions all HKL&rsquo;s offices as approved by the management and the audit board committee.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review and monitor the result of auditing includes efficiency and effectiveness of auditing through HKL&rsquo;s offices.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review a draft audit reports of branch audit staff and send to VP &amp; Director of Branch Audit Department for reviewing and issuing as a final audit report.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Providing necessary training to improve staff competency in doing their jobs and skills auditing.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Follow up branch audit report or other related reports and prepare the reports to make sure that, all previous auditing findings/issues have been fixed timely or on target date by the branch management and related departments.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks as assigned by management team.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Graduate in Banking &amp; Finance, Business Management and Economic, specializing in Accounting or other related fields and MBA is preferable.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">At least 2 years experiences in related to the field.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Excellent interpersonal and verbal communication skills, hard-working and high commitment.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Honest, reliable people, Dynamic and pleasant personality.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Excellence&nbsp; of written and spoken English.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Knowledge of computer (Word, Excel, E-mail, Internet &amp; PowerPoint).</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Be able to work under the pressure.</span><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,77,15,17,'1','07/15/2018',0,7,8,5,2,'English','2018-05-02 04:26:26','2020-05-31 19:12:38'),
	(44,15,'អ្នកបើកបរ និងជាជំនួយការរដ្ឋបាល','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">បើកបរជូនបុគ្គលិក ឬភ្ញៀវតាមការចាត់ចែងរបស់ថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">ធានាសុវត្ថិភាពលើការបើកបរ និងអ្នកដំណើរ</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">ថែរក្សាភាពគង់វង្ស និងគុណភាពរថយន្ត</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">រៀបចំយាន្តជំនិះតាមសំណើ</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">រៀបចំនិងសម្របសម្រួលកិច្ចការរដ្ឋបាលផ្សេងៗទៀតតាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់រដ្ឋបាលសាខា ឬនាយកសាខា</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">បំព