	(58,15,'Team Leader of Environmental and Social (01 Post)','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Monitor and verify borrowers&rsquo; environmental and social impact assessment and high E&amp;S risk borrowers.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Control and verify Monthly Social and Environmental Performance Report for investors and donor.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Monitory and verify Monthly Financial Literacy Performance Report.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Verify and analyze the Progress out of Poverty Index (PPI).</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist on implement and reinforced the Client Protection Principles.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Facilitate all social activities and programs. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned by management.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bachelor degree of Management, Banking and Finance, Economics, or other related field, English degree is preferable.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good understanding and knowledge of loan assessment process in advance. </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Self-motivation and able to manage own workload.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Be flexible with working hours.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Computer literacy in MS Office includes Word, Excel, Power Point, Internet and Email.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good command of English is preferable.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Be able to travel to province.</span><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,70,15,17,'1','05/23/2018',0,8,7,5,1,'English','2018-05-02 08:09:32','2020-05-30 13:19:26'),
	(59,15,'Deputy Director of Financial & Planning Department (01 post.)','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">In lead of financial planning &amp; analysis to continually increase quality &amp; productivity.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Facilitate budgeting process for all offices &amp; business functions to come up with reliable final version for approval and execution.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Design, develop, and implement budgeting module and financial analysis and regular update to support/drive the business operation.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure all financial reports for management, board and Krungsri are prepare timely and correctly.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work and introduce balanced scorecard/dashboard to improve strategic initiative.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Help to identify and enact cost efficiencies and process improvement opportunities throughout the Company and versus peers.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist the Director in evaluation and advice to relevant management or regional directors on areas of improvements, efficiencies, productivity and goals.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist the Director in preparation of financial planning &amp; analysis to continually increase quality &amp; productivity.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist in rolling forecast to improve reliability on financial planning and operations.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist in preparation of bench-marking (In-Ex) to increase productivity &amp; efficiencies.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist in preparation of cost accounting by root causes analyses &amp; initiative cost reductions.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bachelor degree in finance / accounting / management. MBA or pursuing CPA is a plus.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">English language: Speaking and Writing at very good level.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">At least 4 years of experience in banking / financial institutions.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Extensive experience on financial control/ performance management/ budget &amp; planning.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Competency on Business Administration, leadership, management and ability to multi-tasks.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good communication skill and able to travel locally and internal.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Computer skills required.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,17,'1','05/23/2018',0,11,8,5,5,'English','2018-05-02 08:14:31','2020-05-30 13:10:45'),
	(60,15,'Team Leader of Business Development (02 post)','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Respect and follow the tasks that assigned by direct supervisor.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Responsible for developing the new business pipeline or project.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform analytical preparation for opportunities for potential growth and income.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Generate new contacts and sales leads for the company.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Facilitate the definition of project scope, goals and deliverable.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Write specification proposals, under project process, present project progress problems and solutions. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Coordinate with technical team and system for process project.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop comprehensive knowledge about the business and its development practices, its marketing activities, prospective clients, and the trends for the industry and find identify new opportunities for business.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bachelor degree in the field of Management, Marketing, Finance &amp; Banking, Economics and other related skill.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Strong networking, communication skills, negotiating and reconciliation skills.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Excellent in English and Khmer verbal.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Work experience in business development and sale project for 1 year in finance and banking.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good computer Skill as Ms. Work, Excel and Power point.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Strong customer service skills and timely management.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Proven ability to work under pressure.</span><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,43,15,17,'2','05/19/2018',0,8,7,5,2,'English','2018-05-02 08:18:56','2020-05-28 16:17:53'),
	(61,15,'Head Unit of Business Development (01 post)','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Monitor and lead member to find new business pipeline or project.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Explain to potential customers about the various benefits offered products or services and following to close the business deals.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop business proposals for existing, new customers and obey project timeline on time.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Responsible for conversant with all HKL&rsquo;s product and services especially bill payment and liquidity management.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Product in order to give potential and existing customers accurate information in a professional and timely manner.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop comprehensive knowledge about the business and its development practices, its marketing activities,</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prospective clients and the trends for the industry and find identify new opportunities for business.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good and cooperate with teamwork, with strong commitment.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bachelor degree in the field of Management, Marketing, Finance &amp; Banking, Economics and other related skill.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Strong networking, communication skills, negotiating and reconciliation skills.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Excellent in English and Khmer verbal.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Work experience in business development and sale project for 1 year in finance and banking.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good computer Skill as Ms. Work, Excel and Power point.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Strong customer service skills and timely management.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Proven ability to work under pressure.</span><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,43,15,17,'1','05/19/2018',0,8,7,5,2,'English','2018-05-02 08:26:41','2020-06-01 13:38:59'),
	(62,14,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ៥៨នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>Promote and sell credit and saving products to potential clients</li>\r\n<li>Prepare loan application of clients</li>\r\n<li>Monitor and control the loan payment and re-investigate clients after loan disbursement</li>\r\n<li>Report to credit team leader or credit manager</li>\r\n<li>Manage loan/ OD contract</li>\r\n<li>Implement the credit policies</li>\r\n<li>Participate in arranging the credit strategic plan</li>\r\n<li>Evaluate and analyze customers</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of the customer characteristic</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of real estate evaluation and analysis</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of Cambodian law</li>\r\n<li>Be effective sale forces</li>\r\n<li>Other tasks assigned by management</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Male, age range from 20-35 years old</li>\r\n<li>Associated or Bachelor Degree in accounting, finance &amp; banking, management, economics or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Working experience 1 year up.</li>\r\n<li>Good written and verbal communication skill in both Khmer and English.</li>\r\n<li>Strong interpersonal and relationship building skills.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy (Microsoft Office: Word, Excel&hellip;etc.).</li>\r\n<li>Strong organizational and interpersonal communication skill.</li>\r\n<li>Willing to work at the fields.</li>\r\n<li>Be honest, initiative, hard-working and committed.</li>\r\n<li>Must be full of energy, time flexible.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'58','05/30/2018',1,7,3,5,2,'English','2018-05-04 04:23:48','2020-05-30 07:01:53'),
	(63,15,'មន្រ្តីផ្នែកលក់ (Retail Sale Officer) - ១៧នាក់','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333;\">ចូលរួមក្នុងយុទ្ធនាការ ផ្សព្វផ្សាយផ្សេងៗទាក់ទងនឹង ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333;\">ដោះស្រាយបាននូវរាល់បញ្ហាដែលនឹងអាចកើតមានឡើង ចំពោះប្រតិបត្តិការ ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333;\">រៀបចំ និងគ្រប់គ្រងរាល់ឯកសារព័ត៌មានទំនាក់ទំនង ជាមួយអតិថិជន​ ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333;\">រាយការណ៍ពីបាតុភាព និងផលប៉ះពាល់ដល់ ផលិតផល និងសេវាកម្មទាំងឡាយ មកគណៈគ្រប់គ្រងឱ្យបានទាន់ពេល​ច្បាស់លាស់គ្រប់គ្រាន់ និងត្រឹមត្រូវ​​ ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333;\">រៀបចំបាយការណ៍តាមការចាត់ចែងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រ</span><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: #333333; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">ង​ ។</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">ចុះជួបទំនាក់ទំនងអតិថិជន និងសាធារណជនដោយផ្ទាល់និងពន្យល់អំពី</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្