	(172,15,'Manager of Public Relation - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop the PR plan and strategic of HKL in accordance with company vision, mission and strategy.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Identify the tactic in order to bring HKL&rsquo;s brand into public which can ensure the consistency &amp; positive image appears in all media types.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Build good relationship with media partners broadcasting HKL &amp; ensure its positive brand image in all the time.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Promote all product/services of HKL to ensure that they are recognized &amp; understand by external audience.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop and manage policy, framework and process for both internal &amp; external communication, internal communication activities plan, and channel &amp; execute them across all the functions within HKL.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Initiate to develop and implement activities in order to strengthen relationship and HKL&rsquo;s core value among HKL employee.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Manage the HKL communication message and new pipelines, and then follow the feedback.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work as copy write copy of HKL&rsquo;s message, ads, brochures, TV spots, radio, and other forms of advertising.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Manage to support PR activities in relate with photography and video record for using in press release or other communication channel.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Support for internal &amp; external activities and other tasks assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bachelor degree in marketing, Journalism or related majors in business administration</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Understanding of banking and microfinance sector, especially bank/MFI product and service</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">At least 2 years experiences in marketing, journalism or event organizing</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Having solid project management skills</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good public speaking and presentation skills</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">High proficiency in writing, speaking, reading and listening English</span><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,17,'1','06/18/2018',1,14,9,5,4,'English','2018-06-01 05:36:59','2020-05-31 16:38:52'),
	(173,15,'Manager of Branding - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop brand guidelines, brand vision and value proposition for short and long term.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Maintain and enhance brand policies and procedure such as Corporate Identity by ensuring all stakeholders adopt and use it correctly.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Actively promote HKL brand by ensuring all projects/programs meet corporate brand standards.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Manage all the activities stipulated in the brand plan to ensure that brand objectives are achieved.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Manage and track material effectiveness in order to modify and improve promotion development.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Quality checks marketing material at all stages of development and production process, applies changes where required, and provides final approval to ensure quality, finished material being produced.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work closely with research team for competitor and customer insights analysis, brand preference and brand consideration survey.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work with marketing and communication team for plan and execution of all communications and media actions as well as create promotional campaign.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bachelor degree in Business Administration, Marketing, or other related field, master degree is preferable.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">At least 2 years working experiences specializing in marketing and branding.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Strong conceptualization and analytical skills and capacity to pro-actively plan and well-implementation.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Well understand about financial institution environment, experience with bank is preferable.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good interpersonal communication, presentation skill, team work, result-oriented.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Excellent skill in MS Office includes Word, Excel, and Power Point.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">High proficiency in writing, speaking, reading and listening English</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,17,'1','06/17/2018',1,8,9,5,4,'English','2018-06-01 05:39:53','2020-05-31 18:38:37'),
	(174,16,'ICT Service Officer - 06 posts','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Assign CIT service officers for cash in transit to ATMs, NBC, ABA branches and other banks;</li>\r\n<li>Implementation of proper communication with cash department for amount of cash and numbers of trips for daily CIT operation;</li>\r\n<li>Implementation of checking and maintenance CIT card;</li>\r\n<li>Inspection of CIT service equipment of CIT service officer beofre leaving for CIT trip;</li>\r\n<li>Monitoring and receiving CIT trip status from CIT service officers via radio communication</li>\r\n<li>Make report of daily CIT trips into CITService Log book;</li>\r\n<li>Conducting of screening of pamanent CIT service officers;</li>\r\n<li>Assign CIT service officer to escort refinancing team as per instruction from head of security or CIT supervisor;</li>\r\n<li>Checking status of escorting refinancing team from CIT service officers via radio communication;</li>\r\n<li>Observation and investigation of CIT service officers who suspected breach of CIT policy;</li>\r\n<li>Observation and collecting information of ABA staff who breach code of conduct, bank policies and who suspected commited fraud;</li>\r\n<li>Assist CIT service supervisor to do other tasks.</li>\r\n<li>Arrangement of schedule and assign CIT service officers to safeguard ABA head offices on working hours, weekend, day off and public holidays;;</li>\r\n<li>Arrangement of schedule and assign CIT service officers to spot check security guards of security agencies who safeguard for ABA branches in PP;</li>\r\n<li>Assign CIT service officers to protect ABA branches in PP as per instruction from head of security.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree.</li>\r\n<li>CIT skill.</li>\r\n<li>Security skill.</li>\r\n<li>Basic bodyguard skill.</li>\r\n<li>Basic investigation skill.</li>\r\n<li>Computer (Microsoft word and Excel).</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 years with security field and CIT tasks.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,7,17,'6','07/15/2018',1,7,3,5,9,'English','2018-06-02 02:56:34','2020-05-28 06:11:53'),
	(175,15,'Team Leader of Fraud Management - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Coordinate and planning organizing leading and controlling the staff under supervisor to proactively in identify possible fraud incidents that are relevant to HKL.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist risk owner on how to manage fraud in accordance with fraud management policies.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Involve with the relevant business unit to conduct the fraud risk assessment on new business initiative/service/policy procedure and product development&hellip;etc.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Maintain the recording mechanism of the fraud register, fraud incident report register and database as well as the fraud control plan.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist the director of produce the dashboard report and other monthly monitoring report as required.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bachelor degree of Management, Banking and Finance, Economics, or other related field, English degree is preferable.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Self-motivation and able to manage own workload.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">At least 1 year experience in field fraud management, risk management, audit compliance.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Be flexible with working hours.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Computer literacy in MS Office includes Word, Excel, Power Point, Internet and Email.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-con