	(180,15,'Manager of Independent Risk Champion - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure the Independent Risk Champion (IRC) agenda or activities are run smoothly within business of HKL.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Support to the stakeholder in delivering and understanding the line of defense practice in managing the risks.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure all branches of HKL business are aware off the IRC function and participate the implementation it as per the business as usual. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Coordinate to planning or organizing and controlling the staff under supervision to proactively.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop the training program related to specific skill in risk management for supporting the IRC training program. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Maintain the recording mechanism of the quantitative and qualitative performance for staff. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform additional tasks and any duties as required by direct supervisor or management.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Bachelor degree of Management, Banking and Finance, Economics, or other related field, English degree is preferable.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">At least 3 year experience on operational risks and fraud risk management.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good understanding and knowledge of loan assessment process in advance. </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Computer literacy in MS Office includes Word, Excel, Power Point, Internet and Email.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Good command of English is preferable.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Sound risk management and analytical skill</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Understanding of financial or banking business operation.</span><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong><br /></strong></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','06/15/2018',1,7,9,5,5,'English','2018-06-02 03:18:10','2020-05-28 00:01:55'),
