	(224,19,'Branch Credit Admin Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Review Loan Document from Credit Officer before submit to Branch Manager and checking CBC.</li>\r\n<li>Check Client Credit History in CBC by follow the policy and procedure.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare and review loan document before submit Credit Committee.</li>\r\n<li>Review and re-check Loan Agreement, Hypothec Agreement, legal document, and Collateral/Security Documents before giving to customer to process with authority, disbursement, and filing.</li>\r\n<li>Control and monitor Credit Committee Loan minute approving which send by Senior SME Lending Support at Head Office.</li>\r\n<li>Help Branch Manager to share Memo, guideline, and follow up with users to ensure that they are compliance.</li>\r\n<li>Maintain customer information confidentiality.</li>\r\n<li>Record and track client&rsquo;s Collateral information into core banking system.</li>\r\n<li>Safe keeping all client&rsquo;s documents such as Client Information, Loan Document, and Collateral/Security Document by following policy and procedure.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate related works with Credit Admin Office at Head Office.</li>\r\n<li>Others task as assign by supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in the field of banking and finance, accounting, economic, law or other equivalent.</li>\r\n<li>At least 1-year experience in Microfinance/Bank.</li>\r\n<li>Have strong numeric and administrative skill.</li>\r\n<li>Negotiation and internal relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Sound written and verbal English communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>Advanced Computer Skills (Ms. Word, Excel, and Power Point).</li>\r\n<li>Ability on problem solving and good communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>Good behavior committed and disciplined.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,7,23,'1','06/22/2018',1,6,3,5,11,'English','2018-06-15 09:21:05','2020-06-01 01:37:39'),
	(225,20,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ១០នាក់','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 14.95px;\"><span lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 16.1px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">ការផ្សព្វផ្សាយពីផលិតផលរបស់ស្ថាប័ន&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 16.1px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">កំណត់នូវអតិថិជនសក្តានុពលនៅក្នុងតំបន់គោលដៅ ។</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 14.95px;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 16.1px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">កំណត់យុទ្ធសាស្រ្តលក់ និងថែរក្សាអតិថិជន និងស្រាវជ្រាវទីផ្សារ គូរប្រកួតប្រជែង ។</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 14.95px;\"><span lang=\"C