	(265,15,'Manager of Business Loan - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Lead and initiative idea to conduct or analyze the market demand with research team, with development the Business Loan to response to market demand.</li>\r\n<li>Lead in enhancing or revising the existing products to response the market changes and keep these products being competitive and attractive in the market.</li>\r\n<li>Review product performance to identify product&rsquo;s SWOT, and take appropriate reflection to ensure the effectiveness and control of product&rsquo;s performance.</li>\r\n<li>Regular market survey and observation to identify the potential business initiatives in supporting business growth.</li>\r\n<li>Lead, coach, and support subordinates to achieve KPI/target to meet the HKL strategic goals.</li>\r\n<li>Work with relevant departments or cross functional teams to facilitate Business Loan project to ensure, it goes well and smoothly.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in the field of Management, Marketing, Finance &amp; Banking, Economics and other related skill.</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 year experiences in credit product development a plus.</li>\r\n<li>Equip with good understanding and knowledge of microfinance and banking products, especially credit products and/or services.</li>\r\n<li>Be able to coordinate with cross functional team to ensure high productivity</li>\r\n<li>Good computer Skill as Ms. Work, Excel and Power point.</li>\r\n<li>Excellent in English and Khmer verbal.</li>\r\n<li>Committed to timeline and handling pressure.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,17,'1','07/01/2018',1,4,9,5,2,'English','2018-07-01 03:33:35','2020-05-31 12:32:58'),
	(266,15,'Manager of Non credit Product Development for Deposit (01 post.)','<ul>\r\n<li>Manage all detail process of project development including policy, procedure or manual to ensure proper control over transaction flow &amp; other processing model.</li>\r\n<li>Collaborate with marketing team in planning, development and implementation of creative and cost-effective marketing activities to drive success of new product launch.</li>\r\n<li>Manage product launch activities during pilot testing period to ensure performance of the new product.</li>\r\n<li>Seasonal visit branch offices to observe the practice &amp; incorporate their comments/challenges in order to enhance the product policy implementation.</li>\r\n<li>Work closely with distribution division and insurance partners to develop the sale strategies and implement to the market.</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring that non-credit product sale volumes and fee income are achieving accordance with predetermined volumes.</li>\r\n<li>Regularly conduct market research and analysis to understand implications and identify new opportunities in line with institute\'s strategies and expansion plans.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the product knowledge is understood by sale-force team.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other tasks assigned by supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor or Master Degree in banking/finance or business management, or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least 03 year experience in project or business development in financial industry.</li>\r\n<li>Extensive knowledge in insurance, strong analytical, quantitative, problem solving.</li>\r\n<li>Be a communication, presentation, relationship management, project management skill.</li>\r\n<li>Be proficient in English both speaking and writing.</li>\r\n<li>Be Innovative, dynamic and confident.</li>\r\n<li>Be well time management.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,17,'1','07/14/2018',1,4,9,5,4,'English','2018-07-01 03:36:39','2020-05-31 14:35:29'),
	(267,15,'Manager Non of Product Development for Insurance - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Delivery the insurance products line accordance with the company&rsquo;s strategy within the estimate timeframe.</li>\r\n<li>Develop the sale strategies and implement to the market.</li>\r\n<li>Regularly conduct market research and analysis to understand implications and identify new opportunities in line with institute\'s strategies and expansion plans.</li>\r\n<li>Manage and monitor insurance team performance via good team work, motivation and coaching for high productivity and critical understanding.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure end-to-end management of products and campaigns across channels.</li>\r\n<li>Co-ordinate with key internal and external stakeholder groups, including existing clients to continuously growing of insurance business.</li>\r\n<li>Deliver product governance and control such as partner\'s due diligence, product program review, business agreements, and service level agreements.</li>\r\n<li>Analyzes cost &amp; benefit of insurance products, marketing or sale activities</li>\r\n<li>Prepares the budget plan projections for insurance product launch, sale or marketing campaign.</li>\r\n<li>Perform others tasks assigned by supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor or Master Degree in banking/finance or business management, or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least 03 year experience in consumer banking, insurance or financial services industry.</li>\r\n<li>Prior insurance experience preferred.</li>\r\n<li>Extensive knowledge in insurance, strong analytical, quantitative, problem solving,</li>\r\n<li>Be a communication, presentation, relationship management, project management skill.</li>\r\n<li>Be proficient in English both speaking and writing.</li>\r\n<li>Be Innovative, dynamic and confident.</li>\r\n<li>Be well time management.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,17,'1','07/14/2018',1,4,9,5,4,'English','2018-07-01 03:40:07','2020-06-01 17:18:07'),
