	(322,15,'Head Unit of Audit Analysis and Reporting - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Collect and analyze data before conducting pre-audit.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Perform pre-audit analysis and pre-audit checklist.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Prepare risk control matrix and audit program guide including audit working papers.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Review and evaluate adequacy and effectiveness of&nbsp; internal control&nbsp; policies &amp; procedures and workflow process of company/business function.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Participate in conducting the pre-audit and audit field work as assigned by the supervisors. </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Review supporting documents and consolidate the draft audit report, and submit to manager.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Bachelor degree in accounting or equivalent degree is required of accounting, Audit, or Finance qualification.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">At least 2 years working experiences in related field.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Knowledge of financial or business analysis, internal control system, organizational structure, works flow