	(324,15,'Core Banking & Solution Officer for Helpdesk Support - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Manage on core banking products configuration supports, and Follow Technical SLA on ticket issue assignment from all offices and departments.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Prepare as answer and question from all department and office in Helpdesk Issue Solution System.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Support, Feedback and Facilitate users on their daily functioning and operation of products, functions and business applications.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Prepare report to follow up result and feedback with all users on pending ticket issues.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Analyze and investigate, prioritize and Escalate issues to respective technical support team.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Communicate, answer and advice on appropriate actions to users as primary solution.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Follow up supporting result and feedback to respective support helpdesk and business team with all users at Head Office and branches.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Assist in contact off-shore team support and document, update and test products.</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">Perform other task assigned by management.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-co