	(325,15,'Deputy Director of Credit and Market Risk Management - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist Credit and Market Risk Management to achieve the annual work plans, Department&rsquo;s objectives and HKL&rsquo;s goals.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform Credit portfolio management and portfolio quality analysis.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Provide Analysis and risk recommendations.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Deliver high quality data-driven analyses.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Identify and respond to analytics or data trends opportunities.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Manage Excute project indepently from end-to- end.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Overhaul and develop reqular reports.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop forecasting models to enhance.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop staistical credit risk models and credit score card.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Analyze on the credit concentration risk, propose and review credit limit exposure.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Performance other tasks as assigned by management.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Master&rsquo;s Degree with background of financial banking, Finance, Accounting, Economics, Statistic, Mathematics, Computer Science.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work experience in different areas of bank and financial institution at least 5 years, including 3 year experience risk management.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good understanding of the bank and Financial institution lending polic