	(337,15,'Team Leader of HR for Recruitment - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Play as a part of HR management team to research and develop some of policies and procedures of HR department.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prepare and oversee the recruitment plan to make sure all vacant positions are filled within agreed time frame.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prepare and oversee the selection process since the recruitment process until successful result.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Manage and maintain the recruitment database properly and effectively.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">To play a part of recruitment committee to prepare the recruitment process and select the right candidate to run the job effectively.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other duties as required by direct supervisor.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree is required (preferably in HR).</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Human Resource Services Experience 1-2 years. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">General knowledge of various employment laws.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Excellent interpersonal and coaching skills.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Honest, Creative and Healthy. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">English Upper level of writing, speaking and listening skill.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Computer literate in MS Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Internet &amp; E-mail.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good moral and communication.</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Location</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"bodytext\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Head Office, Phnom Penh</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','08/15/2018',1,7,9,5,15,'English','2018-08-08 09:41:37','2020-05-31 23:16:06'),
	(338,15,'Branch Effectiveness Officer for Credit Management - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prepare the Daily performing monitoring Report, Monthly Reports accuracy and timely.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure and manage all kinds of credit reports in credit management unit and be capable to work substitutable for others in parallel positions as well.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Make and Verify the Monthly Report on costs of the branch CBC usage checked credit bureau Cambodia service system.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work closely with CBS department to build the all credit reports in branch effectiveness&nbsp; department.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Handle all tasks as required and assigned by direct supervisors and management team.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other task assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in business administration or related field.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good understanding and knowledge of microfinance and banking sector.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good interpersonal communication, team work and result-oriented.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Computer literacy in MS Office, Word, Excel, Internet and Email.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good command in English both writing and speaking.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good communication.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Commitment, and Honestly.</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Location</strong></h3>\r\n<p class=\"bodytext\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Head Office, Phnom Penh</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','08/20/2018',1,7,3,5,1,'English','2018-08-08 09:44:53','2020-06-01 06:30:21'),
	(339,15,'Business Development Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Maintain new and existing client that have used payroll with HKL and gross sell.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Responsible for conversant with all HKL&rsquo;s product and services as, payroll, bill payment and liquidity management product.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Solve and facilitate all problems that occurred with payroll.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Monitor and process upload payroll on time.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Manage material and work administrative task for department.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in the field of Management, Marketing, Finance &amp; Banking, Economics and other related skill</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Strong networking, communication skills, negotiating and reconciliation skills.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Understand very well of payroll process, project process and solve problem.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Excellent in English and Khmer verbal.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work experience for business development and sale project in finance and banking.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good computer Skill as Ms. Work, Excel and Power point, and Email.<span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong></strong></span></span></span></span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; 