	(368,15,'Branch Effectiveness Officer for Credit Management​ - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prepare the Daily performing monitoring Report, Monthly Reports accuracy and timely.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure and manage all kinds of credit reports in credit management unit and be capable to work substitutable for others in parallel positions as well.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Make and Verify the Monthly Report on costs of the branch CBC usage checked credit bureau Cambodia service system.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work closely with CBS department to build the all credit reports in branch effectiveness&nbsp; department.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Handle all tasks as required and assigned by direct supervisors and management team.&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other task assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in business administration or related field.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good understanding and knowledge of microfinance and banking sector.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good interpersonal communication, team work and result-oriented.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Computer literacy in MS Offic, Word, Excel, Internet and Email.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good command in English both writing and speaking.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good communication.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Commitment, and Honestly.</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; c