	(371,15,'Credit Risk Monitoring and Report Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Produce all credit risk management reports.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform credit portfolio management and recommend on high and low risk segment.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Identify, assess, and measure credit risk and suggest control to mitigate risk.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform credit risk monitoring.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform independent credit review to branches.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned management.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Graduate in bachelor of Mathematics, Economics, Finance and Banking, Accounting, Information Technology, Statistics.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good in computer skill on Excel, advance excel and VBA is an advantage.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Experience in loan assessment or credit affairs is preferable</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good command of English.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Strong analytical skills, and Active and Dynamic.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Willing to travel to province.</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #333333; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">Head Office (Phnom Penh)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','09/15/2018',1,6,3,5,9,'English','2018-08-23 09:57:42','2020-06-01 08:16:05'),
	(372,15,'Regulatory Compliance Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Actively discuss on new/existing regulations among compliance team.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Monitor of compliance checklist with business department.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Assist on compliance assessment on new product/service development.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review and make recommendation on Non-Compliance concern to team.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Coordinate with other related departments of HKL&rsquo;s corresponding.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Communicate to relevant employee/functional department on new regulations.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review of policies/procedures from functional department aim avoiding conflict of interest, and compliance to group and local requirement.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Monitor the lender covenant, and raise of non-compliance team leader.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned by management.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in business administration/law or related studies.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">At least one year experience with banking and FI operation.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Understanding principle of banking and FI products.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Have a good knowledge of banking regulatory requirement and advocate to business team from compliance perspective, </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Excellent verbal, presentation and written communication.</spa