	(375,15,'Field Collection and Recovery Officer - 03 posts','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Collect delinquent and WO based on target set by management.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Analysze and prepare facility restructuring for approval.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Coordinate with bad debt collector or relevant staffs in solving problem with borrowers.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Visit and collect debt at any offices based on Situation.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Support litigation process with effective and timely manner.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Process to write off based on the policy and procedure.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Negotiate and solve the problem with client based on collection code of conduct.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform&nbsp; other tasks as assigned by supervisor</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in the field of Management, Marketing, Finance &amp; Banking, Economics and other related skill.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Useful experience as credit officer, BDC or relevant positions.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Strong networking, communication, negotiation, reconciliation skills, and organization.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Knowledge of relevant legal requirements.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good computer Skill as Ms. Work, Excel and Power point.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good in English and Khmer verbal.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left w100 size-content size1