	(376,15,'Accounting Transaction Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Check all sufficient supporting documents properly before posting into system.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prepare JV with sufficient supporting documents.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Post daily transactions occur into system in timely manner with the correct GL code.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Post monthly transactions completely and properly.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Post monthly end closing entries properly and in timely manneanr.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform daily physical cash count in till to confirm the accuracy of its balance.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Maintain all supporting documents properly and in orderly manner</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Other tasks assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in Accounting, Finance and banking, Economics, or other related fields.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good skill in MS Office includes Word, Excel and PowerPoint.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Friendly, Flexible and can work under pressure.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Good command of English is preferred</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; color: #333333; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; l