	(380,15,'Manager of Business Loan - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Lead and initiative idea to conduct or analyze the market demand with research team, with development the Business Loan to response to market demand.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Lead in enhancing or revising the existing products to response the market changes and keep these products being competitive and attractive in the market.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review product performance to identify product&rsquo;s SWOT, and take appropriate reflection to ensure the effectiveness and control of product&rsquo;s performance. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Regular market survey and observation to identify the potential business initiatives in supporting business growth.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Lead, coach, and support subordinates to achieve KPI/target to meet the HKL strategic goals.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Work with relevant departments or cross functional teams to facilitate.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in the field of Management, Marketing, Finance &amp; Banking, Economics and other related skill.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">At least 2 year experiences in credit product development a plus.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Equip with good understanding and knowledge of microfinance and banking products, especially credit products and/or services.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Be able to coordinate with cross functional team to ensure high productivity</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\