	(388,28,'Quality Control (Vehicle)','<p><span style=\"color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; text-align: justify;\">Make sure the quality of repair the condition of the vehicle, assist to the service adviser for receiving the customer and carried our interactive inspection, assist to the technician for the quality of repair and fix it first time, supporting promotional activities, monitoring inventory, complying with safety and environment programs and practices, and any other duties as assigned.</span></p>','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; line-height: 19.5px; width: 902.391px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;\">Bachelor Degree or higher in Engineering or related field.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;\">Education, training and/or certifications should clearly demonstrate the possession of the knowledge and skills stated above.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;\">High school preferred.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;\">Some college or automotive/vocational training preferred.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,83,15,17,'1','09/28/2018',1,12,8,5,14,'English','2018-08-29 06:46:06','2020-06-01 14:27:00'),
	(389,28,'Service Adviser','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; line-height: 19.5px; width: 902.391px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Follow up with customers to ensure they are satisfied with service.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Promote cooperation and teamwork among technicians and support staff.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Assist other Service Advisors when needed.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Check customer\'s service history, schedule appointments, enter repair order information and manage information.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Follow up to resolve and communicate resolution of customer concerns to local market Ford Customer Satisfaction organization.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Verify time ticket information.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origi