	(390,28,'Lending Officer','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; list-style-position: inside; list-style-type: square; line-height: 19.5px; width: 902.391px; color: #424242; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Update weekly report about cash flow forecast, prospect, and influencer, and monthly planning.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Competitors survey every 3 months on each products (Car, Tractor, HED, Forklifit) and financial institutions and send report to Head of Credit Sales.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Be willing to follow and adapt your supervisor&rsquo;s advice/teaching/request.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Send aged receivable report to Senior Collection Office every Friday afternoon.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Be willing to help and support team when they are busy or on leave.</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">Teach, support, and train the sales of dealer (Ford, HED, JD, JLR, SP&hellip;) about financing services.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 6px 0px 10px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; backgr