	(412,15,'Head Unit of Audit Analysis and Reporting - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Collect and analyze data before conducting pre-audit.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform pre-audit analysis and pre-audit checklist.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Prepare risk control matrix and audit program guide including audit working papers.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review and evaluate adequacy and effectiveness of&nbsp; internal control&nbsp; policies &amp; procedures and workflow process of company/business function.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Participate in conducting the pre-audit and audit field work as assigned by the supervisors. </span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review supporting documents and consolidate the draft audit report, and submit to manager.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Bachelor degree in accounting or equivalent degree is required of accounting, Audit, or Finance qualification.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">At least 2 years working experiences in related field.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Knowledge of financial or business analysis, internal control system, organizational structure, works flow and operating procedures.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Demonstrate high level of ethical commitments and trustworthiness.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Advance written and verbal skills with excellent English.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Computer literate in MS Office (Word, MS Excel, Power Point, etc.)</span></l