	(447,23,'Branch Manager (Urgent) - 03 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Coordinate to set up any necessary contingent plan such as growth/expansion, pilot/rollout of ABP, Mobile Banking, new product, process, staff rearrangement, and delinquency management plans;</li>\r\n<li>Regularly conduct market saturation reviews, competition analysis, and update village profile (prospective target clients identification in each village using household list by village, in urban area, and business center) for necessary expansion and acquisition;</li>\r\n<li>Perform strict loan assessment and loan quality check to ensure high loan quality. In the event of many loan requests, proper assignment for DBM, Specialized CSO (SCSO), or trusted CSO are required;</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that loan, saving, and other required business transactions are properly entered into iPad and/or system;</li>\r\n<li>Ensure proper loan delinquency management implementation, such as effective follow up, timely issuing notification &amp; demand letters to delinquent clients, appropriate logbook completion and posting into the system, and specific action plan for loan recovery of BO;Oversee effective liquidity management at the BO, including providing timely support to authorize and/or approve the day end closing report requested by the Branch Teller/Supervisor;</li>\r\n<li>Ensure proper branch financial management;</li>\r\n<li>Ensure all systems, policies and procedures are abided by and implemented in the branch with proper monitoring and control tools;</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the implementation of audits, Risk and Quality Assurance Officers, NBC, and raters recommendations/suggestions to improve overall branch performances;</li>\r\n<li>Effectively implement fraud prevention guidelines, like reviewing task rotation report and conducting observation/surprise visits to loan collection and loan disbursement, and meeting with CBMCs/focal persons, clients, and other stakeholders for feedback collection and other verification;</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the quality of information and completeness of loan and saving document prepared by staff under supervision (loan documents, PPI, reports, passbook, vouchers, official receipt, saving contract, saver ID, thumbprint/signature, etc.);</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree in Management, Economic, Finance &amp; Banking, Accounting, Marketing or other equivalences;</li>\r\n<li>Minimum 2 years experience in microfinance operations and management &amp; staff supervisory;</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of Cambodian microfinance sector</li>\r\n<li>Good working knowledge of English and computer skills especially on MS Word, Excel, and PowerPoint;</li>\r\n<li>Good interpersonal, communication, staff supervision, training and management skills;</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work under pressure and be highly self-motivated.</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrate high level of ethical commitment and trustworthiness.</li>\r\n<li>Must be willing to work and live in the district.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Location</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>BorsethDistrict (Kampong Speu)</li>\r\n<li>KampotProvincial Town</li>\r\n<li>DambeDistrict (TboungKhmum)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,27,'3','10/30/2018',1,14,6,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-10-27 15:38:52','2020-05-31 03:11:56'),
	(448,23,'Information Security Manager - 01 post','<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Implement firewall solutions to properly secure WB Finance data and provide consultation on all new firewall implementations, firewall configuration changes, and IT projects requiring security operational support;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Actively protect WB Finance company IT Assets and infrastructure from external or internal threats and ensure that the company complies with statutory and regulatory requirements regarding information access, security and privacy;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Assist the end-user, other IT professionals, and external customers in requesting security variances and implementation of subsequent configuration change requests;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Monitor systems for any anomalies, suspicious activity then provide proper updating, and provide patching quickly if notified from security solution provider or make recommendations for resolution;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Maintains system documentation and configuration data from regulatory and audit purpose;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Coach and guide Service Desk and Desk Side Support technicians in their incident response, directing incident first responder actions, and appropriately escalating issues;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Check and collect backup log to ensure the backup job has been done and report to relevant staffs to take an immediate action in case of failure;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Enforce the proper implementation of IT Security in order to comply with IT Security policy and procedure.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Bachelor degree in Information Technology and Computer science preferably in Information Security Management;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">At least 4 years experiences of recent professional experiences in Information Security and Compliance;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Current experience with Network Infrastructure secured design and management;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Knowledge and implementation of IDS/IPS and Syslog and operation of monitoring tools: Cacti, Nagios, SolarWind;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Knowledge of information security principles, including risk assessment and management, threat and vulnerability management, incident response and identity and access management;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Knowledge and experience in penetration testing and ISO 27001 standard and enforcement;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Experience developing, documenting and maintaining security procedures;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Experience and knowledge in Cyber Security, latest thread and attack vectors and mitigation plan;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Experience in enforcing policy, procedure of IT across organization as well as delivery information security awareness across organization;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">In-depth knowledge of operating systems and security applications, as well as a working knowledge of network protocols and tools;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Experience in VPN Management and Support and DPLC and MPLS;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: black; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">Previous experiences in IT Auditing is a plus;</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','10/30/2018',1,7,6,5,13,'Khmer, English','2018-10-28 08:53:22','2020-06-01 06:30:47'),
	(449,15,'ប្រធានផ្នែកស្ថាបត្យកម្ម​ (Head Unit of Architecture) - ០១ នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>បង្កើត និងធ្វើបច្ចុប្បន្នភាពប្លង់ស្តង់ដាររួម ទាំងខាងក្នុង និងខាងក្រៅនៃទីតាំងបណ្តាញសាខាហត្ថាកសិករ។</li>\r\n<li>សម្របសម្រួលផ្តល់ប្លង់សាងសង់ទៅជាង និងម្ចាស់ផ្ទះជួលទីតាំង។</li>\r\n<li>គ្រប់គ្រង និង វិភាគលើគុណភាពសំណង់នៃទីតាំងបណ្តាញប្រតិបត្តិការ។</li>\r\n<li>ផ្តល់ការប្រឹក្សា តាមដាន និងជំរុញការងារសាងសង់ ឲ្យស្របតាមផែនការ។</li>\r\n<li>បង្កើតគំនិតថ្មីៗក្នុងការកែលម្អប្លង់ បង្កើនគុណភាព&nbsp; សោភ័ណ្ឌភាព នៃសំភារៈដែលត្រូវបំពាក់តាមសាខា។</li>\r\n<li>បង្កើតគោលការណ៍ សេចក្តីណែនាំ នីតិវិធីពាក់ព័ន្ធនឹងការសាងសង់។</li>\r\n<li>ចុះត្រួតពិនិត្យនៅតាមការដ្ឋានដែលកំពុងសាងសង់។</li>\r\n<li>អនុវត្តការងារផ្សេងៗទៀតពីអ្នកគ្រប់គ្រង។&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>បញ្ចប់ជំនាញផ្នែកស្ថាបត្យកម្ម ឬជំនាញដេគ័រ ដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ការងាររយៈពេលយ៉ាងតិច ០១ឆ្នាំ។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ការងារគូរប្លង់ និងសាងសង់អគារ។</li>\r\n<li>យល់ដឹងពីបទបញ្ញត្តិជាតិ ស្តីពីសំណង់ និងការងារដេគ័រ។</li>\r\n<li>មានទំនាក់ទំនងល្អ អាចប្រើប្រាស់ភាសាអង់គ្លេសបានល្អ។</li>\r\n<li>ចេះប្រើប្រាស់កម្មវិធី Word, Excel, Auto Cad, Sketch Up, Photoshop</li>\r\n<li>អាចចុះធ្វើការងារតាមខេត្តបាន។</li>\r\n</ul>',1,53,15,17,'1','11/05/2018',1,7,9,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-10-31 13:36:43','2020-05-30 08:51:37'),
	(450,15,'មន្រ្តីដេគ័រ (Decoration Officer) - ០១ នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>គូរប្លង់ការិយាល័យ និងសិក្សាតម្លៃសាងសង់ ឬជួសជុល។</li>\r\n<li>សម្របសម្រួលជាប្រចាំ ជាមួយជាងសាងសង ឬម្ចាស់ផ្ទះជួលស្តីពីការសាងសង់ និងបំពាក់សម្ភារៈ។</li>\r\n<li>វិភាគ និងត្រួតពិនិត្យ គុណភាព នៃការងារសាងសង់ការិយាល័យ ឬផ្ទះអេធីអឹម។</li>\r\n<li>សម្របសម្រួលគម្រោងសាងសង់ គុណភាព និងផែនការ។</li>\r\n<li>ចុះពិនិត្យការដ្ឋានសាងសង់ដល់ទីតាំងដែលសាងសង់សំរាប់ជួល។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើរបាយការណ៍សាងសង់ប្រចាំខែជូនប្រធានផ្នែកដេគ័រ។&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>កំពុងសិក្សា ឬ បញ្ចប់ជំនាញផ្នែកស្ថាបត្យកម្ម ឬវិស្វកម្ម&nbsp; ។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ការងាររយៈពេលយ៉ាងតិច ០១ឆ្នាំ ។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ការងារសាងសង់ ទាំងនៅការដ្ឋាន និងការិយាល័យ។</li>\r\n<li>យល់ដឹងពីបទបញ្ញត្តិជាតិ ស្តីពីសំណង់ ។</li>\r\n<li>មានទំនាក់ទំនងល្អ អាចប្រើប្រាស់ភាសាអង់គ្លេសបានល្អ។</li>\r\n<li>ចេះប្រើប្រាស់កម្មវិធី Microsoft office, AutoCAD 2D, ។</li>\r\n<li>អាចចុះធ្វើការងារតាមខេត្តបាន។&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>',1,53,15,17,'1','11/05/2018',1,7,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-10-31 13:39:07','2020-06-01 06:53:59'),
	(451,16,'Micro Business Loan Officer​ - 47 posts','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Solicits potential and existing clients in accordance with the guidelines stated in the micro business loan policies and procedures.</li>\r\n<li>Analyze and interpret financial statements of the business in order to access the repayment capacity and financial soundness of the borrower.</li>\r\n<li>Receives and screens loan applications.</li>\r\n<li>Conducts credit investigation for borrowers and their co-makers.</li>\r\n<li>Evaluates cash flow of loan applicants.</li>\r\n<li>Conducts sit visit of secure collateral.</li>\r\n<li>Ascertains the completeness of loan documents.</li>\r\n<li>Follows up delinquent clients immediately and refers to immediate supervisor.</li>\r\n<li>Recommends remedial measures for delinquent clients in accordance with the recovery policies and procedures of the Bank.</li>\r\n<li>Responsible for the attainment of his/her performance targets.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Refer from MFI.</li>\r\n<li>Bachelor with major in banking and finance, accounting, management and marketing or related field.</li>\r\n<li>At least one year experience in micro finance institution/commercial bank or related field.</li>\r\n<li>English proficiency.</li>\r\n<li>Good level of computer program (MS Word &amp; Excel).</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of business process.</li>\r\n<li>Hardworking, commitment, ability to communicate and self-motivated person.</li>\r\n<li>Good interpersonal skills.</li>\r\n<li>Attention to details.\r\n<h3>Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Borei Keyla Branch, Phnom Penh (2posts).</li>\r\n<li>Chamkar Doung Branch, Phnom Penh (3 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Chom Chao Branch, Phnom Penh (3 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Independence Monument Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Mao Tse Tung Branch, Phnom Penh (2 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Battambong Branch (2 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Kompong Cham Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Chhuk District Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Cheung Prey District Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Kompot Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Kratie Branch (9 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Kien Svay District Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Mukh Kampul Branch (2 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Ou Baek K&rsquo;am Branch, Phnom Penh (5 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Paoy Paet Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Pursat Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Ratanakiri Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Russey Keo Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Stade Chas Branch, Phnom Penh (9 posts).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'47','11/12/2018',1,5,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-10-31 13:42:51','2020-05-29 04:21:04'),
	(452,16,'ATM/POS Terminal Officer - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>IT task to support card system working smoothly.</li>\r\n<li>Fix and repair (if possible) for any PC problem, printer, and other equipment.</li>\r\n<li>Installation POS, ATM, PC, Server and some other equipment.</li>\r\n<li>Support and fix some issue from terminal team or IT.</li>\r\n<li>Instruction customer or internal employee to operation well with the terminal or PC.</li>\r\n<li>Support customer request related to technology requirement.</li>\r\n<li>POS terminal training when new pos deploy or when customer (in-house or merchant) request a new training session.</li>\r\n<li>Schedule visiting merchant to make strong relationship and get info update from merchant requirement and improvement poor services.</li>\r\n<li>ATM controlling and monitoring, status, connection and other support.</li>\r\n<li>Visit ATM when requested by branch or other department of problem occurred at the terminals.</li>\r\n<li>On site visit merchant when problem occur sometime at night time not only working hours.</li>\r\n<li>Troubleshooting with card system &amp; terminal team of any issue occurred with technical issue.</li>\r\n<li>ATM cash loading, ATM cash reporting and refill receipt delivery.</li>\r\n<li>ATM maintenance and fix issue that come from dusty.</li>\r\n<li>Collect captured card and return to customer representative.</li>\r\n<li>Installation, maintenance and update ATM &amp; POS application and also PC.</li>\r\n<li>Configuring ATM application parameters and POS terminal parameters.</li>\r\n<li>Installing new connection and connect with new installation for ATM, POS and PC.</li>\r\n<li>Troubleshooting with connection provider when connection down took place.</li>\r\n<li>Report immediately of any case urgent needed to be fix due to bank operation or customer needs.</li>\r\n<li>Report to card system, terminal team or clearing regarding to customer complain about POS terminal or ATM machine failure or merchant account is not credit and more.</li>\r\n<li>Arrange schedule for ATM maintenance, merchant&rsquo;s side visit.</li>\r\n<li>Support customer via call or direct visit.</li>\r\n<li>Training how to use POS/ATM in-house and customer.</li>\r\n<li>Come to check and fix problem at office or at merchant site when issue came from technical issue.</li>\r\n<li>Site visit ATM every week at night time and create report for improvement.</li>\r\n<li>Other ad-hoc tasks to be sure the system working smoothly, testing.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in business, communications, computer science, IT or equivalent work or educational experience.</li>\r\n<li>Experience in ATM switching system, card management system and card personalization software.</li>\r\n<li>Good knowledge in ATM and POS implementation and management.</li>\r\n<li>Good knowledge in credit card, debit card and prepaid card operation.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of financial/accounting principles, banking operation, e-banking features and components.</li>\r\n<li>Minimum two years working experience in ATM switching/card management system or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Very good interpersonal skills and communications skills (oral and written) in English language.</li>\r\n<li>Good project management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Good integrity, positive attitude, helpful, high commitment, competence and motivation.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','11/12/2018',1,6,7,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-10-31 13:44:54','2020-05-30 02:21:20'),
	(453,19,'SME Lending Support Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Review and verify the quality of loan application and complementary reference documents after received from branches and before submitted to the Credit Committee</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate and support to branch staff about guidelines related to loan processing and correcting their mistakes and/or errors of completing the loan documents</li>\r\n<li>Prepare loan documents and collect the complementary information from branches for making decision and coordinating to form up the credit committee meeting for loan approval</li>\r\n<li>Prepare loan minute appropriately and submit to the credit committee for sign approval and then scan back to the branch on time</li>\r\n<li>Keep and prepare the file of loan minute with orderly and safe</li>\r\n<li>Facilitate and inform back to the branches on time about the result of credit committee&rsquo;s decision</li>\r\n<li>Monitor and prepare the report of loan approval by the credit committee</li>\r\n<li>Report and monitor about loan quality that approved by the credit committee ( always check the client overdue and report to the credit committee)</li>\r\n<li>Train and contribute good experiences about loan assessment and communication skill to CO, CCO, and BM</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree in Banking &amp; Finance or Accounting at least 1 year prior experience in Credit Skills or commercial Loan</li>\r\n<li>Organizational and time management skills</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment</li>\r\n<li>Negotiation and internal relationship building skills</li>\r\n<li>Sound written and verbal English communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Computer Skills (Ms. Word, Excel, Power Point)</li>\r\n<li>Analysis and Reporting Skills</li>\r\n<li>Proficient Khmer typing skills</li>\r\n<li>Proactive, flexible and a good team player</li>\r\n<li>Ability on problem solving and good communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Good behavior, committed and disciplined</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','11/02/2018',1,5,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-10-31 13:58:48','2020-06-01 14:14:05'),
	(454,19,'Sale and Customer Service Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Perform sale activities on savings and other financial products</li>\r\n<li>Establish personal contact of potential clients</li>\r\n<li>Collect feedback and complaint from clients related sale and customer service care and service providing then report to Deputy Head Sale &amp; Customer Service Department</li>\r\n<li>Analyze the market in order to identify new product growth opportunities</li>\r\n<li>Provide support, monitor the work performance of front line staff related to service providing and products selling, and identify points to be improved.</li>\r\n<li>Work closely with Customer Relationship Officer (CRO) to help boost the sales performance at each branch.</li>\r\n<li>Provide support to regional, branch, and sub branch and training to branch staff</li>\r\n<li>Resolve customer queries and issues related to sale and services</li>\r\n<li>Maintain sale reports and call follow up</li>\r\n<li>And other tasks assigned by supervisor</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor in Marketing or equivalent</li>\r\n<li>At least one year experience in sales, marketing, or microfinance/banking sectors</li>\r\n<li>Excellent oral and written English</li>\r\n<li>Good communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Interpersonal skills and professional appearance</li>\r\n<li>Telephone manner</li>\r\n<li>Capacities and flexibilities of sale and marketing</li>\r\n<li>Responsibility, logical thinking and results oriented in role</li>\r\n<li>Problem solving skill</li>\r\n<li>Honesty and neutrality in work</li>\r\n<li>Ability to travel to province branches</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','11/02/2018',1,7,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-10-31 14:01:06','2020-05-30 02:22:58'),
	(455,19,'Corporate Sales Executive - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Participate in developing policies, procedures, guidelines, sale strategies and setting sales plan and execute the strategies on non-credit services</li>\r\n<li>Select potential prospective such as business owners, NGOs, churches, companies and other partners for business activities</li>\r\n<li>Prepare slides to present to corporate clients and make direct sale, appointment with potential prospective to sell non-credit services/other products or services of KREDIT</li>\r\n<li>Provide direct support to the braches on corporate sales activities, present the services/products to potential prospective, &hellip;</li>\r\n<li>Maintain good relationship with existing and potential prospective</li>\r\n<li>Follow up market information, competitors&rsquo; product information then report to direct</li>\r\n<li>Prepare the corporate sale report and monitor the corporate sale performance across the country</li>\r\n<li>Work with branch staff, CSOs and CREs, to ensure the quality and timely preparation of corporate sales report and corporate sale performance</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate liaison corporate sales activity between branched and sales and customer service department.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that all corporate sales activities are in accordance with policies and guidelines.</li>\r\n<li>Understand all risks in corporate selling process on all KREDIT service/product by reporting to related manager for finding the way to prevent and solving problem on time.</li>\r\n<li>Other Activities as assign from supervisor and requirement from KREDIT.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>At least bachelor degree in marketing, business management or similar disciplines equivalent and one year of corporate sale experience with banks, MFI or relevant fields</li>\r\n<li>Proficiency of English language (Third language: Mandarin or Thai is more advantage and priority)</li>\r\n<li>Have a skill of identifying, evaluating, presenting and selling to the target corporate client and ability to approach to the right person or high level officer of the target firm</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge on analyzing and convincing corporate target clients and on business concept/process/flow and value chain of corporate sector</li>\r\n<li>The sense of transforming the business activities to match with the financial products and provide the solution to the corporate client and capacity to enlarge the corporate reference to another firm and a professional and protocol behaviors to match with the corporate client</li>\r\n<li>High level of communication and negotiation skills with the corporate client</li>\r\n<li>Confidentiality of KREDIT branding in front of the corporate target</li>\r\n<li>Ability to communicate, present and influence credible and effectively at all levels of the organization including executive level</li>\r\n<li>Strong networking in the corporate sectors</li>\r\n<li>Ability to drive the sales process from plan to close and to articulate the distinct aspect of products and services and position them against competitors</li>\r\n<li>Willing to travel to all KREDIT&rsquo;s operation areas in provinces</li>\r\n<li>Both genders is encouraged.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','11/02/2018',1,8,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-10-31 14:06:05','2020-06-01 06:30:28'),
	(456,19,'ប្រធានមន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Chief Credit Officer) - ០២នាក់','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យសំណុំឯកសារឥណទាន និងវាយតម្លៃឥណទានដែលអតិថិជនស្នើសុំដោយគោរពទៅតាមគោលនយោបាយ និងនីតិវិធីផ្សេងៗរបស់ក្រេឌីត ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងតាមដានការបង់សងត្រលប់របស់អតិថិជនប្រចាំថ្ងៃ ព្រមទាំងសម្របសម្រួលក្នុងការចុះដោះស្រាយកម្ចីដែលមានបញ្ហា និងចូលសរួមក្នុង&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ការបញ្ចេញឥណទាននៅតាមសហគមន៍ ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">សិក្សាស្វែងយល់អោយបានច្បាស់អំពីស្ថានភាពឥណទានក្នុងតំបន់ដោយសិក្សាពីគូរប្រកួតប្រជែង សេដ្ឋកិច្ច​ សង្គម ភូមិសាស្រ្ត ប្រវត្តិឥណទាន ។ល។ ដើម្បីរកចំនុចខ្លាំង ចំនុចខ្សោយដែលជះឥទ្ធិពលដល់ប្រតិបត្តិការរបស់ក្រេឌីត ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">ណែនាំ និងកែតម្រូ