	(515,16,'Deputy Head of Cash Operation Service Department - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Manage Complaints resolution team to ensure the process of analyze and settlement are quality by satisfy from customer/Branches in timeline manner.</li>\r\n<li>Seek approval from Treasury Department for all Fund Movement to/from branches.</li>\r\n<li>Manage cash service across branches and ATM/CIM services on bank&rsquo;s public holiday and ensure the process adhere to the policy and procedure for controlling operational risk.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the physical cash (Main Vault &amp; Mini Vault &amp; Teller Bag) are matching with Core banking system &amp; Flex Tool (Daily Cash Record Report, Daily Cash Record Sheet Report, Main &amp; Mini Vault Excel Report) for controlling operational risk.</li>\r\n<li>Report Immediately to management of any issue to get proper support and best solution.</li>\r\n<li>Improve and develop the business process, policy and procedure of Cash Operation Service Department for achievement standard service and performance.</li>\r\n<li>None Complaints/Zero error from Client/branches on dispute transaction. Ex: late of service investigation and settlement to customer account.</li>\r\n<li>None complaints from customer/Branches of cash service.</li>\r\n<li>No complaint/Zero error from Branches on upload and refill cash to ATM Cassette.</li>\r\n<li>No complaint on CIM encasement/cash delivery from clients/branches. Ex: client cannot deposit cash into CIM. Or cash delivery is not on time to the branch.</li>\r\n<li>None error of cash loss/over of Mini &amp; Main Vault &amp; Teller Till.</li>\r\n<li>No complaint on Currency Note from branches/clients. Ex: old note or stain note.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree in Finance &amp; Banking, Accounting, or other related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Minimum 5 years working experience of Cash Management, Problem Solving of Teller&rsquo;s Area.</li>\r\n<li>Practical knowledge of operational risk and compliance with policies and procedures applied in Banking Industry is an asset.</li>\r\n<li>Good customer service skills.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Planning, Organizational &amp; time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Negotiation and internal relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Attention to details and accuracy.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,17,'1','11/26/2018',1,10,6,5,14,'Khmer, English','2018-11-03 15:43:00','2020-05-30 07:13:21'),
	(516,16,'Head of Cash Operation Service Department - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Manage Complaints resolution team to ensure the process of analyze and settlement are quality by satisfy from customer/Branches in timeline manner.</li>\r\n<li>Manage recruitment process of Telling&rsquo;s area by providing planning, educate staff as well as setting up the guideline to improve the weakness and developing service and ensure the staff&rsquo;s performance of Branches transaction and resource for operation growth.</li>\r\n<li>Manage cash service across branches and ATM/CIM services on bank&rsquo;s public holiday and ensure the process adhere to the policy and procedure for controlling operational risk.</li>\r\n<li>Improve and develop the business process, policy and procedure of Cash Operation Service Department for achievement standard service and performance.</li>\r\n<li>None Complaints/Zero error from Client/branches on dispute transaction. Ex: late of service investigation and settlement to customer account.</li>\r\n<li>No complaints from Human Resource team of performance recruiting Teller&rsquo;s Area Staff.</li>\r\n<li>No complaints of staff&rsquo;s performance&nbsp; for set up KPI.</li>\r\n<li>No complaints from customer/Branches of cash service/ATM/CIM on bank&rsquo;s public holiday.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree in Finance &amp; Banking, Accounting, or other related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Minimum 5 years working experience of Cash Management, Problem Solving of Teller&rsquo;s Area.</li>\r\n<li>Practical knowledge of operational risk and compliance with policies and procedures applied in Banking Industry is an asset.</li>\r\n<li>Good customer service skills.</li>\r\n<li>Planning, Organizational &amp; time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Cash Flow Management.</li>\r\n<li>Problem Solving Skill.</li>\r\n<li>Negotiation and internal relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Attention to details and accuracy.</li>\r\n<li>Good in Computer literacy.</li>\r\n<li>Good in written and communication both in Khmer and English.</li>\r\n<li>Honest and highly commitment.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,17,'1','11/26/2018',1,11,6,5,14,'Khmer, English','2018-11-03 15:44:31','2020-05-30 07:18:30'),
	(517,16,'Head of Payroll Service Unit - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Responsible for building and managing payroll service team.</li>\r\n<li>Responsible for the attainment of the bank&rsquo;s target regarding the payroll service.</li>\r\n<li>Facilitates the formulation of sales targets for the unit and each staff.</li>\r\n<li>Develop, implement and manage the sales strategies for payroll business and ensures that the strategic plan objectives are cascaded to sale staffs.</li>\r\n<li>Develop and monitor the implantation for the SQ tools to ensure the customer will get the best quality of service from the bank.</li>\r\n<li>Monitor the smooth implementation of customer experience improvement platform.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that the development and attainment of the sale strategies and sale target are aligned with bank&rsquo;s policies, procedures and guidelines.</li>\r\n<li>Collaborate with relevant business process and developer team to create or revise business process and products.</li>\r\n<li>Responsible for on-going evaluation of the sale target for payroll, and when the results fall short, take remedial actions with other stakeholders to improve the sale.</li>\r\n<li>Develop and manage the cross-selling mechanism between different products of the bank to maximize the profit for the bank and retain customers.</li>\r\n<li>Manage the coaching and training of staff capacity improvement.</li>\r\n<li>Manage the team to undertake market research to understand the opportunities in line with bank&rsquo;s strategies, and keep top management fully informed about the result.</li>\r\n<li>Work collaboratively with key internal and external stakeholders to define product enhancement, detailed specification and go-to-market strategy.</li>\r\n<li>Proactively undertake industry networking to collect market intelligence.</li>\r\n<li>Actively find ways to improve the customer service levels for customer facing staffs.</li>\r\n<li>Propose and monitor the implemented actions to improve the customer service</li>\r\n<li>Assist the solution finding for the complaints from customers.</li>\r\n<li>Actively work with HR and BM to search for qualified candidate for each sale positive.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that the new recruit is thoroughly introduced to the bank through induction program.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that new recruit is well-informed about his/her responsibilities and target during probation period before they start their works.</li>\r\n<li>Track the performance of new recruit during the probation and evaluate new recruit&rsquo;s performance at the end of the probation period.</li>\r\n<li>Continuously provide training about sale skills and customer service to payroll staffs.</li>\r\n<li>Closely work with HR and BM to identify opportunity to send sale staff for external or internal training which is beneficial to his/her works with the bank.</li>\r\n<li>Responsible for career and personal development of direct reporting employee.</li>\r\n<li>Be a proactive team participant, proactively contributing to an environment where members are proud of to be part of ABA Bank, passionate about customers and eager to make the team succeed.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>4 year experience in sale area in banks(at least 2 year in managing sale team).</li>\r\n<li>Experience in managing payroll service is preferable.</li>\r\n<li>Experience in analyzing economy trend.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of bank&rsquo;s product and service.</li>\r\n<li>Practical knowledge of operating risk and compliance policies and procedures.</li>\r\n<li>Practical knowledge of customer service.</li>\r\n<li>Experience in working with senior management.</li>\r\n<li>Result Oriented and be a driver.</li>\r\n<li>Leadership skills and have good people judgment.</li>\r\n<li>Excellent Customer Services Skills.</li>\r\n<li>Time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Skill in analyzing and evaluating financial information.</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrated high level on communication and influencing skills.</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrated entrepreneurial and commercial thinking.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','11/26/2018',1,11,9,5,13,'Khmer, English','2018-11-03 15:46:08','2020-05-30 08:04:46'),
	(518,15,'Director of Project Management Office for Business Development & Corporate Sales - 01 post','<p><strong>Business Development and Corporate Sales:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Develop and manage business development and partnership strategy to support company long term growth aspiration primarily cover across areas of loan, liability products, and fee-based income</li>\r\n<li>Develop new partnership of both target domestic and overseas companies, and manage ongoing relationship</li>\r\n<li>Lead Corporate sales function focusing on non-loan products and work closely with related teams HKL to ensure service delivery satisfaction; For loan products, contribute through loan referrals</li>\r\n<li>Monitor and lead team to implement marketing/sales plan, enhance sales productivity and deliver sales targets</li>\r\n<li>Liaise with parent group company to build synergy and enable best practice sharing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Project Management:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Track, analyze, and report progress of key project portfolio under responsibility</li>\r\n<li>Undertake different role(s) within project management. Depending on nature of each project: 1). Primary role is to lead/manage transformative project to align with corporate strategic direction; the role requires end-to-end management of project delivery which include business requirement development, activity planning, risk/benefit identification, cross functional coordination, and effective project closure monitoring. 2). As and when required, perform business analyst role to support functional teams</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate across key stakeholders to ensure effective changes and collaboration in the organization</li>\r\n<li>Manage necessary communication across organization to support programs or project implementation; including presentation to stakeholders throughout project cycle</li>\r\n<li>Foster a collaborative working environment with functional teams.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Degree in Marketing or sale or related field is preferred, MBA is preferred</li>\r\n<li>Good proficiency in MS. Office including Ms. Excel , Ms. PowerPoint</li>\r\n<li>At least 7 years experiences, including 3 years in management position &amp; 3-4 years in project/product management or relevant experiences<br />Deep knowledge of the Bank&rsquo;s products and services and those provided by the competitors</li>\r\n<li>Sound working knowledge of general business process and organizational framework such as goals, strategy, culture and structure</li>\r\n<li>Candidate with sound experiences in one of the following areas will have advantage, i.e. data analytics, process improvement, digital financial services, product development, and channel development</li>\r\n<li>Be very good in verbal and written English</li>\r\n<li>Good time management skills and ability to multi-task</li>\r\n<li>Strong sense of urgency with high level of commitment and determination to deliver a great result</li>\r\n<li>Ability to monitor process/facilitate progress of process portfolio</li>\r\n<li>Skill analyzing and evaluating financial information</li>\r\n<li>Experience in strategic sales in the financial services sector or retail banking</li>\r\n<li>Expert knowledge and experience in the field of: National sales, developing national sales strategies, cross selling strategies and implementation</li>\r\n</ul>',1,85,15,17,'1','11/30/2018',1,11,6,5,7,'Khmer, English','2018-11-03 15:50:59','2020-05-31 20:16:36'),
	(519,15,'Director of Project Management Office for Customer Experience Management - 01 post','<p><strong>Customer Experience Management:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Define comprehensive target customer experience across customer segments, life cycle, and channels</li>\r\n<li>Lead the development, implementation and evaluation of strategic, tactical and operational customer engagement plans, programs, and initiatives to align with the customer experience strategy</li>\r\n<li>Lead and/or direct specific customer research programs, dialogue and other forms of engagement to understand key concerns and issues and inform review and enhancement of customer services, channel, and service delivery models</li>\r\n<li>Drive the ongoing development of a customer-centric culture across the organization through internal activities and measurement of key processes and/or customer touchpoints</li>\r\n<li>Liaise with parent group company to build synergy and enable best practice sharing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Project Management:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Track, analyze, and report progress of key project portfolio under responsibility</li>\r\n<li>Undertake different role(s) within project management. Depending on nature of each project: 1). Primary role is to lead/manage transformative project to align with corporate strategic direction; the role requires end-to-end management of project delivery which include business requirement development, activity planning, risk/benefit identification, cross functional coordination, and effective project closure monitoring. 2). As and when required, perform business analyst role to support functional teams</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate across key stakeholders to ensure effective changes and collaboration in the organization</li>\r\n<li>Manage necessary communication across organization to support programs or project implementation; including presentation to stakeholders throughout project cycle</li>\r\n<li>Foster a collaborative working environment with functional teams</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Degree or professional qualification in marketing or Business related fields (MBA is preferred)</li>\r\n<li>7 years proven working experiences, including 3 years in Management position, 3-4 years in Research, product development and relevant skill)</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of customer experience management approaches &amp; methodologies used in marketing and sales</li>\r\n<li>Evidence of strong management, planning, project management and organizational skills, required to manage an extensive portfolio of events, communication campaigns and customer-centric activities</li>\r\n<li>Excellent communication (both written and verbal), influencing and negotiation skills, required to cooperate with a wide range of internal and external stakeholders combined with driven and assertive personality</li>\r\n<li>Relevant marketing experience, ideally in a customer-centric fast paced environment</li>\r\n<li>Experience in customer segmentation and successful communication campaigns, supported by data-analysis and market insight, required to deliver successful customer communication campaign</li>\r\n<li>Experience in people management, leading and directing multiple team members in a busy task-oriented environment,</li>\r\n<li>Flexibility with work location</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,85,15,17,'1','11/30/2018',1,9,6,5,7,'English','2018-11-03 15:54:26','2020-06-01 01:41:09'),
	(520,15,'Director of Project Management Office for Corporate Branding Management - 01 post','<p><strong>Corporate Branding Management:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Define corporate branding strategy &amp; annual strategic direction for marketing /media activities.</li>\r\n<li>Implement branding strategy initiatives for both internal and external audiences, including corporate marketing activities.</li>\r\n<li>Engage necessary research to regularly assess market trends, competitor activities, customer behavior and company brand equity.</li>\r\n<li>Oversee PR Plan. Manages relevant communication strategy to strengthen public and corporate brand image</li>\r\n<li>Develop necessary internal communication to staff and lead company culture building initiatives by working closely with Marketing and HR teams, e.g. performance-based, digital embracement culture, etc.</li>\r\n<li>Provide guideline, work closely and review with Marketing, Product, Branch support teams to ensure effective execution to deliver brand promise (culture, e.g. product, advertising, premise, customer interaction, etc,)</li>\r\n<li>Liaise with parent group company to build synergy and enable best practice sharing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Project Management:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Track, analyze, and report progress of key project portfolio under responsibility</li>\r\n<li>Undertake different role(s) within project management. Depending on nature of each project: 1). Primary role is to lead/manage transformative project to align with corporate strategic direction; the role requires end-to-end management of project delivery which include business requirement development, activity planning, risk/benefit identification, cross functional coordination, and effective project closure monitoring. 2). As and when required, perform business analyst role to support functional teams</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate across key stakeholders to ensure effective changes and collaboration in the organization</li>\r\n<li>Manage necessary communication across organization to support programs or project implementation; including presentation to stakeholders throughout project cycle</li>\r\n<li>Foster a collaborative working environment with functional teams</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Degree or professional qualification in marketing or , Journalism, or Business related fields (MBA is preferred)</li>\r\n<li>7 years proven working experiences, including 3 years in Management position, 3-4 years in Marketing and relevant skill)</li>\r\n<li>Experience in brand management, engagement campaign development and experiential marketing,</li>\r\n<li>Excellent communication (both written and verbal), influencing and negotiation skills, required to cooperate with a wide range of internal and external stakeholders combined with driven and assertive personality</li>\r\n<li>Experience in customer segmentation and successful communication campaigns, supported by data-analysis and market insight, required to deliver successful customer communication campaign</li>\r\n<li>Experience in people management, leading and directing multiple team members in a busy task-oriented environment,</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge and understanding of mass/marketing-communication systems</li>\r\n<li>Evidence of strong management, planning, project management and organizational skills</li>\r\n<li>Flexibility with work location</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,85,15,17,'1','11/30/2018',1,9,6,5,7,'English','2018-11-03 15:57:36','2020-05-31 06:09:00'),
	(521,15,'Director of Project Management Office for New Product and Channel Development - 01 post','<p><strong>New Product and Channel Development:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Formulate product strategy and channel strategy roadmap</li>\r\n<li>For new product development, design product concept, conduct feasibility study to obtain relevant approvals, collaborate with relevant functions to develop detailed end-to-end requirements and implement new products which cover across asset, liability, and fee-based categories. Monitor product performance post launch per agreed period</li>\r\n<li>Work closely with business development team to develop product package and client solutions</li>\r\n<li>Lead implementation of new strategic/alternative channels</li>\r\n<li>Liaise with parent group company to build synergy and enable best practice sharing</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Project Management:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Track, analyze, and report progress of key project portfolio under responsibility</li>\r\n<li>Undertake different role(s) within project management. Depending on nature of each project: 1). Primary role is to lead/manage transformative project to align with corporate strategic direction; the role requires end-to-end management of project delivery which include business requirement development, activity planning, risk/benefit identification, cross functional coordination, and effective project closure monitoring. 2). As and when required, perform business analyst role to support functional teams</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate across key stakeholders to ensure effective changes and collaboration in the organization</li>\r\n<li>Manage necessary communication across organization to support programs or project implementation; including presentation to stakeholders throughout project cycle</li>\r\n<li>Foster a collaborative working environment with functional teams</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Degree in business or related field is preferred, MBA is preferred</li>\r\n<li>Good proficiency in MS. Office including Ms. Excel , Ms. PowerPoint</li>\r\n<li>At least 7 years experiences, including 3 years in management position &amp; 3-4 years in project/product management or relevant experiences</li>\r\n<li>Deep knowledge of specific complex financial solutions and products including the knowledge of financial markets, social-economic dynamics, and regulatory requirement relevant to the products</li>\r\n<li>Sound working knowledge of general business process and organizational framework such as goals, strategy, culture and structure</li>\r\n<li>Candidate with sound experiences in one of the following areas will have advantage, i.e. data analytics, process improvement, digital financial services, product development, and channel development</li>\r\n<li>Be very good in verbal and written English</li>\r\n<li>Good time management skills and ability to multi-task</li>\r\n<li>Strong sense of urgency with high level of commitment and determination to deliver a great result</li>\r\n<li>Ability to monitor process/facilitate progress of process portfolio</li>\r\n<li>Be available to travel to rural areas if required</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,85,15,17,'1','11/30/2018',1,9,6,5,7,'English','2018-11-03 16:01:29','2020-05-31 20:38:07'),
	(522,15,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ១៤០នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការផ្សាព្វផ្សាយ ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីធីត(HKL) ដើម្បីពង្រីកទីផ្សារ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនសក្តានុពល។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំឯកសារឥណទាន ដើម្បីផ្តល់ឥណទានជូនអតិថិជន។&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងតាមដានការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>បំពេញការងារផ្សេងៗតាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>ជាប់បាក់ឌុប ឬ កំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្ររង ឬបរិញ្ញាបត្រលើគ្រប់ជំនាញ ។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៏ផ្នែកលក់ ឬការផ្សព្វផ្សាយកាន់តែប្រសើ។</li>\r\n<li>រួសរាយរាក់ទាក់ និងការបាស្រ័យទាក់ទងល្អ។</li>\r\n<li>មានអត្តចរិកល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈ ក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួននិងអាចបើកបរបាន។</li>\r\n<li>ផ្នែកគណិតវិទ្យាៈ ការវិភាគ និង គណនា</li>\r\n<li>ប្រវត្តិរស់នៅក្នុងសហគមន៍ល្អ។</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong>ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ</strong></span><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong>:</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បន្ទាយមានជ័យ (៤នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បាត់ដំបង (១នាក់) </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រាជធានីភ្នំពេញ (៤០នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កំពង់ធំ (១០នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កំពង់ចាម (៤នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ខេត្ដរតនគិរី (៤នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កណ្តាល (១៧នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កំពង់ស្ពឺ(២នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មណ្ឌលគិរី (៣នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កោះកុង(៣នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ព្រះសីហនុ (៨នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ព្រៃវែង (១០នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ពោធិ៍សាត់ (២នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">សៀមរាប (៣នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ក្រចេះ(៣នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">តាកែវ (៦នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ត្បូងឃ្មុំ (៧នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កំពង់ឆ្នាំង (២នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">កំពត(៣នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ខេត្តកែប (២នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ព្រះវិហា(៣នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ស្វាយរៀង(៣នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'140','11/15/2018',1,16,3,1,1,'Khmer, English','2018-11-03 16:06:01','2020-05-31 14:55:20'),
	(523,16,'Regional Administrator - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Monitor the Branch Admin work flow.</li>\r\n<li>Provide training and technical support for branch admin.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate and consolidate the quarterly fixed asset request from all branches.</li>\r\n<li>To act as link officer between the branch admin and the admin support at head office to ensure a smooth and consistent service.</li>\r\n<li>To receive, respond to and initiate correspondence from branch admin, and admin support at head office.</li>\r\n<li>Provide information for consultation documents, and questionnaires concerning all aspects of Branch network.</li>\r\n<li>Develops, coordinates and implements systems, procedures and controls to ensure and effective centralized work flow.</li>\r\n<li>Assist in arranging and facilitating meetings, training events, support groups.</li>\r\n<li>Analyze the root cause of the occurred problem and coordinate the problem solving with concerning body.</li>\r\n<li>Research, prepare and supply information as required.</li>\r\n<li>Responsive feedback and communication &ndash;internally and externally.</li>\r\n<li>Reporting with the branch checklist.</li>\r\n<li>To ensure timeline of branch expansion plan.</li>\r\n<li>Consulting with branch regarding the furfure branch expansion.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure all documentation, checklist report, and calibration has been carried out accordingly and update.</li>\r\n<li>Dealing with local authority or governor to ensure other legal document and framework for admin department.</li>\r\n<li>Act in line with all relevant branches/department to eradicate the problem which affects to banking operation.</li>\r\n<li>Quarterly branch visit.</li>\r\n<li>Assist with preparation of the branch annual budget plan.</li>\r\n<li>To review and monitor branch activity, and assist branches with the creation and monitoring of branch development plans. To take a pro active approach to drive branch activity forward, and delivering on those plans.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree in Administration, Management, Accounting or related skill.</li>\r\n<li>At least, 2 year experiences in administrative or accounting work.</li>\r\n<li>Computer skills including the ability to operate computerized accounting.</li>\r\n<li>Effective written communications skills.</li>\r\n<li>Effective verbal and listening communications skills.</li>\r\n<li>Analytical and problem solving skills.</li>\r\n<li>Develops, coordinates and implements systems, procedures and controls to ensure and effective centralized purchasing.</li>\r\n<li>Trustworthy and with strong negotiation, communication and interpersonal skills</li>\r\n<li>Stress management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Time management skills</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','11/26/2018',1,6,3,5,2,'English','2018-11-10 10:35:45','2020-05-31 05:27:25'),
	(524,16,'NET Developer - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Participate in requirements analysis</li>\r\n<li>Translate business requirements into technical solutions</li>\r\n<li>Create technical design specifications and documentation</li>\r\n<li>Execute processes to ensure application integrity and availability</li>\r\n<li>Collaborate with internal teams to produce software design and architecture</li>\r\n<li>Write clean, scalable code using .NET programming C# language</li>\r\n<li>Test and deploy applications and systems</li>\r\n<li>Revise, update, refactor and debug code</li>\r\n<li>Improve existing software</li>\r\n<li>Serve as an expert on applications and provide technical support</li>\r\n<li>May research alternative development methodologies and make recommendations for team improvement</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>3+ years experience in software design and development</li>\r\n<li>Strong experience with .NET, C# and SQL Server</li>\r\n<li>Participates in defining and guidance of development coding standards</li>\r\n<li>Strong understanding of JavaScript, AJAX, JSON, jQuery, CSS and HTML5</li>\r\n<li>Ability and desire to write object oriented, efficient and maintainable code</li>\r\n<li>Ability and desire to write solid unit test cases</li>\r\n<li>Experience in REST and WCF services</li>\r\n<li>Web Services or Web APIs</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with the ASP.NET framework, SQL Server and design/architectural patterns (e.g. Model-View-Controller (MVC))</li>\r\n<li>Database design and development (Microsoft SQL Server)</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with architecture styles/APIs (REST, RPC)</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of Agile methodologies</li>\r\n<li>Excellent troubleshooting and communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Experience with concurrent development source control (Git) and continuous integration Jenkins</li>\r\n<li>Attention to detail</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','12/07/2018',1,6,7,5,12,'English','2018-11-10 10:37:04','2020-05-30 19:32:11'),
	(525,15,'Independent Risk Champion - 15 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Conduct credit review on post-disbursement to make sure credit file maintain accurate/reliable/sufficient information &amp; match to actual.</li>\r\n<li>Involve in credit review &amp; approval committee at branch level &amp; have authority to comment &amp; risk opinion &amp; voting on loan application</li>\r\n<li>Conduct client visit as well as business assessment &amp; collateral assessment as per required for suspicious or abnormal loan application.</li>\r\n<li>Sample check &amp; review on credit file that assessed by Credit Officer &amp; review the loan application that approved by credit.</li>\r\n<li>Analyze trend of NPL in the operation area &amp; find out the routs cause for reporting to Risk Management Division.</li>\r\n<li>Perform Branch Security Self-Assessment &amp; monitor on top risk at branch level (Operational Risk only)</li>\r\n<li>Act as supporting champion at branch level to support branch staff on AML, CFT, FATCA, ABC agenda.</li>\r\n<li>Perform Compliance Testing and Check to ensure the level of non-compliance is low (base on internal audit finding).</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Banking &amp; Finance, Business Management or Economic or other related field.</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 years experiences in Banking/financial institution, including some experiences in field of risk management, audit &amp; compliance function would be an advantage.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy is a must and excellent communication in English.yExcellent analytical &amp; problem solving skills and willing to work with group &amp; be able to work under pressure.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Location:</span></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Memot District Branch Memot Commune (01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Peam Ro District Branch - Preaek Khsay Kha (01 post)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Rotonak Mondol District Branch - Sdau Commune(01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Operational Support Office&nbsp; (01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Cham Provincial Branch (01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Khan&nbsp; Pur Senchey Branch - Sangkat Chaom Chau(01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Speu Provincial Branch (01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Pursat Provincial Branch (01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Koh Kong Provincial Branch (01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Banteay Mean Chey Provincial Branch&nbsp; (01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Moung Reussey District Branch - Kear Commune (01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Puok District Branch - Puok Commune(01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Bati District Branch - Sour Phi Commune(01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Prey Chhor District Branch - Chrey Vien Commune(01 post)</li>\r\n<li>Basedth District Branch - Pheari Mean Chey Commune(01 post)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,28,'15','11/22/2018',1,8,8,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 10:43:35','2020-06-01 08:23:37'),
	(526,15,'Senior Officer, Human Resource Organization Development - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Collaborate and partner with HR team to ensure HR strategies are aligned and integrated with HR direction;</li>\r\n<li>Accountable for the day to day performance of the Organizational Development (OD);</li>\r\n<li>Support with leadership development, succession planning and talent management to make sure we have someone ready to take over the position if someone leave or new senior position made available;</li>\r\n<li>Design and develop different policies, manuals, guideline and other materials including handouts and visual aids related to HRD;</li>\r\n<li>Assist Head of Human Resource for organization structure design, job/function scope design;</li>\r\n<li>Represent HR to lead manpower planning and staff budgeting plan by working closely with Financial Planning team and other related teams;</li>\r\n<li>Identify and evaluate HR initiatives to ascertain appropriate programs that meet company goals;</li>\r\n<li>Lead and facilitate exit interview process and see whether exited staff is suitable for other position within the company by working closely with other functional department;</li>\r\n<li>Assist Head of Human Resource to develop and design the career path development and management program;</li>\r\n<li>Contributes in the design and implementation of the HR internal communication process, ensure its effectiveness;</li>\r\n<li>Develop other adhoc report as required by management;</li>\r\n<li>Handle and perform other tasks as assigned by direct supervisor.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Human Resource, Management, Political science, Psychology or related field</li>\r\n<li>Good command in English language skills</li>\r\n<li>At least 2-3 years of experience in HR domain</li>\r\n<li>Age above 28 years old</li>\r\n<li>Good analytical skill, systematic thinking, problem solving decision making and managerial skills</li>\r\n<li>A team player with excellent interpersonal</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','11/26/2018',1,6,8,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 10:46:17','2020-05-30 19:19:30'),
	(527,13,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ៤០នាក់','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 14.2667px; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">សិក្សា អនុវត្ថឱ្យត្រឹមត្រូវ និងទាន់សម័យ តាមគោលការណ៍ និងនីតិវិធីឥណទាន។</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">ចុះផ្សព្វផ្សាយ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនគោលដៅ ឱ្យមកប្រើប្រាស់សេវាកម្មហិរញ្ញវត្ថុរបស់ហ្វូណន។</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\">សិក្សា វិភាគ និងវាយតម្លៃឥណទាន ឱ្យបានត្រឹមត្រូវ ច្បាស់លាស់ និងមានប្រសិទ្ធភាពខ្ពស់។</span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\">តាមដានការប្រើប្រាស់ទុន និងការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0.0001pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\">ធ្វើកិច្ចការផ្សេងៗទៀតតាមតម្រូវការរបស់ថ្នាក់ដឹកនាំ។</span></span></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\">បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញបត្រ ឬកំពុងសិក្សាឆ្នាំទី៣ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រងទូទៅ ឬជំនាញដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">មានបទពិសោធន៍ផ្នែកលក់ ឬផ្នែកទីផ្សារកាន់តែ​ប្រសើរ</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">មានជំនាញក្នុងការប្រាស្រ័យទាក់ទង</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">ជាមនុស្សអំណត់ តស៊ូ ស្វាហាប់ ស្មោះត្រង់ មានឆន្ទៈខ្ពស់ និងមានចំណូលចិត្តបម្រើការងារនៅតាមជនបទ</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: #555555; font-family: Content, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 10pt;\">ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួន</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10pt;\">ផ្តល់អាទិភាពចំពោះបេក្ខជនដែលរស់នៅទីតាំងសុំបម្រើការងារ</span>\r\n<h3 style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Content, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.1; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 24px;\">Location</h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Khmer OS Content;\">សាខាខេត្តមណ្ឌលគីរី, សាខាខេត្តរតនគីរី, សាខាស្រុកពញ្ញាក្រែក, សាខាស្រុកស្ទឹងត្រង់, សាខាស្រុកព្រៃឈរ, សាខាស្រុកបាធាយ, សាខាខេត្តកំពង់ធំ, សាខាស្រុកបារាយណ៍, សាខាស្រុកកំពង់ត្រឡាច, សាខាស្រុកមោងឬស្សី,​សាខាស្រុកក្រឡាញ់, សាខាស្រុកខ្សាច់កណ្តាល,​សាខាស្រុកបន្ទាយមាស, សាខាខេត្តព្រះសីហនុ, សាខាខេត្តតាកែវ, សាខាខេត្តពោធិ៍សាត់, សាខាស្រុកពញ្ញាក្រែក, សាខាខេត្តសៀបរាម,​ សាខាស្រុកព្រៃនប់,​សាខាខេត្តក្រចេះ, ខេត្តឧត្តរមានជ័យ, និងក្នុងរាជធានីភ្នំពេញ</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'40','11/15/2018',1,8,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 10:55:00','2020-05-31 06:25:48'),
	(528,16,'Employee Relations Officer - 01 post','<h3>Compliance and Processes</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Manage the branch compliance process and procedure with complying to Cambodia labor law and regulations.</li>\r\n<li>Develop innovative solutions to complex and sensitive employer-employee relations problems.</li>\r\n<li>Perform a wide range of professional-level employer-employee relations activities.</li>\r\n<li>Compile data and analyze situations; translate findings into clear, concise reports and recommendations; and meet important deadlines.</li>\r\n<li>Interpret, apply, and explain applicable laws, policies, and precedents to employee relations matters.</li>\r\n<li>Review any gaps or non-compliance matters to the laws or policies.</li>\r\n<li>Manage departing employees process, including creating appropriate tickets to disable access, retrieve equipment/materials</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Communication with respective stakeholders and customers</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Establish and maintain working relation with Ministry of Labor and Vocational Training, Arbitration, and local government authorities whose functions are related to employer-employee relation.</li>\r\n<li>Effectively counsel employees with problems which are adversely affecting work performance.</li>\r\n<li>Provide support on staff engagement and disciplinary action when needed.;</li>\r\n<li>Participates in a variety of standing and ad hoc committees regarding personnel practices.</li>\r\n<li>Researches information used in the negotiation process on matters such as salaries, employment practices, employee benefits, etc.; prepares reports on findings; and makes recommendations.</li>\r\n<li>Initiate and enhance the staff well-being and staff care program.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Filing and Administrative Management</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-blue bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Compile, store, or retrieve employee related information, such as staff data, insurance, &hellip;etc.</li>\r\n<li>Effectively utilizes the capabilities and functions of standard office or specialized software applications such as data management, spreadsheet, presentation, and word processing in completing assigned reports or projects.&ensp;</li>\r\n<li>Develop and support with various research projects and or special projects, and or survey or feedbacks.</li>\r\n<li>Manage other related administrative tasks as assigned.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree preferably with a major in labor and industrial relations, human resource management, law, industrial or organizational psychology, public administration, or a related field.</li>\r\n<li>Minimum three years of personnel experience in interpreting bargaining contract provisions and investigating, analyzing, and resolving disciplinary matters, and complaints.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of Cambodia Labor Laws and rules.</li>\r\n<li>Good at interpersonal skills, organizational and time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Good in written and oral communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>High-quality of attention to details and accuracy.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively independently and in a team as required.</li>\r\n<li>Capabilities of computer systems, applications, and hardware used in the employer-employee relations field.</li>\r\n<li>Understand administrative organization, personnel, and policies of ABA Bank is a plus.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','12/07/2018',1,7,8,5,12,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 10:57:54','2020-05-30 17:58:18'),
	(529,15,'Manager, Corporate Compliance - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Review on announcement/documents before released to public as assure the transparency and no missed lead of communication;&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Prepare annual AML assessment per group and regulatory requirement;</li>\r\n<li>Support and review criteria on AML/CFT monitoring base on change in market trend and group requirement;</li>\r\n<li>Advise and train to company staff on implementation regards code of conduct, anti-corruption policy and AML;</li>\r\n<li>Initiate the discussion among team on the matter identified from team;</li>\r\n<li>Enhance internal process and support on new initiatives which related to core task of corporate compliance</li>\r\n<li>Review of AML report from team and consolidate&nbsp; monthly report;</li>\r\n<li>Ensure follow up of AML critical issues and escalate accordingly;</li>\r\n<li>Liaise regularly with numerous stakeholder but not limit to front office, other business units, IT Assist with ad-hoc requests;</li>\r\n<li>Some travel required.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Finance/Banking or related studies;</li>\r\n<li>At least 3-years experienced in compliance;</li>\r\n<li>Understanding principle of banking and FI products;</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of due diligence and local money laundering requirement</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrate aware AML/CFT requirement</li>\r\n<li>Understand principles of banking operation, and banking code</li>\r\n<li>Excellent verbal, presentation and written communication</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy required (Excel, Words, PowerPoint)</li>\r\n<li>Integrity and understand of duties and cares</li>\r\n<li>Report to Deputy of Compliance&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','11/30/2018',1,8,9,5,12,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:00:35','2020-06-01 02:03:59'),
	(530,14,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ២០នាក់','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Promote and sell credit and saving products to potential clients</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Prepare loan application of clients</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Monitor and control the loan payment and re-investigate clients after loan disbursement</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Report to credit team leader or credit manager</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Manage loan/ OD contract</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Implement the credit policies</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Participate in arranging the credit strategic plan</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Evaluate and analyze customers</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Good understanding of the customer characteristic</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Good understanding of real estate evaluation and analysis</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Good understanding of Cambodian law</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Be effective sale forces</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">Other tasks assigned by management</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Male, age range from 20-35 years old</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Associated or Bachelor Degree in accounting, finance &amp; banking, management, economics or related fields.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Working experience 1 year up.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Good written and verbal communication skill in both Khmer and English.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Strong interpersonal and relationship building skills.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Computer literacy (Microsoft Office: Word, Excel&hellip;etc.).</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Strong organizational and interpersonal communication skill.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Willing to work at the fields.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Be honest, initiative, hard-working and committed.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">Must be full of energy, time flexible.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Location</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>ទីស្នាក់ការកណ្តាល (៣នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាតាខ្មៅ (៣នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាអង្គស្នួល (៥នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាព្រែកឯង (៣នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាទឹកថ្លា (៣នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាកំពង់ស្ពឺ (៣នាក់)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'20','11/30/2018',1,11,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:13:20','2020-05-31 01:21:32'),
	(531,16,'Nurse - 01 post','<h3>Staff healthcare support</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Work closely with staff and insurance company for both staff health, accident and life insurance provide consultancy on the hospitalization service provider to both staff and insurance company.</li>\r\n<li>Be responsible for the safe administration of medications.</li>\r\n<li>Monitor and administer drugging or other medicines.</li>\r\n<li>Take patient pulses, temperatures, and blood pressures.</li>\r\n<li>Manage First Aid equipment and Nursing room.</li>\r\n<li>Provide pre-care.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Administrative support and reports</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Assess and plan nursing care requirements and develop the day-to-day nursing care.</li>\r\n<li>Send report of new staff and leaving staff to the insurance company weekly or monthly.</li>\r\n<li>Check all medical payment and claims.</li>\r\n<li>Produce report of claim ratio, reject claims, and payment.</li>\r\n<li>Maintain all nursing record accurately and confidentially.</li>\r\n<li>Support employee relations team for reports or other involved tasks.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Health promotion and training</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Research health topic and prepare poster for health campaign and promotion to all staff</li>\r\n<li>Support staff health care activities, eg: Zumba &amp; Yoga, sports&hellip;etc.</li>\r\n<li>Provide staff health care orientation if deemed necessary, eg: First Aid training course.</li>\r\n<li>Be aware of all policies related health and safety especially, Fire prevention, first aid, moving and handling, major accident and waste disposal.</li>\r\n<li>Participate actively in health education program which is brought to share with all staff for health improvement.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Midwife or Nurse Certificate or health equivalent degree.</li>\r\n<li>At least 1 year working experience in nursing or medical.</li>\r\n<li>Have relevant knowledge on nutrition and health care.</li>\r\n<li>Good knowledge or experiences in providing medical consultancy.</li>\r\n<li>Good English communication and computer literate (MS Office).</li>\r\n<li>Good commitment, can work under pressure and ambition to grow.</li>\r\n<li>Be a team player, honest, confidentiality, flexible and patient</li>\r\n</ul>',1,76,15,17,'1','12/07/2018',1,7,7,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:16:19','2020-05-31 02:29:56'),
	(532,16,'Digital Product Owner - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Communicate the vision and collaborate with all related departments: digital technical teams, IT team, Card team, business team to drive development and plan on execution.</li>\r\n<li>Develop detail product; project requirements/ use cases/ user stories for clarity of development scope.</li>\r\n<li>Enforce on Scrum development framework across the development team.</li>\r\n<li>Plan feature releases and manage effective launch to market.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure feature release is of quality and on schedule.</li>\r\n<li>Conduct training to other departments including but not limited to Product Sales and Contact Center.</li>\r\n<li>Document and maintain effective product backlog and related documentation.</li>\r\n<li>Collaborate in R&amp;D activities and the creation of proof of concept of all new initiatives.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>3 plus years of Digital related project management experience.</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of Scrum development framework and other Agile methodologies.</li>\r\n<li>Understands how to effectively lead team, and manage product backlogs as well as release planning.</li>\r\n<li>Quality-oriented mindset, attention to details.</li>\r\n<li>Confident in making and justifying decisions, but flexible enough to change direction based on user feedback, stakeholder needs, and designer/ developer input.</li>\r\n<li>Fluency in English; excellent communication skills, strong interpersonal skills; able to establish and maintain effective and collaborative working relationship.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively under pressure with a high-energy and proactive style.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge/experience with JIRA and Confluence is a plus.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,54,15,17,'1','12/11/2018',1,9,7,5,12,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:20:53','2020-05-31 20:28:01'),
	(533,15,'Head Unit of Independent Credit Review - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Ensure the Independent Credit Review (ICR) activities are run smoothly within business of HKL.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Perform risk analysis in order to set criteria for ICR.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Lead ICR team and conduct ICR to branches, prepare ICR report, and make recommendation for improvement and/or risk prevention.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Lead team to perform collateral evaluation including property and moveable assets, monitor and ensure the up-to-date the collateral price.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Review and make sure the ICR report sent by ICR team are accurate and on time.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Analysis performance and establish report related to ICR achievement.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop and update ICR procedure.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Develop and update collateral guideline.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Coordinate and planning organizing leading and managing the staff under supervision.</span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\">Regular coaching and guide to Independent Credit Review (ICR) team.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Graduate in bachelor of Mathematics, Economics, Finance and Banking, Accounting, Information Technology, Statistics.</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 year experience in field of credit, credit control, credit audit, and/or credit risk.</li>\r\n<li>Good command of English.</li>\r\n<li>Strong analytical skills, and Active and Dynamic.</li>\r\n<li>Good in cpmputer skill on Excel, advance excel and VBA is an advantage.</li>\r\n<li>Good analytical and problem-solving skills</li>\r\n<li>Willing to travel to province.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','11/30/2018',1,9,9,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:29:52','2020-05-30 16:47:07'),
	(534,15,'Team Leader for Independent Risk Champion - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Support to the IRC in delivering the understanding of the line of defense practice in managing the risks.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure all branches of HKL are aware off the IRC implement it as per the business as usual.</li>\r\n<li>Manage staff under unit of Independent Risk Champion.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate and planning organizing leading and controlling the staff under supervision to proactively in IRC.</li>\r\n<li>Maintain the recording mechanism of the report register and database as well as the IRC control plan.</li>\r\n<li>Consolidate of daily report send by IRC&rsquo;s Branches and follow up Branch performance accurately.</li>\r\n<li>Analysis performance and establish report related to IRC achievement.</li>\r\n<li>Regular couching and guide to Independent Risk Champion (IRC) especially, the IRC who has performance need to improve.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Banking &amp; Finance, Business Management or Economic or other related field.</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 years experiences in Banking/financial institution, including some experiences in field of risk management, audit &amp; compliance function would be an advantage.</li>\r\n<li>Sound risk management and analytical skill.</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrable experience with developing or implementing risk management including credit risk and operational risk or related field.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy is a must and excellent communication in English.</li>\r\n<li>Excellent analytical &amp; problem solving skills and willing to work with group &amp; be able to work under pressure.</li>\r\n<li>Good relationships with both internal and external parties.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','11/30/2018',1,7,9,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:31:54','2020-05-30 22:43:53'),
	(535,16,'Software Quality Assurance Tester - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Controls and manages daily test activities.</li>\r\n<li>Assisting developers in creating detailed application test plans.</li>\r\n<li>Perform testing on the products: functional testing, Load testing, exploratory testing, etc.</li>\r\n<li>Analyzing the software&rsquo;s performance against the designer&rsquo;s intentions.</li>\r\n<li>Take ownership of product quality and readiness for every product release</li>\r\n<li>Assists in set-up and maintenance of test lab.</li>\r\n<li>Continuous improvement on the Quality assurance process and tool within the department.</li>\r\n<li>Clear and effective communication of issues to developer or third party.</li>\r\n<li>Provides reports to management as required.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor\'s Degree in computer science</li>\r\n<li>2-3 years of professional experience with QA and Tester role for Mobile or web projects.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of testing process and methodologies.</li>\r\n<li>Experience in reviewing designs, wire-frame, user stories, and software requirements specification.</li>\r\n<li>Excellent oral communication and written documentation skills.</li>\r\n<li>Details oriented and knows how to articulate defects.</li>\r\n<li>Some programming knowledge or experience would be in advantage.</li>\r\n<li>Good time management and self-discipline</li>\r\n<li>Quick ability to learn new systems with minimal documentation.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work independently with minimal guidance</li>\r\n<li>Experience with tools like JIRA.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work with a diverse team and work to develop testing environments and practices.</li>\r\n<li>Strong communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to analyze the complex applications and systems with minimal supervision.</li>\r\n<li>A good standard of English (both written and verbal) is necessary in order to document your findings and communicate them to colleagues.</li>\r\n<li>Strong problem-solving skills to determine the effects on existing and new systems.</li>\r\n<li>Expertise with MS Office products required.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','12/11/2018',1,6,7,5,4,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:33:52','2020-05-30 09:35:22'),
	(536,16,'HR Administrative Officer - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Issue and maintain all letter of internal staff movement, job offer&hellip;, with the accuracy information and comply with the requirements.</li>\r\n<li>Follow up on incomplete documents with relevant stakeholders.</li>\r\n<li>Create data in the system for branch opening, additional position and then employ new comer in the system to make sure on their first day will have user for employment.</li>\r\n<li>Be flexible/ taken action by effective date of user on leave/back from leave in the system and good tracking record to be well managed.&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</li>\r\n<li>Employ in the system for all new staff and change the user of staff movement to be in time and with professional responsibilities.</li>\r\n<li>Consolidate staff\'s OT to be accuracy by making sure it is aligned with labor law/Internal Procedures and also completed on time.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare the internal staff announcement and make sure all internal staff movement data are correct before announcement.</li>\r\n<li>Check all staff\'s leave records to make sure that it is complied with internal rule and labor law.</li>\r\n<li>Maintain and collect all leave records from branches and department to consolidate as monthly basic report.&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</li>\r\n<li>Properly filing of employment documents and checking all employee personal file to make sure it is complied with compliance requirements and labor law.</li>\r\n<li>Well Tracking on&nbsp; new comer to apply National Social Security Fund Member Card with Ministry of Labor.</li>\r\n<li>Weekly providing list of new comer to Security Department for conducting home visit as well as producing the report monthly.&ensp;</li>\r\n<li>Supporting HR Projects such as Recruitment Satisfaction Survey, Uniform,&hellip;etc .&ensp;&ensp;</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring all administrative process for staff on-boarding and off-boarding are completed on time and properly.&ensp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree in Business Administration, Law, Finance, Accounting, HRM or other related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Minimum two years experience in Administration work/HR or other relevant experience.</li>\r\n<li>Good in Computer Literacy (Microsoft Office).</li>\r\n<li>Good in written and communication in English.</li>\r\n<li>Good Knowledge of Cambodian Labor Law and Regulations.</li>\r\n<li>Having negotiation and time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Hight attention to detail and accuracy.</li>\r\n<li>Strongly commitment.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','12/11/2018',1,7,3,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:35:15','2020-05-30 19:10:30'),
	(537,15,'មន្រ្តីគាំទ្រគណនេយ្យ​ (Accounting Support Officer) - ០១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ដោះស្រាយបញ្ហារដែលផ្ញើពីសាខា ទាក់ទងនឹងការចុះប្រតិបត្តិការក្នុងប្រព័ន្ធ និងបញ្ហាប្រតិបត្តិការគណនេយ្យផ្សេងៗទៀត ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រៀបចំទុកដាក់ឯកសារដែលបានដោះស្រាយរួច។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">សម្របសម្រួល និងផ្ញើឯកសារដែលបានដោះស្រាយរួច ឲ្យទៅសាខាសាមីវិញ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ចុះជួយគាំទ្រការងារគណនេយ្យនៅតាមសាខា ដែលទាទាមជំនួយគាំទ្រ។&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ&nbsp;&nbsp; ឬជានិស្សិតឆ្នាំទី៤ ផ្នែកគណនេយ្យ ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ&nbsp;&nbsp; មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់&nbsp; ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់&nbsp; សុភាពរាបសារ និង មានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office (Word &amp; Excel) Internet &amp; Email។</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,17,'1','11/27/2018',1,6,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:39:13','2020-05-31 03:04:16'),
	(538,15,'មន្រ្តីប្រតិបត្តិការគណនេយ្យ (Accounting Transaction Officer) - ០១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យរាល់ប្រតិបត្តិការគណនេយ្យ និងឯកសារតម្រូវ មុនពេលបញ្ចូលក្នុងប្រព័ន្ធ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រៀបចំ Journal Voucher (JV) ដោយមានឯកសារតម្រូវផ្សេងៗ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បញ្ចូលប្រតិបត្តិការគណនេយ្យប្រចាំថ្ងៃទៅក្នុងប្រពន្ធ័ តាមពេលវេលាកំណត់ និងGeneral Ledger (GL) អោយបានត្រឹមត្រូវ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បិទបញ្ជីគណនេយ្យប្រចាំខែអោយបានត្រឹមត្រូវ និងទាន់ពេលវេលា។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ផ្ទៀងផ្ទាត់ និងរៀបសាច់ប្រាក់ប្រចាំថ្ងៃអោយបានត្រឹមត្រូវ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">រៀបចំទុកដាក់ឯកសារប្រតិបត្តិការគណនេយ្យអោយបានត្រឹមត្រូវ។&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ&nbsp;&nbsp; ឬជានិស្សិតឆ្នាំទី៤ ផ្នែកគណនេយ្យ ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ&nbsp;&nbsp; មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់&nbsp; ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់&nbsp; សុភាពរាបសារ និង មានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet MS, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office (Word &amp; Excel) Internet &amp; Email។&nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,17,'1','11/27/2018',1,6,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:41:19','2020-05-31 16:52:58'),
	(539,15,'មន្រ្តីប្រមូលបំណុលយឺតយ៉ាវ (Loan Recovery Officer) - ០៥នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>សិក្សាស្រាវជ្រាវ អំពីស្ថានភាពរស់នៅ និងមូលហេតុនៃបញ្ហា របស់អតិថិជនលើការខកខានមិនបានសងប្រាក់ ។</li>\r\n<li>បែងចែកលំដាប់ថ្នាក់ និងប្រភេទអតិថិជនដែលខកខានសងប្រាក់ឲ្យបានត្រឹមត្រូវ និងច្បាស់លាស់ ដើម្បីកំណត់អាទិភាព ដោះស្រាយបំណុលឥណទានឲ្យមានប្រសិទ្ធភាពខ្ពស់។</li>\r\n<li>ចុះដោះស្រាយបំណុលអតិថិជនដែលខកខានសងប្រាក់ ឲបានគ្រប់គ្រាន់ទៅតាមផែនការ ឬអ្នកគ្រប់គ្រងអាចទទួលយកបាន និងត្រូវធ្វើរបាយការណ៌ជូនអ្នកគ្រប់គ្រង ដើម្បីជួយដោះស្រាយបន្ដឲ្យបានត្រឹមត្រូវ និងទាន់ពេលវេលា ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រួតពិនិត្យរកឲឃើញពីភាពអសកម្មការងាររបស់ខ្លួន ដើម្បីកែលំអនិងបំពេញនូវចំណុចខ្វះខាតឲ្យបានទាន់ពេល ក្នុងគោលបំណងបង្កើនប្រសិទ្ធភាពនៃការអនុវត្ដន៍ការងារជាបន្ដបន្ទាប់ឲ្យបានជោគជ័យ ។</li>\r\n<li>សិក្សា និងអនុវត្ដឲបានល្អតាមគោលការណ៏ និងបទបញ្ជាទាំងឡាយណារបស់សា្ថប័ន។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើកិច្ចការផ្សេងទៀតដែលចាត់ចែងដោយថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង។&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>បព្ចាប់ថ្នាក់ បរិញ្ញាបត្រ ឬកំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់ បរិញ្ញាបត្រឆ្នាំទី៤ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រង ជំនាញទីផ្សារ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ចកម្ម ជំនាញធនាគារ និង ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ, ឫសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតំលៃស្មើ។</li>\r\n<li>មានឆន្ទៈចុះបំពេញការងារនៅតាមមូលដ្ឋាន និងនៅក្នុងដែនគ្រប់គ្រងរបស់សាខា។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឺងមូលដ្ឋានផ្នែកច្បាប់ និង ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រាន់នៅក្នុងការទារបំណុល</li>\r\n<li>មានអត្ដចរិតល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសាមានចិត្តអំណត់ក្នុង ការធ្វើការងារ និង កាយសម្បទាល្អ។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួន។&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>សាខាខេត្តរតនៈគីរី (០១នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកបារាយណ៍-ឃុំបល្ល័ង្គ (០១នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខេត្តបាត់ដំបង (០១នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកទឹកផុស-ឃុំអភិវឌ្ឍន៍ (០១នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកសណ្តាន់-ឃុំសណ្តាន់(០១នាក់)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,8,'5','11/30/2018',1,7,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-11-10 11:45:06','2020-05-31 12:51:23'),
	(540,18,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ២០នាក់','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">ផ្សព្វផ្សាយលក់ផលិតផលឥណទាន ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">ទាក់ទាញអតិថិជន និងពង្រីកតំបន់ប្រតិបត្តិការ ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">ធ្វើការទំនាក់ទំនងអាជ្ញាធរមូលដ្ឋាន ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; color: #333333;\">បញ្ចេញឥណទានជូនអតិថិជនអោយស្របតាមបច្ចេកទេស ។</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; line-height: normal;\"><s