	(576,16,'iOS Developer - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Develop and maintain ABA Bank\'s iOS projects.</li>\r\n<li>Collaborate with the team to define, design and ship new feature Fix existing bugs.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the performance, quality of the application.Write very high quality, efficient and testable software from given requirement.</li>\r\n<li>Doing code review.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare project technical document.</li>\r\n<li>Do R&amp;D on any new / popular (iOS platform related) technologies and tools.</li>\r\n<li>Research on new technologies and tools which can be beneficial to ABA projects.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Experience with third-party libraries and APIs.</li>\r\n<li>Familiar with Restful APIs.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of Apple\'s design principles and interface guidelines.Familiar with continuous integration.Knowledge of Unit Testing.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of architectures MVVM or VIPER.</li>\r\n<li>Solid understanding of the full iOS mobile development life cycle.</li>\r\n<li>Have experience working with Git, Git Flow and other tools such as JIRA, Confluence, Jenkin, code review, etc.</li>\r\n<li>Strong initiative and enthusiasm with mobile technologies and curiousity to learn new things.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','12/25/2018',1,6,7,5,9,'Khmer, English','2018-12-09 08:51:03','2020-05-31 00:57:23'),
	(577,15,'Officer, Credit Risk Control - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Analyst on root cause to loans default</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Perform reassessment of loan assessment process and policy</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Frequency review and suggest for update on credit risk control policy</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Support HKL operation team to reduce loans delinquency&nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Other task assigned by direct supervisor</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Graduate in Bachelor of Finance, Business Administration, or related field</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Understanding of banking and finance industry</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Strong analytical skills</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Computer proficiency </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Flexible to travel and stay overnight including weekends.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','12/12/2018',1,8,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-12-09 08:54:57','2020-05-31 21:21:11'),
	(578,15,'VP & Director of HR Operation & Strategy Department - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Oversee, manage and monitor the compensation and benefits management system/database/structure;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Provide current and perspective employee with information about policies, job duties, working conditions, wages, opportunities for promotion and employment benefits;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Implement and administer the equitable, transparent and efficient Job Grading System in compliance with the established job grading policy, guidelines and procedures;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Develop and revise policy, procedure and form of performance management for effective implementation and manage the whole process of performance management form KPI set up, mid-year review and year-end appraisal by working closely with related departments and offices;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Develop and manage HR Information Management System and develop and execute report as required by management, BoD, investors, and other parties;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Manage employee relation by focus on rules and regulation and disciplinary actions and take care exit interview to improve employee engagement;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Develop creative strategies for communicating across abroad range of stakeholders, employee, leading content, channels and campaigns that engage employee;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Lead, develop, and manage internal employee engagement &amp; communications strategy and execution;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Be responsible for organization structure, job/function scope design;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Lead manpower planning &amp; staff budgeting by working with planning team;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Analyze organizational plans and objective based on the approval MTBP plan by working closely with business and finance team.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Human Resource, Management or other related field</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">At least 3-5 years of hands on HR generalist experience, preferably in areas of HR administration</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">In depth knowledge of compensation &amp; benefits management, total reward management, staff performance management, HR Information system or database, employee relations, employee engagement and communication, organization development and strategic initiative and planning</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Result oriented, good communication and interpersonal skills</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Great service mind and good team player</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Ability to work on multi-task and highly self-motivated</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Computer literacy in MS. Office (Word, Excel, PowerPoint), Internet and Email</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Good command in English</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Be available to travel to province/rural areas</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','12/16/2018',1,6,6,5,12,'Khmer, English','2018-12-09 08:58:13','2020-06-01 05:16:21'),
	(579,16,'Lending Support Officer (SME) - 02 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Supporting Lending Support Manager (LSM) to collect loan proposals and supplementary documents from branches Controlling, reporting and statistics.</li>\r\n<li>Preparing proper loan meeting agendas for designated credit committees.</li>\r\n<li>Preparing approved loan resolutions and its deliveries to branches.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinating for field visiting if needed.</li>\r\n<li>Assisting Lending Support Manager (LSM) with loan processing in Head Office.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor degree of accounting, finance and banking or any related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least one year experience of the relevant duties.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy in Microsoft Officer such as MS. Word, MS. Excel, etc.</li>\r\n<li>High responsible and have integrity manner.</li>\r\n<li>Good writing and communication both in Khmer and English.</li>\r\n<li>Being able to submit tasks before or on deadline.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'2','12/25/2018',1,8,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-12-09 08:59:56','2020-05-31 13:50:09'),
	(580,16,'Loan Reporting Officer - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Prepare NBC reports for lending part according to the guideline of NBC and to ensure timely submission of reports.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare internal management reports and timely submission of reports.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare monthly transaction tickets for adjustment of accrued interest, loan balances, interest in suspense, loan loss provisioning level.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate with IT for timely submission of loan data for CBC upload and make sure for correctness of the data sent to CBC. Coordinate with CBC for further details if required.</li>\r\n<li>Dispute handling with CBC and client if there is mismatch in data between CBC and bank record.</li>\r\n<li>To check for the staff loans and other loans disbursed from head office and arrange all original collateral documents and legal agreements to be kept in the fireproof vault in coordination with Credit Reporting Manager and CCO.</li>\r\n<li>To ensure that the loans of resigned staffs or transferred staffs are properly transferred to other staffs after getting acknowledgement from BM.</li>\r\n<li>To ensure that the loans disbursement both branches and head office are accurately in term of loan reporting and accounting.</li>\r\n<li>To mitigate the fraud of loan disbursement both branches and head office</li>\r\n<li>To check IBSC reports and KPI on quarterly basis and ensure that the scores calculated by IBSC reflects true performance of loan officers. The checking should be done in coordination with Loan Reporting Manager and CCO.</li>\r\n<li>Filing of mortgaged movable assets as collateral to the bank in Filing Office. To monitor for monthly payment of movable asset filing to filing office.</li>\r\n<li>To coordinate with internal and external auditors during audit process.</li>\r\n<li>To work with high ethical standard and to keep all the information related to lending confidential.</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring correctness of all reports prepared for external and internal requirement.</li>\r\n<li>Loan Administrative preparing and management to be concerned from time to time</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in finance and banking, accounting or any related fields</li>\r\n<li>Minimum 1 years experience in loan processing as the term of loan interest accrual, settlement, NPL etc.</li>\r\n<li>Organizational and time management skills</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment</li>\r\n<li>Expertise in Excel and other data management applications</li>\r\n<li>Sound written and verbal communication skills</li>\r\n<li>High ethical and moral standard</li>\r\n<li>High degree of self-motivation and excellent interpersonal skills</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','12/25/2018',1,6,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-12-09 09:01:04','2020-05-30 18:29:03'),
	(581,15,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ៥៧នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">ធ្វើការផ្សាព្វផ្សាយ ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីធីត(</span></span><span class=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333;\">HKL) </span></span><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">ដើម្បីពង្រីកទីផ្សារ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនសក្តានុពល។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">រៀបចំឯកសារឥណទាន ដើម្បីផ្តល់ឥណទានជូនអតិថិជន។</span></span><span class=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333;\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងតាមដានការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">បំពេញការងារផ្សេងៗតាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #0070c0;\"><br /></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">ជាប់បាក់ឌុប ឬ កំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្ររង ឬបរិញ្ញាបត្រលើគ្រប់ជំនាញ ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">មានបទពិសោធន៏ផ្នែកលក់ ឬការផ្សព្វផ្សាយកាន់តែប្រសើ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">រួសរាយរាក់ទាក់ និងការបាស្រ័យទាក់ទងល្អ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈ ក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួននិងអាចបើកបរបាន។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">ផ្នែកគណិតវិទ្យាៈ ការវិភាគ និង គណនា</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">ប្រវត្តិរស់នៅក្នុងសហគមន៍ល្អ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\'; color: #333333;\">ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ៖</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">រាជធានីភ្នំពេញ (២៥នាក់) </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">កំពង់ចាម (២នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">ព្រះសីហនុ (៣នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">កោះកុង (១នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">កណ្តាល (៨នាក់) </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">ក្រចេះ(១នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">មណ្ឌលគិរី (២នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">ត្បូងឃ្មុំ (៣នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">ព្រៃវែង (៥នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">ពោធិ៍សាត់ (២នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">កំពង់ឆ្នាំង (៥នាក់)</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'57','12/25/2018',1,7,3,1,1,'Khmer','2018-12-09 09:05:08','2020-06-01 11:17:23'),
	(582,15,'មន្ត្រីផ្នែកលក់ (Retail Sale Officer) - ១៩នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #333333;\">ដោះស្រាយបាននូវរាល់បញ្ហាដែលនឹងអាចកើតមានឡើង ចំពោះប្រតិបត្តិការ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #333333;\">រៀបចំ និងគ្រប់គ្រងរាល់ឯកសារព័ត៌មានទំនាក់ទំនង ជាមួយអតិថិជន។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #333333;\">រាយការណ៍ពីបាតុភាព និងផលប៉ះពាល់ដល់ផលិតផល និងសេវាកម្មទាំងឡាយ</span></span><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', sans-serif; color: #333333;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #333333;\">មកគណៈគ្រប់គ្រង ឱ្យបានទាន់ពេលច្បាស់លាស់ គ្រប់គ្រាន់ និងត្រឹមត្រូវ។</span></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #333333;\">រៀបចំបាយការណ៍តាមការចាត់ចែងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #0070c0;\"><br /></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #333333;\">បព្ចាប់ថ្នាក់</span></span><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', sans-serif; color: #333333;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; 