amily: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់&nbsp; ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់&nbsp; សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">-&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ </span><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Ms. Office (Ms. Word &amp; Excel) Internet &amp; Email <span lang=\"KHM\">។</span></span></p>',1,39,7,5,'3','12/31/2018',1,5,11,1,1,'Khmer, English','2018-12-18 09:41:40','2020-05-31 10:21:09'),
	(612,16,'Senior Web and Mobile QA Tester - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Controls and manages daily test activities.</li>\r\n<li>Assisting developers in creating detailed application test plans.</li>\r\n<li>Perform testing on the products: functional testing, Load testing, exploratory testing, etc&hellip;</li>\r\n<li>Analyzing the software&rsquo;s performance against the designer&rsquo;s intentions.</li>\r\n<li>Take ownership of product quality and readiness for every product release.</li>\r\n<li>Assists in set-up and maintenance of test lab.</li>\r\n<li>Continuous improvement on the Quality assurance process and tool within the department.</li>\r\n<li>Clear and effective communication of issues to developer or third party.</li>\r\n<li>Provides reports to management as required.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor Degree in Computer Science.</li>\r\n<li>2-3 years of professional experience with QA and tester role for Mobile or web projects.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of testing process and methodologies.</li>\r\n<li>Experience in reviewing designs, wireframe, user stories, and software requirements specification.</li>\r\n<li>Excellent oral communication and written documentation skills.</li>\r\n<li>Details oriented and knows how to articulate defects.</li>\r\n<li>Some programming knowledge or experience would be in advantage.</li>\r\n<li>Good time management and self-discipline.</li>\r\n<li>Quick ability to learn new systems w/ minimal documentation.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work independently with minimal guidance.</li>\r\n<li>Experience with tools like JIRA.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work with a diverse team and work to develop testing environments and practices.</li>\r\n<li>Strong communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to analyze the complex applications and systems with minimal supervision.</li>\r\n<li>A good standard of English (both written and verbal) is necessary in order to document your findings and communicate them to colleagues.</li>\r\n<li>Strong problem solving skills to determine the effects on existing and new systems.</li>\r\n<li>Expertise with MS Office products required.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','01/07/2019',1,7,7,5,4,'Khmer, English','2018-12-24 13:03:27','2020-05-30 23:33:03'),
	(613,15,'Manager, Credit Risk Management - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Assist Credit and Market Risk Management Director to achieve the annual work plans, Department&rsquo;s objectives and HKL&rsquo;s goals.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Perform credit portfolio management and monitoring and stress testing.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Perform credit risk analysis and segment risk analysis and suggest control when necessary.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Perform credit risk identification, assessment and suggest mitigation.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Perform risk assessment on new/changes of credit ;product/service or process flow and suggest mitigation</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Perform portfolio quality analysis, pro-actively or on request, to support operational effectiveness and enhanced portfolio quality.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Analyze on the credit concentration risk, propose and review credit limit exposure.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Manage and execute projects independently from end-to-end; work with cross-functional to deliver on these projects.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Develop statistical credit risk models and credit scorecard</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Build risk culture awareness to all HKL&rsquo;s staff and build capacity of staff under supervision to be able to effectively handle their work efficiently and more independently.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Prepare and verify monthly and quarterly credit risk reports.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Perform relevant tasks as assigned by line management.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Graduate with university degree with background of financial banking, Business Management or Economics.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Highly acquainted with computer systems and programs, such MS Word, MS Excel, MS PowerPoint, Email &amp; Internet and core banking system is advantage.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Highly acquainted with computer systems and programs, such MS Word, Advance MS Excel, VBA, MS PowerPoint, and core banking system is advantage.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Work experience in different areas of bank and financial institution at least 4 years, including 2 years&rsquo; experience of risk management, especially in credit risk management.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">A good understanding of the bank/financial institution&rsquo;s lending policies,&nbsp; procedures, and process, and reasons/events of default.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Proven ability to translate operational and strategic challenges into data driven analysis enabling optimized decision making.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Experience in Statistical model development methodologies or statistical programming language is an advantage.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','12/26/2018',1,7,9,5,13,'Khmer, English','2018-12-24 13:09:49','2020-05-31 06:09:00'),
	(614,15,'Director, Credit and Market Risk Management - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Develop, update, and review risk policies and risk management framework for managing risks within HKL </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Proactively provide suggestion on risk management, identify emerging risks, and advise Senior Management and BoD on appropriate risk management options or controls</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Identify key risks and develop proper strategies to manage in all aspects included business changes and new initiatives</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Manage risk management to be embedded at business operational level as well as to keep all staff aware of risk and manage it as part of their responsibilities</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Calibri Light, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Regular update Senior Management, Risk Management Committee and BoD on risk profile of company through proper report and presentation&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Master&rsquo;s Degree (or any equivalent degree) with background of financial banking, Finance, Accounting, Economics, Statistic, Mathematics, Computer Science</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Highly acquainted with computer systems and programs, such MS Word, Advance MS Excel, VBA, MS PowerPoint; and core banking system is advantage</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Work experience in different areas of bank and financial institution at least 10 years, including 5+ years&rsquo; experience of risk management, especially in credit risk managment.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">A good understanding of the bank/financial institution&rsquo;s lending policies,&nbsp; procedures, and process, and reasons/events of default.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Proven ability to translate operational and strategic challenges into data driven analysis enabling optimized decision making.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Experience in Statistical model development methodologies or statistical programming language is an advantage.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','12/26/2018',1,5,6,9,7,'Khmer, English','2018-12-24 13:14:11','2020-05-31 02:13:56'),
	(615,15,'Head Unit, Support Function Audit - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Perform pre-audit and audit field work for business support functions exclude IT functions</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Review and evaluate adequacy and effectiveness of&nbsp; internal control&nbsp; policies &amp; procedures and workflow process of company/business function</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Provide feedback on risk control matrix, audit program guide and working papers</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Support to subordinates in performing the audit tasks</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Prepare and review the draft audit report of subordinates during field work</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Participate in audit post engagement with Skill manager</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Review staff performance appraisal</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Assist DHAD &amp; Skill manager in performing other tasks.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Bachelor degree in accounting or equivalent degree is required of accounting, Audit, or Finance qualification.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">At least 2 years working experiences in related field.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Knowledge of financial or business analysis, internal control system, organizational structure, works flow and operating procedures.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Demonstrate high level of ethical commitments and trustworthiness.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Advance written and verbal skills with excellent English.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Computer literate in MS Office (Word, MS Excel, Power Point, etc.)</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Be available to travel in rural areas. </span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,77,15,17,'1','12/31/2018',1,4,9,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-12-24 13:17:06','2020-05-30 16:28:04'),
	(616,15,'Customer Service Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Develop and update the customer service and customer complaint policy, procedure, guideline and other related documents.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Manage and follow up the implementation of customer service policy and procedure at branch level.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Manage, consolidate and work with related offices to deal with the customer complaint and suggestion from suggestion box and email. </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Procedure monthly or specific report of follow up the customer service implementation and complaint and suggestion of customer. </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Manage and coordinate to set up QMS at branches and check and solve of its problems.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Manage and support branch to dealt with QMS monthly reports and how to use QMS properly.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Bachelor degree in banking/finance, business, economics, Marketing or other equivalent qualification.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">At least 1 years working experience related to Customer Service.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Strong analytical, decision-making, and problem-solving skills.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Knowledge of customer service principles and practices.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Good interpersonal communication, team work, and result-oriented.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Sound computer literacy, particularly in Word, Excel, Internet, and Email.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Good on both,&nbsp; English writing and speaking.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">High commitment with strong work ethics and integrity.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,57,15,17,'1','12/26/2018',1,4,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-12-24 13:19:46','2020-05-31 21:26:07'),
	(617,16,'Client Service Advisor - 09 posts','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Identify and action on sales opportunity for new business opportunity by responding to inquiries from both new and existing customers.</li>\r\n<li>Provide consultative service in regard to banking products and services which is considered as a good solution to suite the clients&rsquo; needs.</li>\r\n<li>Assist in opening account in system per request from RM or Customers.</li>\r\n<li>Making sure that the documents submitted are accurate and valid.</li>\r\n<li>Take action to follow up in case provided documents are not complete.</li>\r\n<li>Contribute to the development of sound profitable business by creating effective referral networks, including internal business relationship and existing customers in order to achieve the targets.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the compliance with ABA&rsquo;s internal policies, processes &amp; procedure, core values, and code of conducts, etc. are maintained.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in business, finance or marketing field.</li>\r\n<li>Minimum 2 years working experience in sales &amp; marketing.</li>\r\n<li>Negotiation and internal relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Organizational and time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment.</li>\r\n<li>Competent in spoken and written English communication.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy.\r\n<h3>Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Kampot Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Toul kork Branch, Phnom Penh (2 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Operational Hall, Phnom Penh (4 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Sothearos Branch, Phnom Penh (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Toek Thla Branch, Phnom Penh (1 post).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,57,15,9,'9','01/07/2019',1,5,3,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-12-26 07:32:01','2020-05-31 04:36:37'),
	(618,16,'Branch Operations Officer - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Support the process for account opening and validation in system as effective as possible. Making sure documents submitted by front officers are accurate and valid. Take action to follow up in case provided documents are not complete.</li>\r\n<li>Upload the specimen signature form, signed by proper discretionary holder(s) on timely manner.</li>\r\n<li>Contribute to efficient delivery of customer requests, including, issuance of cheques book, cheque activation, bank confirmation (i.e., scheduled account statement printing&hellip;), etc.</li>\r\n<li>Maintain a proper control of sales kits and stock for passbook, FD certificate, blank cheques book, brochures, etc., take action to report and request for the new stock as necessary.</li>\r\n<li>Support and handle complex customer&rsquo;s issues in supporting sales area while executing excellent customer service principles.</li>\r\n<li>Monitor daily account movement in material amount (USD 50K or more) and make necessary reports to DBM/BM.</li>\r\n<li>Work in collaboration with front officers to collect pending fees (i.e., dormant fee) and improve the structure of values account; take action on closure of low value accounts.</li>\r\n<li>Maintains cooperative and productive work atmosphere, including &ldquo;speak-up culture&rdquo; within the branch.</li>\r\n<li>Assist DBM/BM on other operational tasks as assigned by BM/DBMCS.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in business, finance or marketing field.</li>\r\n<li>Minimum 1 year of working experience as an operations officer, customer service-related skills.</li>\r\n<li>Organizational and time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment.</li>\r\n<li>Good internal relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Good written and verbal communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>Attention to details and accuracy.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','01/07/2019',1,5,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-12-26 07:33:35','2020-05-31 18:45:32'),
	(619,15,'Team Leader, Credit Analyst - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Coordinate branch on preparing credit/loan proposal.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Analyze payback ability of loans borrowers.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Identify credit risks as well as suggest corresponding risk mitigations.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Lead, guide, and support a credit analysting team in processing and assessing loan proposal</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Interact with branch staff to solicit and verify borrower&rsquo;s information.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Propose credit decisions and negotiate with branch staff accordingly. </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Liaise with Credit Approval Committee to present loan proposal and respond to query/suggestion from the committee.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Keep track on turnaround time of loan process between branches and Head Office.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Bachelor degree in banking/finance, business, economics, or other equivalent qualification.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">At least 2 years working experience related to credit and/or financial analysis.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Strong analytical, decision-making, and problem-solving skills.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Good understanding and knowledge of microfinance and banking sector.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Good interpersonal communication, team work, and result-oriented.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Sound computer literacy, particularly in Word, Excel, Internet, and Email.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Proficiency in English is a plus advantage.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">High commitment with strong work ethics and integrity.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','12/27/2018',1,3,9,5,2,'Khmer, English','2018-12-26 07:39:32','2020-05-31 05:20:29'),
	(620,15,'មន្រ្តីវិភាគឥណទាន (Credit Analysis Officer) - ០១​នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ពិនិត្យមើលភាពត្រឹមត្រូវ គ្រប់គ្រាន់ និងការអនុលោមទៅតាមគោលការណ៏ឥណទាន និង ជួយសម្រួលក្នុងការបញ្ជូនឯកសារឥណទានទៅកាន់ថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង ដើម្បីធ្វើការអនុម័តហើយបញ្ជូនត្រលប់ទៅកាន់សាខាវិញ។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការវិភាគលើសមត្ថភាពក្នុងការទទួលបានឥណទានរបស់អតិថិជន ដោយពិនិត្យឡើងវិញ លើផែនការអាជីវកម្ម លំហូរសាច់ប្រាក់ របាយការណ៍ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ តារាងតុល្យការ និងលទ្ធភាពក្នុងការសងបំណុល។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំទម្រង់វាយតម្លៃហានិភ័យឥណទានដើម្បីសង្ខេបព័ត៌មានឥណទានដាក់ស្នើទៅនាយកដ្ឋានឥណទានសម្រាប់ធ្វើការអនុម័ត។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការទំនាក់ទំនងទៅកាន់សាខាវិញសម្រាប់ ការឆ្លើយតបណាមួយរបស់គណៈកម្មាធិកាឥណទានដើម្បីធ្វើឱ្យមានភាពច្បាស់លាស់ទៅលើពត៌មាន និង លក្ខខណ្ឌនានា។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើរបាយការណ៍ជាប្រចាំ ពីសំណើរឥណទានដែលទទួលការអនុម័តរឺមិនទាន់បានអនុម័ត និង រាយការណ៍ទៅកាន់ប្រធានផ្នែកវិភាគឥណទាន និងរៀបចំឯកសារតាមលំដាប់លំដោយ ឲ្យបានត្រឹមត្រូវ។</li>\r\n<li>ពិនិត្យឡើងវិញនៃគោលការណ៍ឥណទាន នីតិវិធី និងវិសោធនកម្មដែលពាក់ព័ន្ធទៅ និងការទទួលខុសត្រូវប្រចាំថ្ងៃរបស់ខ្លួនដើម្បីធ្វើឱ្យប្រាកដថាគោលការណ៏និង ស្របទៅតាមបច្ចុប្បន្នភាព។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>ជានិសិ្សតកំពុងសិក្សា ឬ បញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ ផ្នែកគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ជកម្ម ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬសញ្ញាប័ត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍យ៉ាងតិច មួយឆ្នាំ ក្នុងការផ្តល់ឥណទាន និងវិភាគឥណទាន។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office (Ms. Word &amp; Excel) Internet &amp; Email</li>\r\n<li>មានការទំនាក់ទំនងល្អក្នុងការធ្វើការជាក្រុម និងមានជំនាញក្នុងការវិភាគ។</li>\r\n<li>មានអត្តចរិកល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','12/27/2018',1,4,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2018-12-26 07:43:16','2020-05-30 18:03:42'),
	(621,16,'Client Acquisition Officer - 02 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Make customer presentations and Identify sales opportunity for new business for new customers.</li>\r\n<li>Contribute to the development of sound profitable business by continuing on-board new customers and increasing the customer&rsquo;s portfolio.</li>\r\n<li>Agree challenging daily, weekly, and monthly targets for yourself with your branch manager/ head of department. Regularly evaluate these targets &ndash; when results fall short of target, understand why and agree what to do differently to improve performance with your line manager.</li>\r\n<li>Keep up to day with ABA&rsquo;s products suite and marketing campaigns to ensure superior product knowledge.</li>\r\n<li>Develop and implement effective customer retention strategies.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Excellent customer services skills.</li>\r\n<li>Time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment.</li>\r\n<li>Sales, negotiation and relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Sound written and verbal communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>High degree of self-motivation.</li>\r\n<li>Very good interpersonal skills.</li>\r\n<li>Complaint resolving.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy.\r\n<h3>Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Takhmao Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Bavet Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,54,15,25,'2','01/07/2019',1,5,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-12-26 07:46:04','2020-05-31 02:29:05'),
	(622,16,'Deputy Branch Manager - 03 posts','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Ensuring staffs in at the branch level meet/exceed customer expectations through superior customer service, including achievement of serving time targets for both telling and sales areas.</li>\r\n<li>Contributing to the development of sound profitable business by creating effective referral networks, including internal business relationship, and other local marketing activities.</li>\r\n<li>Driving the sales and service team to marketing products to increase the public awareness of the branch, products and services to increase public&rsquo;s trust to the branch.</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring key accounts of the branch are well serviced; immediately report to direct manager in case any potential loss of key account is observed.</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring that all policies and procedures are followed by staff members and forms are ready-to-service and put in order.</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring all staff have a good appearance and are in uniform daily. Further, ensuring that the service standards of ABA Bank have been fully followed by branch&rsquo;s staffs.</li>\r\n<li>Providing induction training for new comer, regular feedback, encouragement and maintain open communication at workplace.</li>\r\n<li>Arranging staff training needs by working with the relevant Departments and ensuring /encouraging staff to attend.</li>\r\n<li>Agree challenging targets for yourself with direct manager. Regularly evaluate these targets &ndash; when results fall short of targets, understand why and agree what to do differently to improve performance.</li>\r\n<li>Keep a close eye on your local competitors &ndash; what they do and how they perform. And,inform to direct manager</li>\r\n<li>Keep up to day with ABA&rsquo;s products and marketing campaigns to ensure superior services provided to clients.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Organizational and time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment.</li>\r\n<li>Sound sales and negotiation skills.</li>\r\n<li>Sound written and verbal communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>Experience in managing a team work and portfolio of business customers.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of economic climate and impact of country factors on customer&rsquo;s business as well as the bank.</li>\r\n<li>High degree of self-motivation and excellent interpersonal skills.\r\n<h3>Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Tboung khmum Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Pursat Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Memot District Branch (1 post).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,27,'3','01/07/2019',1,4,6,5,9,'Khmer, English','2018-12-26 07:47:58','2020-05-31 05:25:18'),
	(623,15,'Manager, Corporate Compliance - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Review on announcement/documents before released to public as assure the transparency and no missed lead of communication; </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Prepare annual AML assessment per group and regulatory requirement; </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Support and review criteria on AML/CFT monitoring base on change in market trend and group requirement; </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Advise and train to company staff on implementation regards code of conduct, anti-corruption policy and AML;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Initiate the discussion among team on the matter identified from team; </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Enhance internal process and support on new initiatives which related to core task of corporate compliance</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Review of AML report from team and consolidate&nbsp; monthly report; </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Ensure follow up of AML critical issues and escalate accordingly;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Liaise regularly with numerous stakeholder but not limit to front office, other business units, IT Assist with ad-hoc requests;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Some travel required.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Bachelor degree in Finance/Banking or related studies;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">At least 3-years experienced in compliance; </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Understanding principle of banking and FI products;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Knowledge of due diligence and local money laundering requirement </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Demonstrate aware AML/CFT requirement </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Understand principles of banking operation, and banking code</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Excellent verbal, presentation and written communication</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Computer literacy required (Excel, Words, PowerPoint) </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Integrity and understand&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'1','12/31/2018',1,3,9,5,12,'Khmer, English','2018-12-26 07:53:06','2020-06-01 12:52:10'),
	(624,15,'Deputy Director, Credit Underwriting Department - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Manage credit underwriting team and monitor underwriting process.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Review and approve small, medium- and SME-loan proposal.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Undertake strategic initiatives to improve the speed and comprehensiveness of credit origination process.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Review credit approval authority of branch managers.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Oversee credit risk profile and implement appropriate mitigating measures.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Participate in due diligence process and liaise with lender/ investor.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Participate in designing and developing new credit products to meet the market demand.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Co-develop Industry papers to improve credit assessment standard.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Review credit policy, procedures, and manual to comply with local/ international regulation and competitive environment.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Ensure that credit policy, procedure and manual are strictly adhered by staff and branch office.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Design and conduct training for credit analyst and other relevant staff.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">MBA degree in banking/finance, business, economics, or other equivalent qualification</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">At least 4 years working experience related to credit and/or financial analysis</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Energetic, detailed oriented, able to adhere deadlines on a timely manner.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Strong analytical, decision-making, and problem-solving skills</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Good understanding and knowledge of microfinance and banking sector</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Good interpersonal communication, team work, and result-oriented</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Sound computer literacy, particularly in Word, Excel, Internet, and Email</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Proficiency in English is a plus advantage</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">High commitment with strong work ethics and integrity</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','12/31/2018',1,4,9,5,13,'Khmer, English','2018-12-26 07:56:45','2020-05-31 06:33:19'),
	(625,16,'Application Development Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Analysis of options available for development and discussing them with the team.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare or create data environment if necessary to support the process of development.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare of development plans for received requests.</li>\r\n<li>Develop of applications and reports based on requests from each department by using PL/SQL code.</li>\r\n<li>Testing developed apps and reports involving department users (UAT).&ensp;</li>\r\n<li>Prepare list of developed apps and reports with status of development.&ensp;&ensp;</li>\r\n<li>Prepare of user manuals and handling over to respective support teams and documentation of processes of development.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other tasks which will assigned by line manager.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Information Technology or Computer Science.</li>\r\n<li>Must have experience in application or report development/customization; NET/SQL/PLSQL experience.</li>\r\n<li>Good Knowledge of JavaScript, JQuery, HTML, HTML5, CSS, CSS3, Responsive Design, Web Programming Skills, Web User Interface Design (UI), Web Application Development Frameworks.</li>\r\n<li>Must have experience working with function, procedure, package and have a good understanding of OOP.</li>\r\n<li>Willing to research/learn new technology.</li>\r\n<li>Be flexible, honest and punctual.</li>\r\n<li>Willing to work as a team.</li>\r\n<li>Good communication skills in Khmer and in English.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','01/21/2019',1,7,7,5,9,'English','2018-12-30 09:29:43','2020-05-30 18:24:41'),
	(626,19,'មន្រ្តីទទួលប្រាក់ហាត់ការ (Office Teller Trainee) - 04 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>ប្រើប្រព័ន្ធ​ Daily Teller-based system ដើម្បីបិទប្រតិបត្តិការសាច់ប្រាក់ប្រចាំថ្ងៃ ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវផ្តល់ព័ត៌មានដល់អតិថិជនដែលមានទំនាក់ទំនងសេវាកម្មក្រេឌីត (ទោះបីអតិថិជនចាស់ ឬថ្មី) និងគារវកិច្ចស្វាគមន៍ក្នុងពួកគាត់ក្នុងលក្ខណៈរួសរាយ ច្បាស់លាស់ត្រឹមត្រូវ និងប្រាកដប្រជា ហើយត្រូវមានគំនិតគិតថាគឺពួកគាត់ជាប្រភពចំណូលដែលមិនចេះរីងស្ងួតរ​បស់ក្រេឌីតយើង ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវពន្យល់ពីផលិតផលសេវាកម្មក្រេឌីតដល់អតិថិជនក្នុងភាពច្បាស់លាស់ និងត្រឹមត្រូវតាមគោលការណ៍របស់ក្រេឌីត ។</li>\r\n<li>ជួយបង្កលក្ខណៈងាយស្រួលដល់អតិថិជនដែលមកបើកគណនីសន្សំជាមួយក្រេឌីតដូចជាជួយអតិថិជនក្នុងការបំពេញទំរង់ឯកសារឱ្យបានត្រឹមត្រូវ ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវដោះស្រាយបញ្ហាជាមួយអតិថិជនជាមួយលក្ខណៈទន់ភ្លន់ និងមិនត្រូវប្រើពាក្យអសុរស់ជាមួយអតិថិជន ឬឈ្លោះទាស់ទែងជាមួយអតិថិជន ។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើ Cash Advance ពីប្រធានមន្រ្តីទទួលប្រាក់សំរាប់ទុកបញ្ចេញទុន ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវត្រួតពិនិត្យមើលរាល់ការវិភាគសងប្រចាំថ្ងៃដែលនៅក្រោមការគ្រប់គ្រងរបស់ខ្លួន ហើយត្រូវជូនដំណឹងទៅប្រធានមន្រ្តីឥណទាន ឬក៏ប្រធានអនុសាខាអំពីអតិថិជនដែលបង់យឺត ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវទទួល និងត្រួតពិនិត្យការដាក់ប្រាក់ចូលរបស់មន្រ្តីទទួលប្រាក់នៅសហគមន៍ និងអតិថិជន ។</li>\r\n<li>ប្រមូលព័ត៌មាននានាអំពីអតិថិជនទាក់ទង និងផលិតផលសេវាកម្ម និងទំនាក់ទំនងរបស់ក្រេឌីត ហើយរាយការណ៍ជូនប្រធានគ្រប់គ្រង ។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>មានបរិញ្ញាបត្រ (ឆ្នាំទី២ ឆមាសទី១ឡើងទៅ) ផ្នែកទីផ្សារ គ្រប់គ្រង គណនេយ្យ ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ រឺសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតំលៃស្មើ</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ត្រួតពិនិត្យរូបិយប័ណ្ណ</li>\r\n<li>មានជំនាញក្នុងការប្រាស្រ័យទាក់ទងទាំងមជ្ឈដ្ឋានខាងក្នុង និងមជ្ឈដ្ឋានខាងក្រៅ</li>\r\n<li>មានចិត្តអត់ធ្មត់ និងស្រលាញ់ការងារដែលគ្រឹះស្ថានបានប្រគល់អោយហើយមានឆន្ទៈធ្វើការច្រើនម៉ោងក្នុងមួយថ្ងៃ និងមានចិត្តចង់បម្រើអតិថិជនក្រីក្រដែលក្រេឌីតកំពុងបំរើសេវាកម្ម</li>\r\n<li>មានភាពវាងវៃក្នុងការដោះស្រាយបញ្ហា</li>\r\n<li>ស្ទាត់ជំនាញក្នុងការប្រើប្រាស់កម្មវិធី Microsoft Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Internet and Email</li>\r\n<li>អាចប្រើប្រាស់ភាសាអង់គ្លេសបានមធ្យម</li>\r\n<li>ពូកែខាងគណិតវិទ្យា និងគណនេយ្យ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ទីតាំងត្រូវបំរើការងារ៖</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>ប៉ោយប៉ែត (១នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ក្រុងព្រះសីហនុ (៣នាក់)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,18,'4','01/28/2019',1,7,3,5,8,'English','2018-12-30 09:59:51','2020-05-30 05:05:08'),
	(627,20,'មន្រ្តីសវនកម្មផ្ទៃក្នុងជាន់ខ្ពស់_តាមតំបន់ (Senior, Internal Audit Officer-by Region) - 02 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>ចុះធ្វើសវនកម្មក្នុងកម្រិតសាខាដូចជា៖ ១. ចុះត្រួតពិនិត្យសំណុំឯកសារឥណទានទាំងអស់ ២. ចុះពិនិត្យភ្លាមៗដោយមិនមានការជូនការជូនដំណឹងទៅលើសុវត្ថិភាពសាច់ប្រាក់ និងលំហូរសាច់ប្រាក់ (សាច់ប្រាក់ចូល សាច់ប្រាក់ចេញ ចំណាយ ការរក្សាទុកសាច់ប្រាក់ សាច់ប្រាក់ក្នុងធនាគារ និងការដឹកជញ្ជូនសាច់ប្រាក់...) ៣. ត្រួតពិនិត្យសន្តិសុខ និងសុវត្ថិភាពរបស់សាខា ។</li>\r\n<li>តាមដានការអនុវត្ដអនុសាសន៍មុនៗដែលផ្តល់ដោយនាយកដ្ឋានគ្រប់គ្រងហានិភ័យ និងប្រតិបត្តិតាម​ និងនាយកដ្ឋានសវនកម្មផ្ទៃក្នុង ។</li>\r\n<li>ចូលរួមជាមួយកិច្ចការចុះធ្វើសវនកម្មរបស់ក្រុមការងារសវនកម្មស្នាក់ការកណ្តាល ។</li>\r\n<li>ស៊ើបអង្កេតរកការកៃបន្លំក្នុងសាខាដែលខ្លួនទទួលខុសត្រូវ ។</li>\r\n<li>សម្របសម្រួលការប្រជុំជាមួយថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង និងធ្វើបទបង្ហាញពីការរកឃើញកំហុស និងផ្តល់អនុសាសន៍កែតម្រូវ ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំរបាយការណ៍សវនកម្មផ្ទៃក្នុង ហើយផ្ញើទៅកាន់ប្រធានផ្នែកសវនកម្មផ្ទៃក្នុង និងគណៈគ្រប់គ្រង ។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>មានសញ្ញាបត្រ ជំនាញផ្នែកធនាគារ ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ គណនេយ្យ គ្រប់គ្រងអាជីវកម្ម ឬជំនាញផ្នែកសវនកម្ម</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ផ្នែកសវនកម្មលើផ្នែកគណនេយ្យ និងសវនកម្មផ្ទៃក្នុងចាប់ពី២ឆ្នាំឡើងទៅ</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវមានជំនាញវិភាគ ជំនាញក្នុងការទំនាក់ទំនង ការគ្រប់គ្រងពេលវេលា ការសិក្សាស្រាវជ្រាវ និងជំនាញក្នុងការទំនាក់ទំនងផ្សេងៗ</li>\r\n<li>យកចិត្តទុកដាក់លើការងារ មានភាពច្បាស់លាស់ និងមានការប្តេជ្ញាចិត្តខ្ពស់ក្នុងការចុះតាមមូលដ្ឋាន</li>\r\n<li>បុគ្គលិកមានភាពជាម្ចាស់ការលើខ្លួនឯង និងអាចធ្វើការឯករាជ្យបាន</li>\r\n<li>អាចទៅធ្វើការតាមបណ្តាខេត្តដែលនាយកដ្ឋានសវនកម្មចាត់តាំង</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ទីតាំងជ្រើសរើស៖</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>ខេត្តតាកែវ (១នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តកំពង់ចា​ម (១នាក់)</li>\r\n</ol>',1,77,15,5,'2','01/02/2019',1,5,3,5,2,'English','2018-12-30 10:19:35','2020-05-30 08:21:54'),
	(628,16,'Credit Operation Officer - 5 posts','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Managing delivery of email correspondence from branches to team members.</li>\r\n<li>Leading disbursement team members to perform their daily transactions efficiently.</li>\r\n<li>Ensuring completion of legal documents and its supportive papers before implementing loan operation in system etc.</li>\r\n<li>Compiling refinanced loans and related reports in a proper databases.</li>\r\n<li>Authorizing and maintaining correspondence between branches and loan disbursement team i.e. loan release, loan amendments, loan disbursement etc.</li>\r\n<li>Informing branches of loan documents\' errors for rectification subject to individual permitted loan limit.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Having bachelor degree of banking fields or IT related degree.</li>\r\n<li>Having experience of the relevant job would be an advance.</li>\r\n<li>Holding computer skills i.e. MS Word and Excel and other applications</li>\r\n<li>Having good personality.</li>\r\n<li>Being able to communicate and write in both English and Khmer.</li>\r\n<li>Being able to work under pressure.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'5','01/21/2019',1,6,3,5,9,'English','2018-12-30 10:22:10','2020-05-31 03:23:52'),
	(629,34,'Legal Internship - 02 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Assist in preparing monthly report on license management, Branch Manager Relocation, Patent, Branch relocation.</li>\r\n<li>Following up court case and monthly reporting.</li>\r\n<li>Review and develop the contract to be in line with international laws &amp; best practice as well as national laws &amp; regulations.</li>\r\n<li>Check and verify the legality of the documents of the companies from different jurisdictions to make sure they are completed, acceptable and compliant with local laws and regulations before signing contract.</li>\r\n<li>Provide support and legal advice on the banking practice.</li>\r\n<li>Manage and update, on the timely basis, the essential reporting task.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Good communication &amp; good presentation skill</li>\r\n<li>Good interpersonal skills</li>\r\n<li>Honest, Integrity, and professional</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of regulatory industry</li>\r\n<li>Good command of English and Khmer, for both writing and speaking.</li>\r\n<li>At least 3<sup>rd</sup> year in Law</li>\r\n</ul>',1,39,15,17,'2','01/14/2019',1,7,2,5,1,'English','2018-12-30 10:25:16','2020-05-29 13:33:41'),
	(630,16,'Teller Supervisor - 01 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Ensure accurate and efficient teller transactions are offered with professionalism.</li>\r\n<li>Give clear instruction and guidance to subordinates.</li>\r\n<li>Check the daily cash count with teller and briefly report to branch manager/chief of cash operation department.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that security and operational guidelines are followed by the teller staff.</li>\r\n<li>Recognize opportunities to recommend bank\'s products and services and refer customers to appropriate staff members.</li>\r\n<li>Supervise tellers with continuous coaching, training and mentoring, particularly about counterfeit note, etc.</li>\r\n<li>Inspire and motivate team work.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in finance and banking, accounting or any related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least 3 years experience in teller or any related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Good communication and organizational skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work in a team environment.</li>\r\n<li>Negotiation and internal relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of basic banking products and services.</li>\r\n<li>Practical knowledge of operational risk and compliance with policies and procedures applied in banking industry.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy.</li>\r\n<li>Good command in English.</li>\r\n<li>Attention to details and accuracy.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,17,'1','12/21/2018',1,6,3,5,12,'English','2018-12-30 10:33:52','2020-05-30 11:04:11'),
	(631,15,'មន្រ្តីដោះស្រាយវិវាទ (Litigation Officer)​​ - ០១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ទទួលបន្ទុកដោះស្រាយវិវាទទាំងឡាយដែលទាក់ទងនឹងផ្លូវច្បាប់របស់ ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីតធីត នៅក្នុង និងក្រៅប្រព័ន្ធតុលាការ។</li>\r\n<li>ប្រឹក្សាយោបល់ផ្នែកច្បាប់ដល់បុគ្គលិក និងថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីតធីត នៅ ពេលមានការស្នើសុំ។</li>\r\n<li>ពិនិត្យ និងតាមដាននូវរាល់វិវាទទាំងឡាយដែលមាននៅក្នុង និងក្រៅប្រព័ន្ធតុលាការ ដែលពាក់ព័ន្ធជាមួយ ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីតធីត និងរៀបចំរបាយការណ៍ជូនថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n<li>ទំនាក់ទំនង និងសម្របសម្រួលជាមួយស្ថាប័នតុលាការ មេធាវី អាជ្ញាធរ និងភាគី ពាក់ព័ន្ធដើម្បីដោះស្រាយវិវាទទាំងឡាយដែលកើតមាន។</li>\r\n<li>ស្រាវជ្រាវ ចងក្រង និងអភិវឌ្ឍកិច្ចការផ្នែកដោះស្រាយវិវាទ ជាពិសេសទាក់ទងនឹងវិស័យ ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ និងធនាគារឱ្យទាន់សម័យ ដើម្បីទទួលបាននូវគំនិតថ្មីស្របតាមតម្រូវការរបស់ ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីតធីត។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>បញ្ចប់ ឬកំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញបត្រផ្នែកនីតិសាស្រ្ត ឬជំនាញប្រហាក់ប្រហែល។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងផ្នែកក្រមរដ្ឋប្បវេណី ក្រមព្រហ្មទណ្ឌ ច្បាប់ ពាណិជ្ជកម្ម ច្បាប់ការងារ និងក្រមនីតិវិធី។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ផ្នែកច្បាប់ក្នុងវិស័យធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹង ឬមានបទពិសោធន៍ទាក់ទងនឹងការចរចា ការសម្របសម្រួន និងការដោះស្រាយវិវាទតាមផ្លូវតុលាការ និងក្រៅប្រព័ន្ធតុលាការ។</li>\r\n<li>និយាយ និងសរសេរភាសាអង់គ្លេសបានល្អ និងចេះប្រើប្រាស់កុំព្យូទ័រ&nbsp; Word, Excel និង Power Point។</li>\r\n<li>ជំនាញក្នុងការប្រាស្រ័យទាក់ទងល្អ និងអាចចុះខេត្តបាន។</li>\r\n</ul>',1,68,15,17,'1','01/10/2019',1,7,3,5,9,'Khmer, English','2018-12-30 10:36:57','2020-05-30 16:33:41'),
	(632,19,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) និង មន្រ្តីឥណទានហាត់ការ (Credit Officer Trainee) - ១២៥នាក់','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 13.3333px;\">ចុះផ្សព្វផ្សាយពីផលិតផល (ឥណទាន និងប្រាក់សន្សំ) របស់ក្រេឌីតទៅក្នុងសហគមន៍ ។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 13.3333px;\">បង្រៀនរាល់សេវាកម្មរបស់ក្រេឌីតអោយអស់ពីសមត្ថភាព និងលទ្ធភាពទៅតាមគោលការណ៍ឥណទាន គោលការណ៍ប្រាក់សន្សំ និងការអប់រំ ឬការផ្តល់បទពិសោធន៍មុខជំនួញ ដើម្បីអោយពួកគាត់ចូលរួមជាមួយក្រេឌីត ។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 13.3333px;\">វាយតំលៃជ្រើសរើសអតិថិជនដែលមានសក្តានុពលដើម្បីផ្តល់ប្រាក់កម្ចី ។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; font-size: 13.3333px;\">ទទួលខុសត្រូវទៅលើការប្រមូលប្រាក់សងត្រលប់របស់អតិថិជន​ និងដោះស្រាយទុនខូច ។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: borde