	(644,16,'Relationship Manager - 05 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Make customer presentations and identify &amp; action sales opportunity for new business from both new and existing customer.</li>\r\n<li>Contribute to the development of sound profitable business by creating effective referral networks, including internal business relationship, existing customer and local market activities</li>\r\n<li>Agree challenging daily, weekly, and monthly referral targets for yourself with your branch manager/ Head of Department. Regularly evaluate these targets &ndash; when results fall short of target, understand why and agree what to do differently to improve performance with your line manager.</li>\r\n<li>Keep up to day with ABA&rsquo;s products suite and marketing campaigns to ensure superior product knowledge.</li>\r\n<li>Develop and implement effective customer retention strategies</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Excellent customer services skills.</li>\r\n<li>Time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment.</li>\r\n<li>Sales, negotiation and relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Sound written and verbal communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>High degree of self-motivation.</li>\r\n<li>Very good interpersonal skills.</li>\r\n<li>Complaint resolving.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy.\r\n<h3>Location</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Takhmao Branch (2 posts).</li>\r\n<li>Chom Chao Branch, Phnom Penh (1 post).</li>\r\n<li>Mao Tse Tung Branch, Phnom Penh (2 posts).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,57,15,10,'5','01/21/2019',1,4,9,5,9,'English','2018-12-30 11:38:39','2020-05-31 00:16:06'),
	(645,15,'Manager, Insurance Product - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Delivery the insurance products line accordance with the company&rsquo;s strategy within the estimate timeframe.&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Develop the sale strategies and implement to the market.</li>\r\n<li>Regularly conduct market research and analysis to understand implications and identify new opportunities in line with institute\'s strategies and expansion plans.&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Manage and monitor insurance team performance via good team work, motivation and coaching for high productivity and critical understanding.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure end-to-end management of products and campaigns across channels.</li>\r\n<li>Co-ordinate with key internal and external stakeholder groups, including existing clients to continuously growing of insurance business.</li>\r\n<li>Deliver product governance and control such as partner\'s due diligence, product program review, business agreements, and service level agreements.</li>\r\n<li>Analyzes cost &amp; benefit of insurance products, marketing or sale activities</li>\r\n<li>Prepares the budget plan projections for insurance product launch, sale or marketing campaign</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor or Master Degree in banking/finance or business management, or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least 03 year experience in consumer banking, insurance or financial services industry.</li>\r\n<li>Prior insurance experience preferred.</li>\r\n<li>Extensive knowledge in insurance, strong analytical, quantitative, problem solving,</li>\r\n<li>Be a communication, presentation, relationship management, project management skill.</li>\r\n<li>Be proficient in English both speaking and writing.</li>\r\n<li>Be Innovative, dynamic and confident.</li>\r\n<li>Be well time management.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,54,15,17,'1','01/20/2019',1,6,9,5,12,'English','2018-12-30 11:41:30','2020-05-29 18:08:46'),
	(646,15,'Deputy Director, Learning & Development Department - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Contribute in developing annual training plan and budget for HKL staff</li>\r\n<li>Develop effective training curriculum including on campuse and distance learning respecting L&amp;D strategic direction</li>\r\n<li>Take lead and assist Department Director in developing Leadership Development, Succession Planning, and Career Development programs</li>\r\n<li>Assisting Department Director to ensure quality and sucess of all aspects of five-core L&amp;D programs</li>\r\n<li>Manage department policy, procedure, manuals, and guidelines</li>\r\n<li>Provide technical assistance and performance feedback to trainers</li>\r\n<li>Maintain good relationship with cross departments and stakeholders</li>\r\n<li>Source for external training providers to hold required courses Provide requalr report and presentation to Senior Management Team</li>\r\n<li>Other task as required</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Master degree in business or related fields</li>\r\n<li>Specialized in Pedagogy or knowledge and experience in learning needs analysis and curriculum development</li>\r\n<li>Solid knowledge and experience in MFI or bank is preferable</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge and experience in staff leadership development and succession planning is preferable.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy in MS Word, MS Excel, PowerPoint, Internet and E-mail</li>\r\n<li>Good moral and interpersonal communication</li>\r\n<li>Fluency in both written and spoken English.</li>\r\n<li>Be available to travel to rural areas.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','01/20/2019',1,7,9,9,9,'English','2018-12-30 11:45:31','2020-06-01 04:08:02'),
	(647,15,'Senior Officer, Human Resource Organization Development - 01 post','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Collaborate and partner with HR team to ensure HR strategies are aligned and integrated with HR direction;</li>\r\n<li>Accountable for the day to day performance of the Organizational Development (OD);</li>\r\n<li>Support with leadership development, succession planning and talent management to make sure we have someone ready to take over the position if someone leave or new senior position made available;</li>\r\n<li>Design and develop different policies, manuals, guideline and other materials including handouts and visual aids related to HRD;</li>\r\n<li>Assist Head of Human Resource for organization structure design, job/function scope design;</li>\r\n<li>Represent HR to lead manpower planning and staff budgeting plan by working closely with Financial Planning team and other related teams;</li>\r\n<li>Identify and evaluate HR initiatives to ascertain appropriate programs that meet company goals;</li>\r\n<li>Lead and facilitate exit interview process and see whether exited staff is suitable for other position within the company by working closely with other functional department;</li>\r\n<li>Assist Head of Human Resource to develop and design the career path development and management program;</li>\r\n<li>Contributes in the design and implementation of the HR internal communication process, ensure its effectiveness;</li>\r\n<li>Develop other adhoc report as required by management;</li>\r\n<li>Handle and perform other tasks as assigned by direct supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Bachelor degree in Human Resource, Management, Political science, Psychology or related field<br /></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Good command in English language skills<br /></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">At least 2-3 years of experience in HR domain<br /></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Age above 28 years old<br /></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Good analytical skill, systematic thinking, problem solving decision making and managerial skills<br /></span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">A team player with excellent interpersonal skill and able to lead team to achieve business target<br /></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri Light\', sans-serif;\">Computer literacy in MS. Office (workable)</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','01/20/2019',1,3,3,5,4,'English','2018-12-30 11:48:16','2020-05-30 06:40:59'),
	(648,16,'Accounting and Administrative Officer - 02 post','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Handle monthly budget.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare ticket advance.</li>\r\n<li>Handle leave form of all staff.</li>\r\n<li>Manage stationery and supplies.</li>\r\n<li>Keep letter in/out.</li>\r\n<li>Collect all assets from staff resigned.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare Fixed Assets.</li>\r\n<li>Handle emergency demand.</li>\r\n<li>Check voucher from operation department.</li>\r\n<li>Prepared voucher in order for accounting department.</li>\r\n<li>Prepared Cash record and verify with chief of teller.</li>\r\n<li>Daily report: Deposit, Other Transaction review, cash reconciliation, customer report, general information.</li>\r\n<li>Monthly performance report: income detail, deposit portfolio and loan portfolio.</li>\r\n<li>New account opened during the month and outstanding balance by end of Month Report.</li>\r\n<li>Do financial report: profit and loss statement, balance sheet, and summary report.</li>\r\n<li>Handle some tasks from Branch Manager when he/she was absent.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in finance/accounting or any related field.</li>\r\n<li>Must have 1 year experience related to accounting, finance or admin job.</li>\r\n<li>Strong in communication skill.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment.</li>\r\n<li>Good command in Khmer and English.</li>\r\n<li>Computer skills in word, excel, internet &amp; e-mail.\r\n<h3>Locations</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Kien Svay District Branch (1post)</li>\r\n<li>Siem Reap Branch (1 post)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,23,'2','01/28/2019',1,5,3,5,11,'English','2018-12-30 11:50:55','2020-05-31 18:41:57'),
	(649,20,'ប្រធានក្រុមឥណទាន (Credit Supervisor) - ០១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ត្រួតពិនិត្យវាយតម្លៃ កម្ចីដល់ទីតាំងអតិថិជនផ្ទាល់ និងឯកសារកម្ចី ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងធ្វើផែនការ ប្រចាំឆ្នាំ ប្រចាំខែ សប្តាហ័ របស់បុគ្គលិក ។</li>\r\n<li>សិក្សា វាយតំលៃ ប្រមូលព័ត៌មាន នៃតំបន់​ប្រតិបត្តិការសក្តានុពលតំបន់គោល ឥរិយាបទអតិថិជន មុខរបរ ស្ថានភាពសេដ្ឋកិច្ច ស្ថានភាពប្រវត្តិឥណទាន ស្ថានភាពដីធ្លី ហេដ្ឋារចនាសម្ពន្ធ័ យុទ្ធសាស្រ្ត និងផលិតផលរបស់គូរប្រកួតប្រជែង ។</li>\r\n<li>គ្រប់គ្រងគុណភាពផលប័ត្រកម្ចី និងចូលរួមដោះស្រាយកម្ចីយឺតយ៉ាវ ឬស្ថិតក្នុងហានិភ័យឱ្យបានទាន់ពេល និងរាយការណ៍ជូននាយកសាខា ។</li>\r\n<li>ថែរក្សាអតិថិជន ចំណែកទីផ្សារ និងសេវាកម្មល្អ តាមរយៈការដោះស្រាយបណ្តឹងអតិថិជនឱ្យទាន់ពេលវេលា ។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>មានកម្រិតបរិញ្ញាបត្រជំនាញធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬពាណិជ្ជកម្មមានលក្ខណៈប្រហាក់ប្រហែល</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ក្នុងការផ្តល់ឥណទានយ៉ាងតិច២ឆ្នាំក្នុងវិស័យមីក្រូហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬធនាគារ</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹង ក្នុងការគ្រប់គ្រង និងដឹកនាំ</li>\r\n<li>មានជំនាញដោះស្រាយបញ្ហា ការគិតទុកជាមុន និងមានគំនិតផ្តួចផ្តើម</li>\r\n<li>ទំនាក់ទំនងល្អ រួសរាយរាក់ទាក់ ស្មោះត្រង់ និងមានការទទួលខុសត្រូវ និងឆន្ទៈក្នុងការសម្រេចគោលដៅ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ៖&nbsp;</strong>សាខាស្រុកគិរីរង់</p>',1,71,15,26,'1','01/12/2019',1,4,9,5,2,'English','2018-12-30 12:05:21','2020-05-29 21:33:43'),
	(650,15,'មន្ត្រីត្រួតពិនិត្យឥណទាន (Credit Control Officer) - ០១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>បង្កើតនិងកែលម្អ សៀវភៅគោលការណ៍ណែនាំនិងនីតិវិធី។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំតាមដានប្រាក់កម្ចីច្រើនជាង 5.000 ដុល្លារ។</li>\r\n<li>ពិនិត្យមើលឯកសារកម្ចីនិងអតិថិជនស្នាក់នៅតាមមូលដ្ឋានឬ​តំបន់។</li>\r\n<li>បង្កើតនិងធ្វើគោលនការណ៍និងនីតិវិធីឥណទានឡើងវិញ។</li>\r\n<li>ពិនិត្យបរិមាណឥណទាននិងគុណភាពនៃសាខានីមួយៗ។</li>\r\n<li>អភិវឌ្ឍន៍ផលិតផលនិងសេវាកម្មឥណទានដែលអាចលក់បានទៅលើក្រុមហ៊ុនផ្សេងៗ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំរបាយការណ៍ទម្លាក់ប្រាក់កម្ចី។</li>\r\n<li>រក្សាទុកអតិថិជនក្នុងអត្រាដែលអាចទទួលយកបាន។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើឱ្យប្រាកដថាសមតុល្យឥណទានស្ថិតក្នុងហានិភ័យនិងកម្ចីសមាមាត្រដែលត្រូវបានសរសេ​រ​និងអាចគ្រប់គ្រងបានតាមផែនការយុទ្ធសាស្រ្ត&nbsp; /និង ផែនការអាជីវកម្ម។</li>\r\n<li>អនុវត្តកិច្ចការផ្សេងៗ ទៀតដែលត្រូវចាត់តាំងដោយថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>មានបរិញ្ញាបត្រគណនេយ្យហិរញ្ញវត្ថុនិងធនាគារបរិញ្ញាបត្រសេដ្ឋកិច្ចឬមុខវិជ្ជាពាក់ព័ន្ធផ្សេងទៀត។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងអំពីមីក្រូហិរញ្ញវត្ថុនិងផលិតផលធនាគារ។</li>\r\n<li>អាចប្រើប្រាស់ប្រព័ន្ធកុំព្យូទ័រនៅក្នុង MS Office រួមមាន Word, Excel, Power Point, internet និង Email ។</li>\r\n<li>ចេះភាសាអង់គ្លេស ទាំងសរសេរនិងនិយាយបានល្អ។</li>\r\n<li>ទំនាក់ទំនងល្អជាមួយ បុគ្គលិកទាំងខាងក្នុងនិងខាងក្រៅ, ការប្តេជ្ញាចិត្ត,ខ្ពស់​និង​មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់។</li>\r\n<li>មានឆន្ទៈធ្វើការជាមួយក្រុមនិងធ្វើដំណើរទៅតាមខេត្ត។</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','01/20/2019',1,6,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-12-30 12:11:17','2020-05-31 02:18:47'),
	(651,16,'Contact Center Consultant - 01 post','<h3>1. Inbound call</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Respond to customer inquiries by following the customer service standard and script provided by ABA Bank.</li>\r\n<li>Research required information using available resources (if assigned by Head of department).</li>\r\n<li>Handle/ resolve customer complaints (if doable in your level) and/or Identify and escalate priority issues/complaints to the right person of the units which a complaint/issue raised to.</li>\r\n<li>Perform your role and contact point from the client to follow up and close the complaint/issue.</li>\r\n<li>Follow‐up customer calls where necessary.</li>\r\n<li>Provide customers with product and service information, terms and conditions if asked by the client.</li>\r\n<li>Route calls to appropriate departments if a query/complaint is not manageable within your discretion.</li>\r\n<li>Complete call logs and prepare call reports on the timely manner.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>2. Outbound Calls</h3>\r\n<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Contact businesses or private individuals by phone to survey about the service provided by ABA Bank.</li>\r\n<li>Deliver prepared sales scripts to persuade potential customers to purchase a product or service if you are asked.</li>\r\n<li>Describe products and services, respond to questions, identify for the opportunity for sales, obtain customer information, and refer sales opportunity to Relationship Manager/ Consultant.</li>\r\n<li>Data entry and maintenance of customer/potential customer data bases.</li>\r\n<li>Follow‐up on initial contacts.</li>\r\n<li>Maintain records of telephonic interactions, orders and accounts.</li>\r\n<li>Keep a close eye on your local competitors &ndash; what they do and how they perform. Plan to gain market share.</li>\r\n<li>Keep up to date with ABA&rsquo;s products suite and marketing campaigns to ensure superior product knowledge.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul class=\"bullet-red\">\r\n<li>Organizational and time management skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work effectively in a team environment.</li>\r\n<li>Sound written and verbal communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>High degree of self‐motivation and excellent interpersonal skills.</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding of basic banking products and services.</li>\r\n<li>Practical knowledge of operating risk and compliance policies and procedures.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','01/28/2019',1,3,3,5,8,'English','2018-12-30 12:13:28','2020-05-31 03:29:32'),
	(652,15,'មន្រ្តីផ្នែកលក់ (Retail Sale Officer) - ១៣នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ដោះស្រាយបាននូវរាល់បញ្ហាដែលនឹងអាចកើតមានឡើង ចំពោះប្រតិបត្តិការ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំ និងគ្រប់គ្រងរាល់ឯកសារព័ត៌មានទំនាក់ទំនង ជាមួយអតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>រាយការណ៍ពីបាតុភាព និងផលប៉ះពាល់ដល់ ផលិតផល និងសេវាកម្ម ទាំង ឡាយ មកគណៈគ្រប់គ្រង ឱ្យបានទាន់ពេលច្បាស់លាស់ គ្រប់គ្រាន់ និងត្រឹមត្រូវ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំបាយការណ៍តាមការចាត់ចែងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>បព្ចាប់ថ្នាក់ បរិញ្ញាបត្រ ឬកំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់ បរិញ្ញាបត្រឆ្នាំទី៤ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រង ជំនាញទីផ្សារ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ចកម្ម ជំនាញធនាគារ និង ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ, ឫសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតំលៃស្មើ។</li>\r\n<li>មានឆន្ទៈចុះបំពេញការងារនៅតាមមូលដ្ឋាន និងនៅក្នុងដែនគ្រប់គ្រងរបស់សាខា។</li>\r\n<li>មានអត្ដចរិតល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសា និងមានអ៊ំណត់ក្នុង ការធ្វើការងារ។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួន។</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #0070c0;\">ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ:</span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">ការិយាល័យប្រតិបត្តិការ (០១នាក់)</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">សាខារាជធានីភ្នំពេញ (១០នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">សាខាខេត្តកំពត(០១នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">សាខាខេត្តព្រះសីហនុ (០១នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'13','01/25/2019',1,4,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-12-30 12:16:37','2020-05-30 06:58:45'),
	(653,15,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ៣៥៦នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការផ្សាព្វផ្សាយ ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីធីត(HKL) ដើម្បីពង្រីកទីផ្សារ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនសក្តានុពល។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំឯកសារឥណទាន ដើម្បីផ្តល់ឥណទានជូនអតិថិជន។&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងតាមដានការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>បំពេញការងារផ្សេងៗតាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង ។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>ជាប់បាក់ឌុប ឬ កំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្ររង ឬបរិញ្ញាបត្រលើគ្រប់ជំនាញ</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៏ផ្នែកលក់ ឬការផ្សព្វផ្សាយកាន់តែប្រសើ</li>\r\n<li>រួសរាយរាក់ទាក់ និងការបាស្រ័យទាក់ទងល្អ</li>\r\n<li>មានអត្តចរិកល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈ ក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួននិងអាចបើកបរបាន</li>\r\n<li>ផ្នែកគណិតវិទ្យាៈ ការវិភាគ និង គណនា</li>\r\n<li>ប្រវត្តិរស់នៅក្នុងសហគមន៍ល្អ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; color: #0070c0;\">ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ: </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"left\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; រាជធានីភ្នំពេញ (៤៥នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - បន្ទាយមានជ័យ (១៥នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - បាត់ដំបង(១៦នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - សាខាខេត្តកំពង់ធំ(១៩នាក់)<br />-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; កំពង់ចាម (១២នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - កំពង់ស្ពឺ(០៧នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - កំពត(០៨នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ក្រុងកែប-សង្កាត់ព្រៃធំ(០២នាក់) <br />-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ព្រះសីហនុ (៣នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - កោះកុង (០៦នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - មណ្ឌលគិរី(០៩នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ឧត្តរមានជ័យ(០៧នាក់)<br />-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ព្រះវិហារ(០៧នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - កណ្តាល (៥៦នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ក្រចេះ(០៦នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ក្រុងសៀមរាប(៣៣នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; រតនគិរី(៣នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ត្បូងឃ្មុំ (១៨នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ស្ទឹងត្រែង(០៣នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ស្វាយរៀង(១០នាក់) <br />-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; តាកែវ(១៦នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ព្រៃវែង (២៤នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - ពោធិ៍សាត់ (២២នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp; - កំពង់ឆ្នាំង (៩នាក់)</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',1,71,15,28,'356','01/25/2019',1,6,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2018-12-30 12:20:41','2020-05-30 18:33:14'),
	(654,29,'Senior Internal Auditor (01 Post)','<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left: 22.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 102.65pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Prepare draft annual activities and budget plan;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 22.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 102.65pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Lead IA team to conduct regular internal audit branch and functional department;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 22.5pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 102.65pt;\"><!-- [if !