es New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: GillSans-Bold; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Follow up on Departmental and branches&rsquo; corrective actions as per the previous audit carried out and ensure implementation and effectiveness of these; and</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left: 22.3pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 102.65pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: GillSans-Bold; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Draft report and send to direct supervisor for review.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: GillSans-Bold; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">-&nbsp; &nbsp; Work other task assigned by manager.</span></p>','<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left: 22.3pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 102.65pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: GillSans-Bold; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Finance and Banking or other related fields;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 22.3pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 102.65pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: GillSans-Bold; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">At least 1 year experiences in Banks or MFIs;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left: 22.3pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 102.65pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: GillSans-Bold; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Computer literacy &ndash; MS Office skills on Word, Excel, and PowerPoint;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left: 22.3pt; mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: 102.65pt;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Khmer OS Siemreap\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-bidi-font-family: GillSans-Bold; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">Have a good interpersonal, strongly verbal communications skills; and</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arrus BT\',\'serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: GillSans-Bold; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">-&nbsp; &nbsp; English proficiency.</span></p>',1,28,11,17,'1','01/31/2019',1,5,3,5,15,'Khmer, English','2019-01-04 13:44:57','2020-05-31 08:00:51');
