	(776,15,'Manager, Server Infrastructure - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Manage the day-to-day operations of the Non-core business system environment that included but not limited to server system infrastructure that included VMware-vSphere platform, Windows Server Operating System, Open-Source system platform, Server system and Services: Active Directory, DNS, Microsoft Exchange, Skype for business, SCCM, web server services</li>\r\n<li>Monitor system performance, configurations, maintenance and troubleshooting. Ensures of proper records of critical system incident and equipment inventory are maintained. Applies revisions to server system firmware, server system update and patching. Works with vendors to assist support activities.</li>\r\n<li>Develop new system and application implementation plans, custom scripts and testing procedures to ensure server system operational reliability. Trains technical staff on how to use new server system and related server hardware.</li>\r\n<li>Perform troubleshooting as required. As such, leads problem-solving efforts often involving outside vendors and other supporting staff within IT Infrastructure Department.</li>\r\n<li>Update procedure to manage on users accounts. Administration on system change and configuration&nbsp; on relate server system and services.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Computer Science or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Certified qualification of Ms. Server System</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 years experienced in Server system (Microsoft and Open-source), and server &amp; storage hardware administration</li>\r\n<li>Good knowledge at Window server, Linux, VMWare-VSphere, Microsoft Exchange, Skype for business, and Microsoft System Center</li>\r\n<li>Experience on enterprise monitoring tools and backup solution</li>\r\n<li>Working experience at MFI or Bank is a plus</li>\r\n<li>Good at oral and written communication skills both English and Khmer</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','04/30/2019',0,5,9,5,2,'Khmer, English','2019-04-18 09:57:32','2020-05-31 12:26:32'),
	(777,15,'Manager, Technical Support - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Manage Operations of IT technical Helpdesk Service as daily basis</li>\r\n<li>Manage IT technical issue escalation to related teams under IT Division,</li>\r\n<li>Update procedure on network access and connectivity, performance issues including availability, utilization, throughput, and latency; update policies and procedures on network access and authentication;</li>\r\n<li>Administrate and manage network monitoring tool</li>\r\n<li>Administrate and Manage networking equipment inventory</li>\r\n<li>Manage on change control to network equipment and configuration</li>\r\n<li>Support on Design and deploy network system and connectivity</li>\r\n<li>Support on LANs, WANs, network segments, Internet, and intranet systems</li>\r\n<li>Monitor to ensure of network system performance, and network availability and document on activity log and network incidents.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Computer Science or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least 3 years experienced in design and implement network connectivity, Network technical support and management</li>\r\n<li>Certified qualification of Network technology (CCNA-4, CND, CCNP&hellip;)</li>\r\n<li>Experience in network monitoring tools; hands on experiencing networking, routing and switching,</li>\r\n<li>knowledge of best practices around management, control, and monitoring of server infrastructure</li>\r\n<li>Working experience at MFI or Bank is a plus</li>\r\n<li>Good at oral and written communication skills both English and Khmer.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','04/30/2019',0,5,9,5,12,'Khmer, English','2019-04-18 09:59:45','2020-05-31 18:15:42'),
	(778,15,'Manager, Mobile App Development - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Take lead in mobile app development project including Prototyping (UX/UI), designing, and developing mobile applications</li>\r\n<li>Work closely with related department and stakeholders to translate ideas, high level specifications into new or enhanced mobile application solutions</li>\r\n<li>Work with product owners across the businesses to understand market needs &amp; vision; quickly translate that vision into demonstrable applications</li>\r\n<li>Lead internal resources and provide guidance ensuring all development standards and practices are adhered to pursues continuous improvement in development processes, standards and quality ; to coach, mentor, and lead a diverse group of lean/agile software engineers</li>\r\n<li>Communicate effectively with immediate team and leadership, ensuring team receives consistent messages and has clear understanding of business direction, strategy, and results</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Computer Science or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Proven work experience as a Mobile Developer with proven portfolio of released applications</li>\r\n<li>In-depth knowledge of programming languages like Swift, Java, Flutter, React -&nbsp; Experience with third-party libraries and APIs</li>\r\n<li>Familiarity with OOP design principles</li>\r\n<li>Excellent analytical skills with good problem-solving attitude</li>\r\n<li>Working experience with Microfinance or commercial bank is a plus</li>\r\n<li>Fluency in spoken and written English</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','04/30/2019',0,5,9,5,9,'Khmer, English','2019-04-18 10:02:39','2020-05-30 07:00:03'),
	(779,15,'Team Leader, System Administration - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Monitor resources of servers, storages and troubleshoot.</li>\r\n<li>Implement securities of operating system and perform regular securities monitoring&nbsp; to identify any possible intrusions.</li>\r\n<li>Perform patching on the system (OS, Server, and Storage) as required.</li>\r\n<li>Utilize resources efficiency on Server and Storage for production, DR, and UAT environment.</li>\r\n<li>Implement and monitor user access rights on System.</li>\r\n<li>Implement the Disaster Recovery, Data Continuity Plan and new system administration procedure.</li>\r\n<li>Assist Manager on security enhancement on OS, Server, and Storage.</li>\r\n<li>Complete the tasks assigned by management and establish the activities plan for System Administration Unit.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure system is running 24/7 without interruption.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Computer Science or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least two year experiences as System Administrator, especially on Oracle Hardware.</li>\r\n<li>Working experience at MFI or Bank is a plus.</li>\r\n<li>Good knowledge of Oracle Solaris, Oracle Linux, Oracle VM for x86 and SPARC.</li>\r\n<li>Good knowledge of Oracle Server and Oracle Storage.</li>\r\n<li>Commitment and self-motivated.</li>\r\n<li>Able to work at night for solving critical issue or other tasks assigned by management.</li>\r\n<li>Good at oral and written communication skills both English and Khmer.</li>\r\n<li>Willing to learn new business application and new technology.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','04/30/2019',0,6,9,5,2,'Khmer, English','2019-04-18 10:05:18','2020-05-29 19:39:49'),
	(780,15,'IT Operations Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Daily control and monitor of business databases.</li>\r\n<li>Analyze event logs and report on access to business databases.</li>\r\n<li>Report on business database performance status.</li>\r\n<li>Backup business databases to physical storage and to tape library.</li>\r\n<li>Restore database for monthly basic.</li>\r\n<li>Cooperation in IT technical team, operation team and finance team.</li>\r\n<li>Clear daily transactions in system with relevant business support team.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Computer Science or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least have basic knowledge on Linux, UNIX and Oracle database.</li>\r\n<li>Basic of SQL language is preferable.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge on some business applications is a plus.</li>\r\n<li>Be patient and work commitment.</li>\r\n<li>Good written and spoken English.</li>\r\n<li>Be able to work at night shifts.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','04/30/2019',0,5,7,5,1,'Khmer, English','2019-04-18 10:07:34','2020-06-01 16:54:09'),
	(781,15,'មន្រ្តីផ្នែកលក់ (Sale Officer) - ១០នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ដោះស្រាយបាននូវរាល់បញ្ហាដែលនឹងអាចកើតមានឡើង ចំពោះប្រតិបត្តិការ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំ និងគ្រប់គ្រងរាល់ឯកសារព័ត៌មានទំនាក់ទំនង ជាមួយអតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>រាយការណ៍ពីបាតុភាព និងផលប៉ះពាល់ដល់ ផលិតផល និងសេវាកម្ម ទាំងឡាយ មកគណៈគ្រប់គ្រង ឱ្យបានទាន់ពេលច្បាស់លាស់ គ្រប់គ្រាន់ និងត្រឹមត្រូវ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំបាយការណ៍តាមការចាត់ចែងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>បព្ចាប់ថ្នាក់ បរិញ្ញាបត្រ ឬកំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់ បរិញ្ញាបត្រឆ្នាំទី៤ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រង ជំនាញទីផ្សារ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ចកម្ម ជំនាញធនាគារ និង ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ, ឫសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតំលៃស្មើ។</li>\r\n<li>មានឆន្ទៈចុះបំពេញការងារនៅតាមមូលដ្ឋាន និងនៅក្នុងដែនគ្រប់គ្រងរបស់សាខា។</li>\r\n<li>មានអត្ដចរិតល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសា និងមានអ៊ំណត់ក្នុង ការធ្វើការងារ។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួន។</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ៖</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌចំការមន-សង្កាត់ទួលស្វាយព្រៃទី២ (១នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌចំការមន-សង្កាត់បឹងកេងកងទី២ (១នាក់)&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌពោធិ៍សែនជ័យ-សង្កាត់កាកាប (១នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌសែនសុខ-សង្កាត់ភ្នំពេញថ្មី (១នាក់)&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកខ្សាច់កណ្ដាល-ឃុំស្វាយជ្រំ (១នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកពញាក្រែក-ឃុំកោងកាង (១នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខេត្តព្រះសីហនុ(១នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;​​​​​&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌទួលគោក-សង្កាត់ទឹកល្អក់ទី៣(១នាក់)&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'10','04/30/2019',0,6,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2019-04-18 10:11:30','2020-05-31 12:55:47'),
	(782,15,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ១៤២នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការផ្សាព្វផ្សាយ ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីធីត(HKL) ដើម្បីពង្រីកទីផ្សារ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនសក្តានុពល។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំឯកសារឥណទាន ដើម្បីផ្តល់ឥណទានជូនអតិថិជន។&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងតាមដានការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>បំពេញការងារផ្សេងៗតាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>ជាប់បាក់ឌុប ឬ កំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្ររង ឬបរិញ្ញាបត្រលើគ្រប់ជំនាញ ។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៏ផ្នែកលក់ ឬការផ្សព្វផ្សាយកាន់តែប្រសើរ។</li>\r\n<li>រួសរាយរាក់ទាក់ និងការបាស្រ័យទាក់ទងល្អ។</li>\r\n<li>មានអត្តចរិកល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសារ និងមានឆន្ទៈ ក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួននិងអាចបើកបរបាន។</li>\r\n<li>ផ្នែកគណិតវិទ្យាៈ ការវិភាគ និង គណនា</li>\r\n<li>ប្រវត្តិរស់នៅក្នុងសហគមន៍ល្អ។</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ៖</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">រាជធានីភ្នំពេញ (២៧នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">បន្ទាយមានជ័យ (០៨នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">បាត់ដំបង(៨នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">សាខាខេត្តកំពង់ធំ(៤នាក់)<br /></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">កំពង់ចាម (៨នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">កំពត(៤នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">កំពង់ឆ្នាំង (២នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;ព្រៃវែង (៦នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">ព្រះសីហនុ(០៤នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">កោះកុង (៣នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">ព្រះវិហារ(០១នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">កណ្តាល (២៧នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">ត្បូងឃ្មុំ (១៣នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">ស្វាយរៀង(៤នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">តាកែវ(៤នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">សៀមរាប(៨នាក់)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /></span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">ពោធិ៍សាត់ (៩នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span class=\"left w100 size-content size13\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\">ក្រុងកែប-សង្កាត់ព្រៃធំ(០២នាក់)&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'142','04/30/2019',0,6,3,5,1,'Khmer','2019-04-18 10:14:24','2020-05-30 00:29:32'),
	(783,31,'Relationship Management Officer(SME Agent) - 14 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Promote Sathapana Bank&rsquo;s products and services to&nbsp; clients&nbsp; at&nbsp; the&nbsp; target&nbsp; and&nbsp; remote&nbsp; areas&nbsp; to ensure that both banking services and products are successfully sold to potential clients</li>\r\n<li>Meet, discuss and assist potential clients in obtaining loan information, loan application and loan disbursement&nbsp; process with&nbsp; other&nbsp; related&nbsp; information&nbsp; which&nbsp; benefit&nbsp; them&nbsp; to&nbsp; ensure&nbsp; the&nbsp; effective customer service and service level agreement</li>\r\n<li>Discuss and give recommendations to clients on the different types of loans and credit options as well as the terms and conditions of Sathapana Bank&rsquo;s services and products</li>\r\n<li>Analyze clients&rsquo; assets including financial status, credit and property to assure that the evaluation and determination feasibility of granting loans are effectively executed followed the bank policy and other both internal and external regulatory</li>\r\n<li>Review and verify loan agreements to ensure that they are well organized, completed and accurate according to the policies and regulatory</li>\r\n<li>Build a very good relationship and keep in touch with both the existing and the&nbsp; newest&nbsp; potential clients</li>\r\n<li>Compute,review and update credit and loan files to insure the payment schedule is accurately and effectively executed</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Business Administration,Finance and Banking, or related fields</li>\r\n<li>At least 2-year-experience in loan disbursement with a huge amount of outstanding loan and cooperate loan from financial industries</li>\r\n<li>Good at both English and Microsoft Office</li>\r\n<li>Be welcoming, friendly, and patient</li>\r\n<li>Willing to work at fields</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Locations:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Chi Pou Branch (03 Positions)</li>\r\n<li>Tuk Meas Branch (02 Positions)</li>\r\n<li>Svay Antor Branch (03 Positions)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Chrey Branch (03 Positions)</li>\r\n<li>Preah Netr Preah Branch (03 Positions)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,25,'14','05/31/2019',1,5,3,5,2,'English','2019-05-12 09:44:33','2020-05-30 01:40:53'),
	(784,31,'Teller - 06 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Provide superior banking service by exhibiting a friendly and professional demeanor at all times</li>\r\n<li>Keep good communication and relationship with the team and others</li>\r\n<li>Understand bank products and respond appropriately to customer inquiries regarding product</li>\r\n<li>Understand Retail Banking policies and procedures for position and ensure compliance</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the accuracy and completeness of customer transaction recordings and postings</li>\r\n<li>Perform daily cash balancing and investigate for all any discrepancies</li>\r\n<li>Generate cross sales and referrals to generate new business and additional services</li>\r\n<li>Promote bank products and further establish business relationships&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Accept assignments as required to maintain adequate staffing levels throughout branch system</li>\r\n<li>Ensure all customer application forms and other related documents are adequate for daily operations</li>\r\n<li>Any ad-hoc work(s) assigned by supervisor, Deputy Branch Manager or/and Branch Manager</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Accounting, Finance and Banking, or other related fields</li>\r\n<li>At least 1-year-experience in banking services and products from financial industries; banks, MFIs, and other MDIs, or fresh graduated are also encouraged to apply</li>\r\n<li>Good at both English and Computer Users</li>\r\n<li>Be welcoming, friendly, and patient</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Locations: </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Chi PouBranch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Tuk Meas Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Svay Antor Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Preah Netr Preah Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Chrey (02 Positions)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,25,'6','05/31/2019',1,8,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 09:50:50','2020-06-01 14:21:10'),
	(785,31,'ជំនួយការគ្រប់គ្រងទំនាក់ទំនងអតិថិជន(ភ្នាក់ងារឥណទាន) - ០៤នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការផ្សព្វផ្សាយពីផលិតផល និងសេវាកម្មរបស់ធនាគារស្ថាបនាទៅដល់អតិថិជនទៅតាមមូលដ្ឋាន</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការសិក្សាពីទីផ្សារ និងរៀបចំផែនការការងារក្នុងការលក់ផលិតផលឥណទាន រួមទាំងសេវាកម្មរបស់ធនាគារស្ថាបនាជូនអតិថិជនគោលដៅ និងអតិថិជនសក្តានុពលនៅក្នុងតំបន់</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការប្រាស្រ័យទាក់ទង និងរក្សាទំនាក់ទំនងល្អជាមួយអាជ្ញាធរដែនដីគ្រប់ជាន់ថ្នាក់ ព្រមទាំងអតិថិជនដែលមានស្រាប់ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនថ្មី</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការវិភាគ វាយតម្លៃទៅតាមឥណទាន ទ្រព្យសកម្ម និងអាជីវកម្មរបស់អតិថិជន ព្រមទាំងបំពេញទម្រង់បែបបទ និងឯកសារផ្សេងៗដែលពាក់ព័ន្ធ</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>កម្រិតបរិញ្ញាបត្រជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រងទូទៅ​ ពាណិជ្ជកម្ម សេដ្ឋកិច្ចហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ និងគណនេយ្យ</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍យ៉ាងតិច០១ឆ្នាំ ឬមិនមានបទពិសោធន៍ក៏ត្រូវបានលើកទឹកចិត្តអោយដាក់ពាក្យ</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងផ្នែកកុំព្យូទ័រ និងភាសាអង់គ្លេស</li>\r\n<li>មានឆន្ទៈខ្ពស់ ភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ភាពរួសរាយរាក់ទាក់ និងភាពហ្មត់ចត់ចំពោះការងារ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ៖</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកទូកមាស (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកស្វាយអន្ទរ (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកព្រះនេត្រព្រះ (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,21,'4','05/31/2019',1,7,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 10:04:15','2020-06-01 05:59:48'),
	(786,31,'Customer Service Assistant - 05 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Welcome, consult and provide consistent and high quality products and services to customers</li>\r\n<li>Provide certain non-cash transactions to customers including account opening, account closing, passbook update, renew Fixed Deposit certificate, card services (card request, PIN request, card demo, card loss/damage, etc), eBanking Services ( eBanking request, demo, etc)</li>\r\n<li>Facilitate VIP customers to obtain demanded service(s) such as cash withdrawal/deposit, account opening with satisfactory arrangement including privacy room</li>\r\n<li>Execute account opening and closing transactions for customers to ensure all required information and procedures on account opening are completely made</li>\r\n<li>Attend customers&rsquo; needs and enquiries on the bank&rsquo;s products and services in a manner which ensures overall customer satisfaction</li>\r\n<li>Ensure all customer areas including the on-site (office) ATM booth, banking hall, cash count room and VIP room are neat and clean, and display properly; broachers are available</li>\r\n<li>Adhere to all relevant compliance requirement including FATCA, KYC and world-check screening</li>\r\n<li>Assist to monitor and report of customer Term Deposit with special rate for seeking approval from Sale and Business department</li>\r\n<li>Ensure all ATM cards are accurately received from Card Center and E-banking department</li>\r\n<li>Assist direct supervisor in preparing various daily, weekly, and monthly customer service reports including account opening, account closing, card report, eBanking report and so on as required by the policy and procedures</li>\r\n<li>Assist to monitor on daily reports of Account Opening, Account Closing, CIF creation/amendment, Dormant&nbsp; Account, ATM, e-Banking, and other requirements reports forms related departments, and document filing</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Accounting, Finance and Banking, or other related fields</li>\r\n<li>At least 1-year-experience in banking services and products from financial industries</li>\r\n<li>Good at both English and Computer Users</li>\r\n<li>Be welcoming, friendly, and patient</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Locations:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Chi Pou Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Tuk Meas Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Svay Antor Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Preah Netr Preah Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Chrey (01 Position)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,57,15,25,'5','05/31/2019',1,8,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 10:09:49','2020-05-30 22:19:16'),
	(787,31,'Credit Administration Assistant - 05 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Operate personal computer to type correspondence and reports to enter or retrieve data and other related court documents</li>\r\n<li>Compose correspondence and review outgoing documents for appropriate format, grammatical and spelling accuracy, and conformance with administration department directives</li>\r\n<li>Answer telephone and walk-in inquiries and provides assistance regarding procedures or scheduling inquiries from supervisors</li>\r\n<li>Receive, sort, distribute and file the incoming documents including correspondence, court documents or reports</li>\r\n<li>Assist operations in other offices by answering telephone calls</li>\r\n<li>Respond to inquiries and requests</li>\r\n<li>Prepare time-and-attendance records and other personnel documents for the office</li>\r\n<li>Maintain calendar, schedules and managing files</li>\r\n<li>Monitor branch requests for supplies and equipment</li>\r\n<li>Maintain requisition files and monitors receipt of items requested in requisitions</li>\r\n<li>Distribute weekly and monthly statistical reports to supervisors</li>\r\n<li>Maintain confidentiality and security of documents and information</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Accounting, Finance and Banking, or other related fields</li>\r\n<li>At least 1-year-experience in banking services and products from financial industries</li>\r\n<li>Good at both English and Computer Users</li>\r\n<li>Be welcoming, friendly, and patient</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Locations:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Chi Pou Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Tuk Meas Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Svay Antor Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Preah Netr Preah Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Chrey (01 Position)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,21,'5','05/31/2019',1,8,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 10:14:35','2020-05-31 23:44:13'),
	(788,31,'Cashier - 05 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Assist Chief Branch Cashier to monitor branch cash operations including on branch&rsquo;s premise (daily business operation) and in branch&rsquo;s bank account(s) to ensure that Branch has sufficient fund/cash in all operating currencies and denominations for daily operations</li>\r\n<li>Branch has good quality notes for daily operations and ATM cash operation</li>\r\n<li>Soiled or poor quality notes are sorted and separated from good quality notes for bank-in to Branch&rsquo;s account(s) or transferring to main branch or provincial branch in region</li>\r\n<li>Assist Chief Branch Cashier to prepare money for bank deposits when cash in vault is going to excess the cash limit in the bank premise</li>\r\n<li>Assist Tellers in counting and verifying money when customers deposit large amounts</li>\r\n<li>Always adhere to all bank&rsquo;s policies and procedures especially physical cash management&nbsp; and relevant procedure</li>\r\n<li>Assist to record accurate bank account against all cash</li>\r\n<li>Assist to provide optimum cash management</li>\r\n<li>Assist to verify cash held against records, and prepare statement after closing the day&rsquo;s business</li>\r\n<li>Act as custodian of Cash Safe in the Vault</li>\r\n<li>Assist in ATM cash replenishment by selecting good quality notes</li>\r\n<li>Assist to manage cash for supporting other branches when needed</li>\r\n<li>Assist to verify cash returned from Tellers</li>\r\n<li>Assist Chief Branch Cashier to deposit soiled notes at Central Bank at regular intervals</li>\r\n<li>Assist to arrange new notes stock for festive seasons</li>\r\n<li>Assist to maintain knowledge, educate and coach Tellers on how to identify counterfeit notes</li>\r\n<li>Assist Chief Branch Cashier to prepare cash report as required by Branch Manager/Deputy Branch Manager and policies/procedures</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Accounting, Finance and Banking, or other related fields</li>\r\n<li>At least 1-year-experience in banking services and products from financial industries</li>\r\n<li>Good at both English and Computer Users</li>\r\n<li>Be welcoming, friendly, and patient</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Locations:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Chi Pou Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Tuk Meas Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Svay Antor Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Preah Netr Preah Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Chrey (01 Position)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,28,15,25,'5','05/31/2019',1,7,3,5,11,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 10:20:19','2020-06-01 15:04:26'),
	(789,31,'Branch Manager - 05 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Manage the operational plan, internal control system, and sufficient fund maintenance at branch to be effectively implemented, executed followed by policies and ensuring all financial transactions are&nbsp; authorized at the right time, the utilization of financial assets is made in the manner of minimizing cost, and maximizing profit including financial data is always updated properly</li>\r\n<li>Manage all income and expense transactions by reviewing strictly and authorizing all sufficient support documents of transactions possess, and ensure that all accounting documents are always ready for internal&nbsp; and external check with all transactions are recorded into the right accounting code when generating reports are required</li>\r\n<li>Manage the fixed assets by ensuring that the development and implementation of systems tracking and controlling the utilization and movement of assets at branch are effectively and efficiently used</li>\r\n<li>Review, analyze, and approve loan disbursement with maintaining portfolio in a very good quality by ensuring a proper documentation which is used for client&rsquo;s collateral to meet the minimum requirement</li>\r\n<li>Manage and lead the operation on the marketing campaign by promoting the products and services to ensure that the market share and expanding its operation without encountering risks are effectively executed at the under control area</li>\r\n<li>Manage actively in facilitating the general process of government relation at branch level by ensuring the efficient coordination with local authority in processing paper work, legal compliance and coping with problem solving</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Business Administration, Management, and other related fields</li>\r\n<li>At least 3-year-experience in banking industry related to credit loan management</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of industry rules, regulations, and good at results driven attitude</li>\r\n<li>Good at management skills, outstanding organization, strong customer service, written and oral communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Good at both English user and computer literacy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Locations:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Chi Pou Branch (01Position)</li>\r\n<li>Tuk Meas Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Svay Antor Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Preah Netr Preah Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Chrey (01 Position)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,36,15,25,'5','05/31/2019',1,6,3,5,12,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 10:27:58','2020-06-01 17:07:24'),
	(790,31,'Banking Service Supervisor - 05 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Provide excellent customer service as well as oversee the work of subordinators as a leader</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that cash is balanced for the Chief Cashier as well as total cash holding at the Bank at the end of the working day</li>\r\n<li>Count and record currency in Chief Cashier vault</li>\r\n<li>Assign team the workload on a daily basis and make decisions on various daily workload demands</li>\r\n<li>Assign duties and work schedules to subordinator to ensure efficient functioning of branch</li>\r\n<li>Maintain and update knowledge to subordinators in term of customer service, system functions, bank policies and procedures</li>\r\n<li>Handle customer and staff\'s complaints, conflicts or concerns related to Bank Procedures and other activities</li>\r\n<li>Adhere to bank&rsquo;s procedures,policies and regulations</li>\r\n<li>Assist line manager to appraise staff&rsquo;s performance and handle staff&rsquo;s grievances</li>\r\n<li>Deal with the assigned security company regarding delivery/collection of cash from the Central Bank and/ r other branches</li>\r\n<li>Housekeeping in assigned area is free of dust, arranged neatly, tidily</li>\r\n<li>For Branch&nbsp; that has&nbsp; not Chief Branch Back Office, BSS must responsible duties of Chief Branch Back Office</li>\r\n<li>Monitor and prepare daily/monthly/yearly operational reports</li>\r\n<li>File document and ensure accuracy and completeness of all filing documents</li>\r\n<li>Monitor and review bank\'s security procedures and control access to vault</li>\r\n<li>Handle daily team conflicts or simple disciplinary actions such as attendance problems</li>\r\n<li>Perform any other duties or responsibilities consistent with the role as assigned by management</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in Accounting, Finance and Banking, or other related fields</li>\r\n<li>At least 3-year-experience in banking services and products from financial industries</li>\r\n<li>Good at both English and Computer Users</li>\r\n<li>Be welcoming, friendly, and patient</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Locations:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Chi Pou Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Tuk Meas Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Svay Antor Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Preah Netr Preah Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n<li>Kampong Chrey Branch (01 Position)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,57,15,25,'5','05/31/2019',1,5,9,5,12,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 10:34:33','2020-05-29 15:06:14'),
	(791,31,'Marketing Support Assistant - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Assist to monitor the implementation and usage of the marketing materials and collaterals at all branches and to make sure all marketing material are aligned with guideline.</li>\r\n<li>Controls and follows up on the implementation of ongoing marketing, advertising and promotion activities against policies and plans.</li>\r\n<li>Monitors the effectiveness of media, billboards and other non-digital marketing channels.</li>\r\n<li>Monitors the branches signboards, light boxes, and the interior and exterior of branches&rsquo; building ensuring all are within corporate guidelines.</li>\r\n<li>Monitors the ATMs in branches and offsite locations ensuring all marketing and branding collaterals are within corporate guidelines.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in marketing, communications, media and digital, public relations, and international relations.</li>\r\n<li>Good relevant marketing skills and good knowledge of event management.</li>\r\n<li>Good analytical skills with data gathering, understanding, and interpretation.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to support on a given project and see it through a final resolution.</li>\r\n<li>Good communication skills.</li>\r\n<li>Enthusiasm and positive attitude.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','05/31/2019',1,7,3,5,1,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 10:43:44','2020-05-30 07:52:28'),
	(792,31,'Manager of Digital and Media Communications Unit - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Lead and monitors all standard and consistent of digital media both internal and external communications.</li>\r\n<li>Lead and monitors all the contents update of the social medias, website, intranet, and other communications</li>\r\n<li>Promote our corporate identity to public with clear, precise and consistent communication without the unnecessary confusion.</li>\r\n<li>Tracks conversation rates and improves on the social media and website interaction and visited.</li>\r\n<li>Leads and improves the internal communication for inter-departments, inter-branches, and inter head office and branches</li>\r\n<li>Leads and improves external communications to partners, agencies, authorities, and press.</li>\r\n<li>Leads and manage public announcements and manage public relations.</li>\r\n<li>Leads and improves media relations.</li>\r\n<li>Gathers and prepares information and data from other departments to draft annual report and newsletter timely and accurately.</li>\r\n<li>Plans and implements the bank&rsquo;s annual CSR activities including community activity.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinates and works with the publishers, designers, journalist, marketing agency, and consultant for requires services.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other tasks assigned by direct supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>BA or higher in related fields but not limited to marketing, communications, media and digital, public relations, and international relations.</li>\r\n<li>Good relevant marketing skills</li>\r\n<li>Strong analytical skills with data gathering, understanding, and interpretation</li>\r\n<li>Strong leadership skills and the ability to take charge of a given project and see it through a final resolution</li>\r\n<li>Good communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Enthusiasm and positive attitude</li>\r\n<li>Strong leadership management</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','05/31/2019',1,7,9,5,9,'Khmer, English','2019-05-12 15:52:24','2020-05-30 22:17:48'),
	(793,31,'Digital Operational Excellence Assistant - 03 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Assist in develop and update the digital banking operation manual, procedure and policy to ensure the&nbsp; streamline processes and seamless experience to improve the effectives and efficiency of digital banking operation.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure all services delivered comply with Sathapana Bank Strategy, policies, process and standards with internal and external regulatory requirements.</li>\r\n<li>Assist line manager to manage daily operation of digital banking transaction which including settlement and dispute of digital product as well as alliance partnership.</li>\r\n<li>Closely work with relevant stakeholder to ensure all the required procedure are properly in place</li>\r\n<li>Develop strong relationship with operation, risk and compliance stakeholders.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other tasks assigned by Department Head.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Degree or relevant professional qualification in Business, Accounting, Economics, Management or relevant working experience in this area.</li>\r\n<li>Fresh Graduate are encouraged.</li>\r\n<li>Sound good knowledge in Digital Banking Service within financial institution.</li>\r\n<li>Hard working, Commitment and willing to learn new things.</li>\r\n<li>Good Communication skill and strong team player.</li>\r\n<li>Good in verbal and written English.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'3','05/31/2019',1,7,3,5,8,'English','2019-05-12 15:56:31','2020-06-01 14:42:13'),
	(794,31,'Digital Product Management Assistant - 03 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Assist line manager managing a suite of digital banking products/services and proposition incorporating:&nbsp; digital product strategy, product life cycle management, digital product definition, digital product and proposition development, launch and commercialization.</li>\r\n<li>Assist in monitor and review digital product performance and recommend for improvements.</li>\r\n<li>Assist and co-ordinate on report requirement of digital banking products/services for regulators, management, branches and relevant business team.</li>\r\n<li>Follow up the competitor&rsquo;s activities to ensure ongoing competitive service in the market.</li>\r\n<li>Assist and prepare formulate, recommend and present committee submission.</li>\r\n<li>Make sure all digital productivities properly documented/ maintained.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other task assigned by Department Head.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Degree or relevant professional qualification in Business, Accounting, Economics, Management or relevant working experience in this area.</li>\r\n<li>Fresh Graduate are encouraged.</li>\r\n<li>Sound good knowledge in Digital Banking Service within financial institution.</li>\r\n<li>Hard working, commitment and willing to learn new things.</li>\r\n<li>Good Communication skill and strong team player.</li>\r\n<li>Good in verbal and written in English.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,54,15,17,'3','05/31/2019',1,7,11,5,9,'English','2019-05-12 15:59:53','2020-05-31 17:44:29'),
