VALUES
	(879,19,'Lending Monitoring Officer - 02 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Coordinate and support to branch staff about guidelines related to loan processing and correction their mistakes and/or errors of completing the loan documents.</li>\r\n<li>Monitor and report about loan quality that approved by credit committee or branch committee (always check the client overdue and report to credit committee).</li>\r\n<li>Train and contribute good experiences about loan assessment and communication skill to COs, CCOs and BMs.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate loan processing with all Branches and ensure that all field staff implementations are&nbsp; full compliance of Loan Policies and Guidelines.</li>\r\n<li>Conduct periodic internal controls and check on areas are concerned.</li>\r\n<li>Maintain customer confidence by keeping loan confidential information.</li>\r\n<li>Find out the lending issues at the branches and suggest the ways for improving.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree of Finance and Banking or closest fields.</li>\r\n<li>Having experience of the relevant job at least two years.</li>\r\n<li>Must support KREDIT vision and mission.</li>\r\n<li>Honest, rigor and friendly.</li>\r\n<li>Have the ability to analyze and interpret financial statements of the business in order to access the repayment capacity and financial soundness of the borrower.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of computer applications (Work and Excels).</li>\r\n<li>Good understanding of business process.</li>\r\n<li>Good interpersonal skill.</li>\r\n<li>Acceptable written and verbal communication skills (Khmer and English).</li>\r\n<li>Problem Solving and Decision Making.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'2','06/27/2019',1,8,3,5,2,'Khmer, English','2019-06-23 09:52:48','2020-05-29 04:31:32'),
	(880,19,'Senior Sale and Customer Service Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Participate in developing policies, procedures, guidelines and sale strategies.</li>\r\n<li>Participate in setting sales plan and execute the strategies on non-credit services.</li>\r\n<li>Participate in providing training, refreshment, or strengthening the capacity of KREDIT&rsquo;s staff on customer service and selling skills.</li>\r\n<li>Select potential prospective such as business owners, NGOs, churches, companies and other partners for business activities.</li>\r\n<li>Make direct sale, appointment with potential prospective to sell non-credit services/other products or services of KREDIT.</li>\r\n<li>Provide direct support to the colleagues in sales team, branch staff on sales activities such as lead group promotion, present the services/products to potential prospective, ...</li>\r\n<li>Maintain good relationship with existing and potential prospective&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Follow up market information, competitors&rsquo; product information, and customer&rsquo;s satisfaction and then report to direct supervisor.</li>\r\n<li>Work with branch staff, CSOs and CREs, CSEs to ensure the quality and timely preparation of sale report and sale performance on non-loan service.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinates liaison between marketing, sales and customer&nbsp; service&nbsp; department&nbsp; and&nbsp; branches&nbsp; level on selling activities.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that all selling activities are in accordance with policies and guidelines.</li>\r\n<li>Understand all risks in selling process on all KREDIT services/products by reporting to related manager for finding the way to prevent and solving problem on time.</li>\r\n<li>Other Activities will be assigned by supervisor and required by KREDIT.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor in Marketing &amp; Sales or equivalent</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 years&rsquo; experience in sales (banking/microfinance is preferred)</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrate ability to communicate, present and influence credible and effectively at all levels of the organization including executive level</li>\r\n<li>Strong conceptualization and analytical skills</li>\r\n<li>Good in negotiation and presentation skills</li>\r\n<li>Strong communication skill in English and Khmer(written and spoken)</li>\r\n<li>Ability to drive the sales process from plan to close</li>\r\n<li>Ability to articulate the distinct aspect of products and services and position them against competitors</li>\r\n<li>Willing to travel to all KRET&rsquo;s operation areas in provinces</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,7,8,5,2,'English','2019-06-23 09:59:28','2020-05-29 13:30:57'),
	(881,19,'Senior Creative Designer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Generally lead the design and website team in their daily work</li>\r\n<li>Plan, lead in designing, and control the quality of approved printing projects.</li>\r\n<li>Workout directly with media agency for production of radio or TVC of KREDIT</li>\r\n<li>Be responsible for production of premium gifts.</li>\r\n<li>Work closely with related departments to arrange any big event of KREDIT.</li>\r\n<li>Make sure the updates the website and face book as needed.</li>\r\n<li>Do the process for approval of the project</li>\r\n<li>Lead in designing and arranging the installation of big panel at each office.</li>\r\n<li>With committee, call for quote of material productions.</li>\r\n<li>Participate in the development of marketing, planning and budgeting.</li>\r\n<li>Do field visit to take photos and video for supporting design work.</li>\r\n<li>Build and maintain critical relationships in a professional manner with other KREDIT&lsquo;s staffs, partners and stakeholders to promote KREDIT&rsquo;s brand name and services.</li>\r\n<li>Perform other related tasks as requested by supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Computer Science or equivalent</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 year experiences with designing or work art</li>\r\n<li>Fluency in Khmer and English</li>\r\n<li>Ability to keep ordered and systematic records and organizational skills</li>\r\n<li>Honest and excellent character with high commitment to work with and help poor people</li>\r\n<li>Problem solving and complain management skill</li>\r\n<li>Proficient in MS Words, Excel, PowerPoint,&nbsp; Internet and Email, Corel Draw and other designing software</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,7,8,5,2,'English','2019-06-23 10:05:42','2020-05-29 18:19:20'),
	(882,19,'Corporate Sales Executive - 02 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Participate in developing policies, procedures, guidelines, sale strategies and setting sales plan and execute the strategies on non-credit services</li>\r\n<li>Select potential prospective such as business owners, NGOs, churches, companies and other partners for business activities.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare slides to present to corporate clients and make direct sale and appointment with potential prospective to sell non-credit services/other products or services of KREDIT.</li>\r\n<li>Provide direct support to the braches on corporate sales activities and present the services/products to potential prospective etc.</li>\r\n<li>Maintain good relationship with existing and potential prospective.</li>\r\n<li>Follow up market information, competitors&rsquo; product information then report to direct supervisor.</li>\r\n<li>Prepare the corporate sale report and monitor the corporate sale performance across the country.</li>\r\n<li>Work with branch staff, CSOs, and CREs to ensure the quality and timely preparation of corporate sales report and corporate sale performance.</li>\r\n<li>Coordinate liaison corporate sales activity between branches and sales and customer service department.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that all corporate sales activities are in accordance with policies and guidelines.</li>\r\n<li>Understand all risks in corporate selling process on all KREDIT services/products by reporting to related managers for finding the way to prevent and to solve the problem on time.</li>\r\n<li>Other Activities will be assigned by superior.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>At least bachelor degree in marketing, business management or similar disciplines equivalent and one year&nbsp; of corporate sale experience with banks, MFI or relevant fields</li>\r\n<li>Proficiency of English language (Third language: Mandarin or Thai is more advantage and priority).</li>\r\n<li>Have a skill of identifying, evaluating, presenting and selling to the target corporate client and ability to approach to the right person or high level officer of the target firm</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge on analyzing and convincing corporate target clients and on business concept/process/flow and value chain of corporate sector&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>High level of communication and negotiation skills with the corporate client</li>\r\n<li>Confidentiality of KREDIT branding in front of the corporate target</li>\r\n<li>Ability to communicate, present and influence credible and effectively at all levels of the organization&nbsp; &nbsp;including executive level</li>\r\n<li>Strong networking in the corporate sectors</li>\r\n<li>Willing to travel to all KRET&rsquo;s operation areas in provinces</li>\r\n<li>Both genders are encouraged.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'2','06/27/2019',1,7,3,5,1,'English','2019-06-23 10:14:09','2020-06-01 07:28:41'),
	(883,19,'Sale and Customer Service Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Perform sale activities on savings and other financial products</li>\r\n<li>Establish personal contact of potential clients</li>\r\n<li>Collect feedback and complaint from clients related the sale and customer service care and service providing then report to Head of Sale &amp; Customer Service Department</li>\r\n<li>Analyze the market in order to identify new product growth opportunities.</li>\r\n<li>Provide support, monitor the work performance of front line staff related to service providing and products selling, and identify points to be improved.</li>\r\n<li>Work closely with Customer Relation Executive (CRE) to help boost the sales performance at each branch.</li>\r\n<li>Provide support to regionals and branches and training to branch staffs</li>\r\n<li>Resolve customer queries and issues related to sale and services</li>\r\n<li>Maintain sale reports and call follow up</li>\r\n<li>Other tasks will be assigned by supervisor</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor in Marketing or equivalent</li>\r\n<li>At least one year experience in sales, marketing, or microfinance/banking sectors</li>\r\n<li>Excellent oral and written English</li>\r\n<li>Good communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Interpersonal skills and professional appearance</li>\r\n<li>Telephone manner</li>\r\n<li>Capacities and flexibilities of sale and marketing</li>\r\n<li>Responsibility, logical thinking and results oriented in role</li>\r\n<li>Problem solving skill</li>\r\n<li>Honesty and neutrality in work</li>\r\n<li>Ability to travel to province branches</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,7,3,5,11,'English','2019-06-23 10:20:05','2020-05-29 18:41:35'),
	(884,19,'Creative Designer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>With brand and communication unit manager based on the approval from authorized people on the&nbsp; printing projects, initiate and perform different designs for KREDIT as needed</li>\r\n<li>After doing work art, call different suppliers for quotations by giving them same specs.</li>\r\n<li>Do quality control before handing over to admin counter-part staff to distribute to related offices.</li>\r\n<li>Update the website as needed</li>\r\n<li>Check with the suppliers or producers about progress of project movement to make sure that the final&nbsp; products will be on time sent to the related offices.</li>\r\n<li>Participate in the development of branding and communication plan and budget.</li>\r\n<li>Assist in establishing and providing training as needed</li>\r\n<li>Perform other tasks assigned by Branding and Communication Unit Manager.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Any bachelor degrees in the field of design, IT, marketing and other related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least 1 years experiences in web and graphic design.</li>\r\n<li>Skillful in using design software such as Adobe Illustrator, Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Flash, Adobe In design,&nbsp; web-design (Microsoft Expression web, Joomla...) -related program.</li>\r\n<li>Understanding written and spoken skills, both English and Khmer.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work under pressure, independently and highly self-motivated.</li>\r\n<li>Having good inter-personal skills.</li>\r\n<li>Ability to work creatively and be initiative.</li>\r\n<li>Able to travel throughout the country.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,8,3,5,11,'English','2019-06-23 10:25:38','2020-05-31 14:09:58'),
	(885,19,'Senior Customer Service Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Ensure that our customer are greeted warmly and friendly.</li>\r\n<li>Sell products and service as plan.</li>\r\n<li>Monitor and collaborate on customer service to ensure customer need and satisfaction.</li>\r\n<li>Customer facilitation in order speed up the process of account opening, ATM card request, and other customer inquiries.</li>\r\n<li>Develop strategies and be responsible for convincing potential customer to use KREDIT&rsquo;s products and services.</li>\r\n<li>Proactive customer problem solving, complaint handling and escalation.</li>\r\n<li>Effectively manage and monitor information notification to customer regarding to terms and conditions changing.</li>\r\n<li>Collect customer feedback and compliant, report to direct supervisor,and follow customer complaint resolution.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure that office and customer area are well organized and provided comfortable environment to customer.</li>\r\n<li>Be responsible for timely CIF and account create in system with an accurate data entry.</li>\r\n<li>Review CIF and account opening document in order to align with our internal policy.</li>\r\n<li>Follow ATM policy to manage ATM card request at branch.</li>\r\n<li>Coach, supervise, and develop staff&rsquo;s capacity and subordinate for all KREDIT products and policies.</li>\r\n<li>Understand well the competitor product, services, fee charge, and ...etc.</li>\r\n<li>Be able to work under pressure to complete the assigned task from direct supervisor.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Obtain Bachelor of Business Administration or equivalent.</li>\r\n<li>Integrity, friendly, patient and good disciplined.</li>\r\n<li>Good communication for both internal and external.</li>\r\n<li>Willing to work with poor people who served by KREDIT.</li>\r\n<li>Proactive problem solving skill.</li>\r\n<li>Good computer literacy and fast data entry</li>\r\n<li>Fluent in spoken and written English</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,6,3,5,1,'English','2019-06-23 10:31:40','2020-05-31 17:13:57'),
	(886,19,'Admin Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Draft and Check letters out such as spelling, format, meaning, date, and stamp.</li>\r\n<li>Check invoice for monthly consumption of water, electricity, and rubbish.</li>\r\n<li>Consolidate requests of promotional materials, documents from branches and submit to the department of Sale.</li>\r\n<li>Check and distribute printed documents and promotional materials that are delivered to the head office of KREDIT and branches.</li>\r\n<li>Check items in the head office such as lamp, fan, turn on-off button, table, chair, cabinet, door, window,&nbsp; air conditioner, bathroom, to make sure they are in order and function.&nbsp; And manage to repair it on time if it doesn&rsquo;t work.</li>\r\n<li>In Charge of photocopier: contact to supplier of repair, Check on rental contract, and verify monthly invoice.</li>\r\n<li>In charge of meeting room coordination.</li>\r\n<li>Facilitate on staff&rsquo;s accommodation and staff&rsquo;s Vehicles parking area.</li>\r\n<li>Monitor guard head office on weekends or holidays especially when the guards are absent eventually.</li>\r\n<li>Arrange shifts for guards for long holidays and spot check on them, complete the Over Time form online for them.</li>\r\n<li>D&eacute;cor head office such as national flag, religious flag, color lamp, banner, photo of the king, to welcome national events.</li>\r\n<li>Other tasks will be assigned by superior.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in Business Administration and other related fields.</li>\r\n<li>At least 1 year experience in Administration officer.</li>\r\n<li>Priority tasks of the institution as the first rather than personal tasks.</li>\r\n<li>Be honest and obey working hours.</li>\r\n<li>Keep good relation among the team work.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,66,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,7,3,5,11,'English','2019-06-23 10:37:10','2020-06-01 13:42:38'),
	(887,19,'Web Developer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Cooperate well with developer team to develop website and web application.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the performance, quality, and responsiveness of web site.</li>\r\n<li>Practice writing clean and maintainable codes according to best practices.</li>\r\n<li>Must be able to perform duties with moderate to lower supervision.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Male/female, Cambodian nationality</li>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in computer science or equivalent</li>\r\n<li>Strong skills in Web Development.</li>\r\n<li>Good experience with Laravel, WordPress, React, Vue</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrable knowledge of web technologies including HTML,CSS, Javascript, AJAX</li>\r\n<li>Experience in common third-party APIs (Google, Facebook)</li>\r\n<li>Programming/scripting experience and knowledge of software development life cycle is preferred</li>\r\n<li>Experience working with a development team</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,7,7,5,9,'English','2019-06-23 10:40:09','2020-06-01 12:59:16'),
	(888,19,'IT Technician - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Monitor computer processing systems.</li>\r\n<li>Check list computer at operation zone monthly and Schedule maintenance.</li>\r\n<li>Order computer parts.</li>\r\n<li>Install new computer, standard software and perform test on computer equipment and programs.</li>\r\n<li>Respond for daily maintenance.</li>\r\n<li>Create and manage IT inventory.</li>\r\n<li>Configure network, E-mail,and internet connection.</li>\r\n<li>Solve the problems related to information technology in helpdesk system.</li>\r\n<li>Train clients to use some programs and maintenance.</li>\r\n<li>Send monthly report every month to manager.</li>\r\n<li>Do other tasks assigned by manager.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Need to have Information Technology certificate or other relevant certificates</li>\r\n<li>Have experiences at least one year with technical or relevant job</li>\r\n<li>Able to keep confidence to all recording files and information related to loan</li>\r\n<li>Skills in some program such as Word, Excel, Access, Power point, Outlook, Microsoft window, Data&nbsp; communication and network peer to peer</li>\r\n<li>Have a good communication skill and easy-going person to train to user</li>\r\n<li>Know how to install program, computer repairing Hardware &amp; Software</li>\r\n<li>Flexible to find solution and research new technology</li>\r\n<li>Able to use English in average level</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,7,7,5,11,'English','2019-06-23 10:44:48','2020-06-01 05:23:15'),
	(889,19,'Application Support Officer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Do weekly and monthly data consolidation; perform matching to ensure the data is correct</li>\r\n<li>Prepare user guide and procedure to all system users</li>\r\n<li>Provide system training to new staff</li>\r\n<li>Provide refreshment to existing staff</li>\r\n<li>Provide on-call, remote support and electronic medium as required to support the users</li>\r\n<li>Manage FLEXCUBE system user account</li>\r\n<li>Follow up FLEXCUBE system users activities</li>\r\n<li>Consolidate all the FLEXCUBE system database from sub branches</li>\r\n<li>Performances and products Testing in FLEXCUBE system</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Master/Bachelor degree in Computer science or equivalent</li>\r\n<li>One year of relevant work/management experience in FlexCube core banking system.</li>\r\n<li>Excellent understanding and practice of FLEXCUBE Core Banking System</li>\r\n<li>Fundamental knowledge in Oracle Database and Linux</li>\r\n<li>Experience of writing procedures, manuals and drafting reports</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','06/27/2019',1,7,7,5,11,'English','2019-06-23 10:47:39','2020-06-01 05:48:57'),
	(890,19,'BI Report Developer - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Understand the business requirements and design reports for Business</li>\r\n<li>Participate in business analysis activities to gather requirement.</li>\r\n<li>Provide training and assistance to users for generation of adhoc report.</li>\r\n<li>Provide support as required to ensure the availability and performance of developed report.</li>\r\n<li>Performance tuning experience related to reporting queries.</li>\r\n<li>Develop/enhance report reports based on Jasper Report and Oracle BI.</li>\r\n<li>Translate business requirement into specifications that will be used to implement the reports and dashboards.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Bachelor degree in computer science or equivalent</li>\r\n<li>Strong analytical, conceptual and problem-solving ability</li>\r\n<li>Strong skill in SQL, PL/SQL and knowledge of Relationship Databases (Oracle, PostgreSQL and SQL Server)</li>\r\n<li>Strong Skills in query tuning</li>\r\n<li>Understand key Financial and Banking concepts</li>\r\n<li>Basis understanding with Data Warehouse concepts</li>\r\n<li>Creative, good problem solving and research skills</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','05/26/2020',1,11,7,5,9,'English','2019-06-23 10:51:24','2020-05-29 04:46:32'),
	(891,20,'មន្រ្តីសេវាកម្មឥណទាន (Lending Service Officer) - ០១​ នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>រៀបចំរបាយការណ៍យឺតយ៉ាវប្រចាំថ្ងៃ ប្រចាំសប្តាហ៍ និងប្រចាំខែ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំរបាយការណ៍ប្រចាំខែសម្រាប់អតិថិជនដែលលុបចេញពីបញ្ជី។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំរបាយការណ៍ប្រចាំខែសម្រាប់អតិថិជនស្ថិតក្នុងការតាមដាន និងអតិថិជនសង្ស័យ។</li>\r\n<li>កំណត់គម្លាតរវាងលទ្ធផលធៀបនឹងផែនការនៃការប្រមូលកម្ចីស្ថិតក្នុងហានិភ័យ និងកម្ចីលុបចេញពីតារាងតុល្យការ។</li>\r\n<li>កំណត់ហានិភ័យឥណទាន ព្រមទាំងផ្តល់ដំណោះស្រាយប្រកបដោយប្រសិទ្ធភាព។</li>\r\n<li>តាមដានរាល់ការវិវត្តរបស់អតិថិជន បន្ទាប់ពីបានផ្តល់ជាដំណោះស្រាយ ដើម្បីធ្វើអោយស្ថានភាពឥណទានត្រឡប់មករកភាពល្អប្រសើរវិញ។</li>\r\n<li>បំពេញភារកិច្ចសំខាន់ៗមួយចំនួនទៀតចាត់តាំងដោយថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>បញ្ជប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រផ្នែកគ្រប់គ្រង ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ និងធនាគារ។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍យ៉ាងតិច ១ឆ្នាំ ផ្នែកផ្តល់សេវាកម្ចីឥណទាន។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ផ្នែកដោះស្រាយបំណុលយឺតយ៉ាវត្រូវបានផ្តល់អទិភាពជូន។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះភាសាអង់គ្លេស អាចទំនាក់ទំនងគ្នាបាន។</li>\r\n<li>មានជំនាញក្នុងការប្រើប្រាស់កុំព្យូទ័រ (Microsoft Office: Ms. Word &amp; Excel and PowerPoint)</li>\r\n<li>មានប្រវត្តិ និងអត្តចរិកល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសារ មានសុជីវធម៌ល្អ និងមានការប្តេជ្ញាចិត្តខ្ពស់ចំពោះការងារ។</li>\r\n<li>អាចចុះបំពេញភារកិច្ចនៅតាមបណ្តាការិយាល័យសាខាខេត្ត/ក្រុងរបស់គ្រឹះស្ថានបាន។</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','06/28/2019',1,6,3,5,11,'English','2019-06-23 11:46:22','2020-05-31 15:50:54'),
	(892,20,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ៥០នាក់','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">ការផ្សព្វផ្សាយពីផលិតផលរបស់ស្ថាប័ន កំណត់នូវអតិថិជនសក្កានុពលនៅក្នុងតំបន់គោលដៅ ។</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">កំណត់នូវយុទ្ធសាស្រ្តលក់ និងថែរក្សាអតិថិជន និងស្រាវជ្រាវទីផ្សារ គូរប្រកួតប្រជែង ។</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">សិក្សាព័ត៌មាន វាយតម្លៃកម្ចី និងតាមដាននូវការប្រើប្រាស់កម្ចីរបស់អតិថិជន ។</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">ធ្វើការទំនាក់ទំនងល្អជាមួយអាជ្ញាធរមូលដ្ឋាន ក្នុងការផ្តល់កម្ចីដល់អតិថិជន ។</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">ដោះស្រាយបញ្ហាក្នងករណីមានកម្ចីមិនល្អ ។</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding-top: 1px; padding-bottom: 1px; font-family: Content, sans-serif;\">ធ្វើរបាយការណ៍ជូន​ប្រធាន ប្រចាំសប្តាហ៍ ប្រចាំខែស្តីពីសមិទ្ធិផល និងការងារប្រឈម ។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555555; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">មានកម្រិតសញ្ញាបត្របរិញ្ញាបត្ររង ឬបរិញ្ញាបត្រ ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ គណនេយ្យ សេដ្ខកិច្ច ឬជំនាញដែលពាក់ព័ន្ធ (បេក្ខជនឆ្នាំទី៤ ឬទើបបញ្ចប់ការសិក្សាត្រូវបានលើកទឹកចិត្ត)</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">មានបទពិសោធន៍ក្នុងការផ្តល់កម្ចី&nbsp; ទីផ្សារ ឬការងារពាក់ព័ន្ធ មានគំនិតច្នៃប្រឌិត ចេះដោះស្រាយបញ្ហា មានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការបំពេញការងារ</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">មានគំនិតចូលរួមការងារជាក្រុម មានទំនាក់ទំនងល្អ និងមានភាពបត់បែន</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: circle; font-size: 13px; border-color: #0dc2c9; padding: 0px; font-family: Content, sans-serif; margin: 0px;\">អាចបំពេញការងារនៅទីតាំងឆ្ងាយៗ</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'50','06/28/2019',1,6,3,4,1,'Khmer, English','2019-06-23 11:48:25','2020-05-28 22:13:22'),
	(893,20,'Lending Project Manager - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Preparing and defining the project scope of work, financial plan, resource&rsquo;s requirement, its goals and delivery;</li>\r\n<li>Design the project workflow for each lending projection with stakeholder (s);</li>\r\n<li>Managing the design of the project documents such as MoU, assessment form, loan contract, and other documents to monitoring on project performance;</li>\r\n<li>Coordinating directly and indirectly with project staff and stakeholders to ensure successful completion of the project;</li>\r\n<li>Resolving and tracking critical issues to minimize project risk factors;</li>\r\n<li>Reporting on project progress and communicated relevant information to management;</li>\r\n<li>Communicating intensively with clients, project partners and project stakeholders to establish an effective working relationship;</li>\r\n<li>Being able to negotiate with the project partner (s) and be capable to initiate the new project to suit the current needs of our customers or potential customers;</li>\r\n<li>Followed up with clients to verify satisfaction; and</li>\r\n<li>Other tasks required by Head of Sale and Strategies</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>At least bachelor degree from Business Administration, Banking and Finance or Economics or other equal certificates;</li>\r\n<li>At least 5 years&rsquo; experience in Microfinance and Banking sector;</li>\r\n<li>At least 2 year-work experiences in the project management</li>\r\n<li>Be responsible and committed to complete the given tasks with deadlineGood communication and negotiation skill</li>\r\n<li>Analytical skill, good at data analysis and report writing;</li>\r\n<li>Initiative and critical thinking;</li>\r\n<li>Good in English (writing and speaking)</li>\r\n<li>Sound in computer (MS. Word, Ms. Excel, PowerPoint...)</li>\r\n<li>Be honesty and high commitment; and</li>\r\n<li>Travel to province if needed.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,85,15,17,'1','06/30/2019',1,4,6,5,14,'English','2019-06-23 12:38:26','2020-05-31 12:57:51'),
	(894,20,'Financial Audit Supervisor - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Plan audits by understanding organization objectives, structure, policies, processes, internal controls, and&nbsp; &nbsp;external regulations;identifying risk areas; preparing audit scope and objectives; preparing audit programs;</li>\r\n<li>Assess compliance with financial regulations and controls by executing audit program steps; testing general ledger, account balances, balances sheets, income statements, and related financial statements;&nbsp; examining and analyzing records, reports, operating practices, and documentation;</li>\r\n<li>Conduce on-site financial, compliance, and operational audits of different complexity and scope at Head Quarter and Branch level;</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the internal audit result has sufficient working papers and evidences as reference of audit findings.</li>\r\n<li>Provide on-the-job training and report to new and existing internal auditors to well comply with audit procedures and programs;and</li>\r\n<li>Other tasks assigned by Financial Audit Manager</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>University degree in banking/finance, accounting, business and professional audit certifications is preferred;</li>\r\n<li>Two years plus audit experience in public accounting or internal audit;</li>\r\n<li>Good analytical, interpersonal, time management, and communications skills;</li>\r\n<li>Good communication, hard-working, honesty and integrity;</li>\r\n<li>Must possess highly developed analytical skills and the ability to think creatively about ways to analyze LH MFI&rsquo;s operations;</li>\r\n<li>Have great attention to detail and strong commitment to work in the field;</li>\r\n</ul>',1,77,15,17,'1','06/30/2019',1,6,9,5,2,'English','2019-06-23 12:43:24','2020-05-31 06:52:06'),
	(895,20,'SME Lending Manager - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការសិក្សា តាមដានកម្ចី និងដោះស្រាយបំណុលដែលអតិថិជនសងយឺត។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការទំនាក់ទំនង និងផ្សព្វផ្សាយជាមួយអតិថិជន ទាំងខាងក្នុង និងខាងក្រៅស្ថាប័ន។</li>\r\n<li>ធ្វើរបាយការណ៍សកម្មភាព ផែនការប្រចាំសប្តាហ៍ និងប្រចាំខែជូននាយកដ្ឋានសាម៉ី។</li>\r\n<li>សិក្សាតំបន់ថ្មី និងសិក្សាសក្កានុពលគូប្រគួតប្រជែង។</li>\r\n<li>ធានាលើកការអនុវត្តគោលនយោបាយរបស់ស្ថាប័នអោយបានត្រឹមត្រូវ។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>មានកម្រិតបរិញ្ញាប័ត្រជំនាញ ធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ គ្រប់គ្រងទូទៅ ឬសញ្ញាប័ត្រពាណិជ្ជកម្មមានលក្ខណៈប្រហាក់ប្រហែល។</li>\r\n<li>មានបទពិសោធន៍ក្នុងការផ្តល់ឥណទានយ៉ាងតិច២ឆ្នាំក្នុងវិស័យមីក្រូហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ ឬធនាគារ។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងក្នុងការគ្រប់គ្រង និងដឹកនាំ។</li>\r\n<li>មានជំនាញដោះស្រាយបញ្ហា ការគិតទុកជាមុន និងមានគំនិតផ្តួចផ្តើម។</li>\r\n<li>ទំនាក់ទំនងល្អ រួសរាយរាក់ទាក់ ស្មោះត្រង់ និងមានការទទួលខុសត្រូវខ្ពស់។</li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'1','06/30/2019',1,5,9,5,2,'Khmer, English','2019-06-23 12:50:58','2020-05-31 09:27:47'),
	(896,15,'មន្រ្តីឥណទាន (Credit Officer) - ១៤៨នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការផ្សាព្វផ្សាយ ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីធីត(HKL) ដើម្បីពង្រីកទីផ្សារ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនសក្តានុពល។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំឯកសារឥណទាន ដើម្បីផ្តល់ឥណទានជូនអតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងតាមដានការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>បំពេញការងារផ្សេងៗតាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>ធ្វើការផ្សាព្វផ្សាយ ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីធីត(HKL) ដើម្បីពង្រីកទីផ្សារ និងទាក់ទាញអតិថិជនសក្តានុពល។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំឯកសារឥណទាន ដើម្បីផ្តល់ឥណទានជូនអតិថិជន។&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>ត្រួតពិនិត្យ និងតាមដានការសងត្រឡប់របស់អតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>បំពេញការងារផ្សេងៗតាមការចាត់តាំងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ៖</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>ធានីភ្នំពេញ (៣៤ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តកណ្តាល (១៨ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តព្រៃវែង (០៧ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តស្វាយរៀង (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តកំពង់ចាម (០៨ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តត្បូងឃ្មុំ (១៣ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តប៉ៃលិន (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តពោធិ៍សាត់ (០៧ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តប៉ៃលិន (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តតាកែវ (០៩ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តកំពង់ស្ពឺ (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តកំពត (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តព្រះសីហនុ (០៥ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តមណ្ឌលគីរី (០៣ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តកោះកុង (០៤ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តកំពង់ឆ្នាំង (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តបាត់ដំបង (០៦ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តរតនៈគីរី (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តបន្ទាយមានជ័យ (០៩ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តឧត្តរមានជ័យ (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តស្ទឹងត្រែង (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តសៀមរាប (០៤ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តកំពង់ធំ (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តព្រះវិហារ (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>ខេត្តក្រចេះ (០២ នាក់)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'148','06/30/2019',0,4,3,1,1,'Khmer','2019-06-24 17:07:51','2020-05-28 23:31:12'),
	(897,15,'មន្រ្តីផ្នែកលក់ (Sale Officer) - ១១នាក់','<ul>\r\n<li>ចូលរួមក្នុងយុទ្ធនាការ ផ្សព្វផ្សាយផ្សេងៗទាក់ទងនឹង ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម។</li>\r\n<li>ចុះជួបទំនាក់ទំនងអតិថិជន និងសាធារណជនដោយផ្ទាល់និងពន្យល់អំពី។</li>\r\n<li>ផលិតផល សេវាកម្ម របស់ហត្ថាកសិករ លីមីតធីត។</li>\r\n<li>ដោះស្រាយបាននូវរាល់បញ្ហាដែលនឹងអាចកើតមានឡើង ចំពោះប្រតិបត្តិការ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំ និងគ្រប់គ្រងរាល់ឯកសារព័ត៌មានទំនាក់ទំនង ជាមួយអតិថិជន។</li>\r\n<li>រាយការណ៍ពីបាតុភាព និងផលប៉ះពាល់ដល់ ផលិតផល និងសេវាកម្ម ទាំងឡាយ មកគណៈគ្រប់គ្រង ឱ្យបានទាន់ពេលច្បាស់លាស់ គ្រប់គ្រាន់ និងត្រឹមត្រូវ។</li>\r\n<li>រៀបចំបាយការណ៍តាមការចាត់ចែងរបស់គណៈគ្រប់គ្រង។</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>កំពុងសិក្សាថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ ឬបញ្ចប់ថ្នាក់បរិញ្ញាបត្រ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រង ជំនាញទីផ្សារ ជំនាញគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ចកម្ម ជំនាញធនាគារ និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ, ឫសញ្ញាបត្រដែលមានតំលៃស្មើ។</li>\r\n<li>មានឆន្ទៈចុះបំពេញការងារនៅតាមមូលដ្ឋាន និងនៅក្នុងដែនគ្រប់គ្រងរបស់សាខា។</li>\r\n<li>មានអត្ដចរិតល្អ មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់ ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់ សុភាពរាបសា និងមានអ៊ំណត់ក្នុង ការធ្វើការងារ។</li>\r\n<li>មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ Ms. Office។</li>\r\n<li>ត្រូវមានម៉ូតូផ្ទាល់ខ្លួន។</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>ទីតាំងបម្រើការងារ៖</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកមោងឬស្សី-ឃុំគារ(០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាស្រុកពញាក្រែក-ឃុំកោងកាង (០១ នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌឫស្សីកែវ-សង្កាត់ច្រាំងចំរ៉េះទី១ (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌដូនពេញ-សង្កាត់ផ្សារកណ្តាលទី១ (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌច្បារអំពៅ - សង្កាត់ច្បារអំពៅទី២ (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាក្រុងបាត់ដំបង-សង្កាត់ព្រែកព្រះស្តេច (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខេត្តព្រះសីហនុ (០១នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខេត្តសៀមរាប (០១នាក់)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខេត្តត្បូងឃ្មុំ (០១នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌដូនពេញ-សង្កាត់ស្រះចក (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n<li>សាខាខណ្ឌចំការមន-សង្កាត់បឹងកេងកងទី២ (០១ នាក់)</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'11','06/30/2019',0,3,3,5,1,'Khmer','2019-06-24 17:18:12','2020-05-31 14:05:13'),
	(898,15,'Deputy Director, Business Development - 01 post','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Develop and manage business development and partnership strategy to support company long term growth aspirations primarily cover across areas of loan, liability products, and fee-based income;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Develop new partnership of both target domestic and overseas companies, and manage ongoing relationship;</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Liaise with parent Group Company to build synergy and enable best practice s