	(904,34,'SME Lending Manager - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>To market SME banking products. To promote SME products in line with management&rsquo;s direction.</li>\r\n<li>To support branch and coach BMs, HBSs &amp; COs towards bank&rsquo;s requirement and attain higher productivity.</li>\r\n<li>To initiate and drive marketing &amp; sales strategy to support SME Business Growth.</li>\r\n<li>To be the key contact of external/internal stakeholder for SME Business</li>\r\n<li>Marketing of SME Loan in achieving the targets for CPBank Plc.</li>\r\n<li>Achieve set goals and financial targets for loan &amp; advances.</li>\r\n<li>Manage asset quality by maintain low NPL ratio below industry.</li>\r\n<li>Submission of Marketing Calls per required.</li>\r\n<li>Providing advice to branches on viability of cases prior to processing.</li>\r\n<li>Submit Credit Proposal for Corporate Project</li>\r\n<li>Key driver/coordinator for internal stakeholder and external stakeholder on corporation program</li>\r\n<li>Monitoring of product performances</li>\r\n<li>Submission of reports. And assist branches on matter relating to SME Products.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the department&rsquo;s housekeeping, audit ratings are satisfactory through implementation of proper system/controls and Bank&rsquo;s requirement are complied with.</li>\r\n<li>Other duties will be assigned by Manager or Management.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>At least 2 years of experience in sale management and 3 years in management level relating to MFI/Bank performance Management.</li>\r\n<li>Excellence in English communication (both verbal and writing)</li>\r\n<li>Strong leadership and people management skill with the ability to drive performance of the team.</li>\r\n<li>Superior communication and interpersonal skills with the ability to influence outcomes.</li>\r\n<li>Proven ability to establish credibility and maintain and develop good business relationships with business associations and customers.</li>\r\n<li>Knowledge of credit policies, procedures and practices. Experiences in a retail SME banking or related field</li>\r\n<li>Proven and strong strategic planning skill and business development experience</li>\r\n<li>Proven strong communication skill especially customer and business relationship management.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'1','07/20/2019',1,7,6,5,14,'English','2019-06-30 10:00:28','2020-05-31 08:48:57'),
	(905,34,'Branch Manager - 02 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Run your business to deliver outstanding results across all key dimensions &ndash; Funds Under Management (FUM) growth, revenue growth, productivity, branch profit.</li>\r\n<li>Understand the economics of the branch and what can do to improve the branch&rsquo;s profit.</li>\r\n<li>Keep a close eye on your local competitors &ndash; what they do and how they perform. Plan to gain market share.</li>\r\n<li>Proactively identify and address areas of customer dissatisfaction, following up and resolving any customer complaints within your discretion or refer appropriately. Welcome customer complaints as an opportunity to learn, and take personal responsibility for their resolution.</li>\r\n<li>Ensure the governance of branch operations in line with bank&rsquo;s governance standards.</li>\r\n<li>Take ownership of your team&rsquo;s performance and development and ensure that their behavior reflects the values and policies of the Bank.</li>\r\n<li>Embrace, drive and support changes to improve performance and provide better services/products to customers.</li>\r\n<li>Identify potential process/service enhancements, escalate as appropriate and document suggestions.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Broad understanding how bank operates and customer service manager work flow.</li>\r\n<li>Branch management experience.</li>\r\n<li>Sales skills and understanding of sales culture, preferably acquired in the financial services sector</li>\r\n<li>Working knowledge of administrative functions in an operational environment e.g. budgets, personnel administration.</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrated experience in managing and motivating a team.</li>\r\n<li>Strong relationship building.</li>\r\n<li>Excellence in English communication (both verbal and writing) and Chines is advance.</li>\r\n<li>Qualifications in a financial discipline.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,17,'2','07/20/2019',1,5,9,5,9,'English','2019-06-30 10:02:12','2020-05-29 06:05:21'),
	(906,34,'Internal Auditor - 01 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>Assist Senior Internal Audit in preparing the internal audit reports,</li>\r\n<li>Performs financial, operational, credit, IT, departments audit and other audits in order to provide assurance to risk department,</li>\r\n<li>Update audit check lists,</li>\r\n<li>Analyze the weakness of operation and management processes, and provide the evident supports for recommendations in reports,</li>\r\n<li>Develop audit programs and testing procedure relevant to risk and test the objectives,</li>\r\n<li>Obtain and review evidences ensuring audit conclusion are well-documented,</li>\r\n<li>Documents the findings/issues, drafts the recommendations using unbiased opinion to submit to Senior Internal Audit for reviewing,</li>\r\n<li>Builds and maintain respectful and effective communication and relationship with teams, managements and staffs of areas under review,</li>\r\n<li>Maintains confidentiality of bank and customer affairs in accordance with standards of professional conduct of auditors,</li>\r\n<li>Performs related works as assigned by Senior Internal Audit.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>At least Bachelor&rsquo;s degree in auditing or related fields,</li>\r\n<li>Good English proficiency, both written and spoken,</li>\r\n<li>One year&rsquo;s experience in related field,</li>\r\n<li>Computer literacy (MS, Office, Ms, Excel, Power Point, e-mail etc.),</li>\r\n<li>Plans and organizes workload properly with infrequent exception</li>\r\n<li>Makes good decision; timing and presentation of the decisions are acceptable</li>\r\n<li>Work consistently accurate, complete, and precise; rarely makes errors and/or omissions</li>\r\n<li>Responds to criticism in a constructive fashion; exhibits more initiatives than most in taking steps to correct problem areas as identified</li>\r\n<li>Building relationships &amp; networks</li>\r\n<li>Willing to travel to support business operations at provinces.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,77,15,17,'1','07/30/2019',1,6,3,5,11,'English','2019-06-30 10:03:23','2020-05-28 10:48:09'),
	(907,34,'MIS Report - 01 post','<ul>\r\n<li>Prepare all daily portfolio report</li>\r\n<li>Prepare all monthly portfolio reports (performance report, average DPD, collections efficiency, late/paid off penalties, report by due days, SMS sending and so on.)</li>\r\n<li>Prepare loan portfolio of credit officer for HR on credit officer salary appraisal</li>\r\n<li>Prepare NBC report</li>\r\n<li>Other requirements from Risk Analytics Manager</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>A university degree in Finance and Banking and related field</li>\r\n<li>Minimum of 1 year of experiences in Financial Institution</li>\r\n<li>Excellence in Ms. Excel spread sheet and SQL language.</li>\r\n<li>Broad understanding how bank operates</li>\r\n<li>English communication (both verbal and writing) is preferred.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'1','07/30/2019',1,5,3,5,11,'English','2019-06-30 10:04:48','2020-05-29 19:49:36'),
	(908,34,'Credit Officer - 100 posts','<ul>\r\n<li>To promote and sell the company&rsquo;s products and services.</li>\r\n<li>To process all new applications within the stipulated turnaround time.</li>\r\n<li>To build a good relationship with all levels of local authorities to get their support on loan documents processing.</li>\r\n<li>To fill in all new loan/existing loan applications with clients, and following up clients&rsquo; repayment on time.</li>\r\n<li>To manage and maintaining clients&rsquo; relationship with clients, to gain more loyalty from clients through high quality services.</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Minimum third year or graduated in Banking &amp; Finance, Management, Marketing or related fields.</li>\r\n<li>Good experience in sales (Experience in Credit/ Saving is preferable)</li>\r\n<li>Commit to the core value of the company.</li>\r\n<li>Good analytical, attention to details, communication, time management, and interpersonal skills.</li>\r\n<li>Abilities to decision-making and problem-solving</li>\r\n<li>Proficiency in English both speaking and writing.</li>\r\n<li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office.</li>\r\n</ul>',1,71,15,28,'100','07/30/2019',1,7,3,5,1,'English','2019-06-30 10:05:52','2020-06-01 11:14:42'),
	(909,15,'IT Security Operations Officer - 02 posts','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Conduct site visit of borrower&rsquo;s resident, business premise and/or working place to collect information to verify and support loan proposal.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Assess and Analyze financial statements and credit worthiness of borrowers.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Identify borrowers&rsquo; business risks and propose corresponding mitigations.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Propose credit decisions and negotiate with PC officer accordingly.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Liaise with Management Credit Committee in presenting loan proposal and responding to query/suggestion from the committee.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">File reports of turnaround time of loan process at Head Office.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Other tasks assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\