so-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">High commitment with strong work ethics and integrity.</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,59,15,17,'2','07/25/2019',0,6,3,5,2,'English','2019-07-13 10:18:02','2020-05-30 07:57:22'),
	(910,15,'Corporate Compliance Officer - 02 posts','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Collect and review of AML document in accordance to current KYC procedure.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Create and build a KYC due diligence profile for each client assign.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Understand of enhance due diligence trigger.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Maintain blacklist and sanction list.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Follow up of AML critical issues and escalate accordingly.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Ensure due diligence KYC process is consistent globally but adopted local rules.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Contribute to implementation and controls for daily process and assist with the update procedure.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Liaise regularly with numerous stakeholder including but not limit to front office, back office, IT, and business officer.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Perform other task assigne by management.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Bachelor degree in business administration or related studies.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">At least one year experience with banking and FI operation.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Understanding principle of banking and FI products.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Knowledge of due diligence and local money laundering requirement.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Understand principle of banking and FIs operation </span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Excellent verbal, presentation and written communication.</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Computer literacy required (Excel, Words, PowerPoint).</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,78,15,17,'2','07/20/2019',0,6,3,5,11,'English','2019-07-13 10:19:23','2020-05-31 13:37:38'),
	(911,15,'មន្រ្តីវិភាគឥណទាន (Credit Analysis Officer) - ០២នាក់','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ពិនិត្យមើល</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​</span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ភាពត្រឹមត្រូវ</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​​​​​​ </span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">គ្រប់គ្រាន់</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">និង</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​</span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ការអនុលោមទៅតាមគោលការណ៏ឥណទាន​</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">និង ជួយសម្រួលក្នុងការបញ្ជូនឯកសារឥណទានទៅកាន់ថ្នាក់គ្រប់គ្រង</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ដើម្បីធ្វើការអនុម័តហើយបញ្ជូនត្រលប់ទៅកាន់សាខាវិញ។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ធ្វើការវិភាគលើសមត្ថភាពក្នុងការទទួលបានឥណទានរបស់អតិថិជន</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ដោយពិនិត្យឡើងវិញ</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">លើផែនការអាជីវកម្ម</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">លំហូរសាច់ប្រាក់</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">របាយការណ៍ហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​</span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\"> តារាងតុល្យការ</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">និង​លទ្ធភាពក្នុងការសងបំណុល។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">រៀបចំទម្រង់វាយតម្លៃហានិភ័យឥណទានដើម្បីសង្ខេបព័ត៌មានឥណទាន</span><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​</span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ដាក់ស្នើទៅនាយកដ្ឋានឥណទាន</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​​</span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">សម្រាប់ធ្វើការអនុម័ត។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ធ្វើការទំនាក់ទំនងទៅកាន់សាខាវិញសម្រាប់ ការឆ្លើយតបណាមួយរបស់​គណៈ</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​</span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">កម្មា</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​</span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ធិកាឥណទានដើម្បីធ្វើឱ្យមានភាពច្បាស់លាស់ទៅលើពត៌មាន និង​ លក្ខខណ្ឌនានា។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ធ្វើរបាយការណ៍ជាប្រចាំ ពីសំណើរឥណទានដែលទទួលការអនុម័តរឺមិនទាន់បានអនុម័ត</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">និង</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​​​​ </span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">រាយការណ៍ទៅកាន់ប្រធានផ្នែកវិភាគឥណទាន</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​ </span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">និងរៀបចំឯកសារតាមលំដាប់លំដោយ ឲ្យបានត្រឹមត្រូវ។</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ពិនិត្យឡើងវិញនៃគោលការណ៍ឥណទាន</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">នីតិវិធី</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">និងវិសោធនកម្មដែលពាក់ព័ន្ធទៅ</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">និងការទទួលខុសត្រូវប្រចាំថ្ងៃរបស់ខ្លួនដើម្បីធ្វើឱ្យប្រាកដថាគោលការណ៏និង ស្របទៅតាមបច្ចុប្បន្នភាព។</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ជានិសិ្សតកំពុងសិក្សា ឬ បញ្ចប់​​ថ្នាក់​បរិញ្ញាបត្រ</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ផ្នែកគ្រប់គ្រងពាណិជ្ជកម្ម</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ធនាគារ</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">និងហិរញ្ញវត្ថុ</span><span dir=\"RTL\" lang=\"AR-SA\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">​​</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">ឬសញ្ញាប័ត្រដែលមានតម្លៃស្មើ។</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">មានបទពិសោធន៍យ៉ាងតិច មួយឆ្នាំ ក្នុងការផ្តល់ឥណទាន និងវិភាគឥណទាន។</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">មានចំណេះដឹងភាសាអង់គ្លេស និងកុំព្យូទ័រ </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\';\">Ms. Office (Ms. Word &amp; Excel) Internet &amp; Email</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Battambang\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">មានការទំនាក់ទំនងល្អក្នុងការធ្វើការជាក្រុម និងមានជំនាញក្នុងការវិភាគ។</span></li>\r\n<li><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">មានអត្តចរិកល្អ </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\';\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">មានភាពស្មោះត្រង់<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span>ម៉ឺងម៉ាត់</span> <span lang=\"KHM\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: \'Khmer OS Content\'; mso-bidi-language: KHM;\">សុភាពរាបសារ និង មានឆន្ទៈក្នុងការធ្វើការងារ។</span></li>\r\n</ul>',1,41,15,17,'2','07/20/2019',0,6,3,5,11,'English','2019-07-13 10:21:03','2020-05-30 14:00:16'),
	(912,15,'Credit Analyst Officer for Unsecured Loan product​ - 02 posts','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul type=\"disc\">\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Conduct site visit of borrower&rsquo;s resident, business premise and/or working place to collect information to verify and support loan proposal.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Assess and Analyze financial statements and credit worthiness of borrowers.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Identify borrowers&rsquo; business risks and propose corresponding mitigations.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Propose credit decisions and negotiate with PC officer accordingly.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Liaise with Management Credit Committee in presenting loan proposal and responding to query/suggestion from the committee.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">File reports of turnaround time of loan process at Head Office.</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; text-align: justify; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-element: frame; mso-element-frame-hspace: 9.0pt; mso-element-wrap: around; mso-element-anchor-vertical: paragraph; mso-element-anchor-horizontal: column; mso-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"CA\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-ansi-language: CA;\">Other tasks assigned by supervisor.</span></li>\r\n</ul>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\