INSERT INTO `term_conditions` (`id`, `title`, `body`, `created_at`, `updated_at`)
VALUES
	(1,'Privacy Statements','<p>PaysJob dot com respects the privacy of the personal information and data of its users and will ensure compliance by its staff to the strictest standards of security and confidentiality in respect of all personal information and data submitted by users via the Site and PaysJob dot com will not, subject to the terms herein, release such information to anyone without the prior consent of the relevant user(s) of the Site (whether registered or not) (&ldquo;User(s)&rdquo;).</p>\r\n<p>Users are strongly recommended to read this privacy statement (&ldquo;Privacy Statement&rdquo;) carefully to have an understanding of PaysJob dot com&rsquo;s policy and practices with regard to the treatment of personal information and data provided by Users on the Site. This Privacy Statement is applicable to both registered and unregistered Users, and the terms herein may be updated, revised, varied and/or amended from time to time as PaysJob dot com may deem necessary and/or appropriate.</p>\r\n<p>By registering for or using the services/Site, or by clicking the &lsquo;Sign up&rsquo; button, User:</p>\r\n<p>(a) consent to PaysJob dot com collecting, using, disclosing and/or processing User&rsquo;s personal data for the purposes as described below;</p>\r\n<p>(b) consent to PaysJob dot com disclosing Users&rsquo; personal data to PaysJob dot com&rsquo;s third party service providers or agents (whether within or outside Cambodia) for the purposes as described below.</p>\r\n<p>If Users have questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Statement, they should contact the Customer Support Executive of PaysJob dot com, whose contact details are set out under the section headed &ldquo;Enquiries&rdquo; below.</p>\r\n<p>In this Privacy Statement, the following terms shall have the respective meanings specified below unless the context otherwise requires:</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Advertiser(s)&rdquo; means user who places a job advertisement or promotes any job related activities via the Site.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Pays Job dot com&rdquo; means PaysJob recruitment Site.</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Job Seeker(s)&rdquo; means users seeking employment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Sign up User(s)&rdquo; means Users who sign up on the Site to obtain services offered by PaysJob dot com.</p>\r\n<p>Unless the context provides otherwise, references in this Privacy Statement to &ldquo;users&rdquo; or &ldquo;you&rdquo; include references to generic users and Registered Users.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&ldquo;Site&rdquo; means any website, job portal or mobile application owned and operated by PaysJob dot com or its service providers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Purpose of Collection and Use of Personal Data&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>In the course of using the Site, Users may disclose or be asked to provide personal information and/or data. In order to have the benefit of and enjoy various services offered by the Site, it may be necessary for Users to provide PaysJob dot com with their personal information and/or data. Although Users are not obliged to provide the information and/or data as requested on the Site, PaysJob dot com will not be able to render certain services on the Site in the event that Users fail to do so.</p>\r\n<p>PaysJob dot com&rsquo;s purposes for collecting and using the information and data on the Site include but are not limited to the following:</p>\r\n<p>(a) for the daily operation of the services provided to Users;</p>\r\n<p>(b) to assist Job Seekers to find appropriate employment with Employers and to assist Employers to assess the suitability of candidates for job vacancy for a wide spectrum of jobs and industries including using artificial intelligence (&ldquo;AI)&rdquo; and data analytics in relation to personal information in order to improve PaysJob dot com&rsquo;s ability to find appropriate employment for Job Seekers;</p>\r\n<p>(c) to provide Users with various services offered by the Site and newsletters, job openings and promotional and marketing materials (for further details, please refer to section headed &ldquo;Subscription of Newsletter/Promotional Materials/Marketing Materials&rdquo; below);</p>\r\n<p>(d) to handle and follow up on enquiries, requests and complaints from Users;</p>\r\n<p>(e) to contact Users regarding administrative notices and communications relevant to his/her use of the Site and to respond to Users&rsquo; inquiries or requests;</p>\r\n<p>(f) to assist PaysJob dot com with developments for future marketing and promoting purposes or other internal purposes;</p>\r\n<p>(g) to verify the identity of Users who have posted advertisements, materials, representations, messages, views or comments or such other information (collectively &ldquo;Information&rdquo;) on the Site;</p>\r\n<p>(h) to identify Users who have viewed the Information posted on the Site;</p>\r\n<p>(i) to allow Users to enjoy their benefits as members of the Site by enrolling for special events and promotions hosted by PaysJob dot com and or partner company;</p>\r\n<p>(j) to identify Users who have enjoyed their benefits as members of the Site by receiving and using marketing promotional materials;</p>\r\n<p>(k) to facilitate PaysJob dot com to use the Users&rsquo; personal data for the purposes relating to the provision of services offered by PaysJob dot com and marketing services and/or special event of PaysJob dot com;</p>\r\n<p>(l) to obtain statistics about Users to analyze usage of the Site in order to help its further development for internal use; and</p>\r\n<p>(m) for purposes other than the above mentioned which are related to PaysJob dot com&rsquo;s provision of their product and/or services as PaysJob dot com may deem fit.</p>\r\n<p>If a User is under the age of 18, PaysJob dot com would strongly recommend him/her to seek prior consent from a person with parental responsibility for him/her, e.g. parent or guardian, who may contact the responsible Customer Support Executive whose contact details are set out under the section headed &ldquo;Enquiries&rdquo; for registering the User as member of the Site.</p>\r\n<p>PaysJob dot com strives to only collect personal data which are necessary and adequate but not excessive in relation to the purposes set out hereinabove.</p>\r\n<p>If PaysJob dot com requires the use of your personal data for a purpose other than those set out hereinabove, we will request your prescribed consent to the same. If you are a minor, the prescribed consent should be given by your parent or guardian.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Advertisers</strong></p>\r\n<p>PaysJob dot com collects the company name, business address and billing address of Advertisers. It also collects the name, email address and phone number of a primary contact (also referred to on the Site as the &lsquo;administrator&rsquo;). Advertisers can change the company name, billing address, or any other details by contacting the designated Account Manager. We use these details to manage your account, including sending Advertisers applications of Candidates, contacting Advertisers if there is an issue with their job ad and organizing payment and invoicing of the account.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Collection of Personal Data&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>PaysJob dot com may collect personal information and/or data about a User such as his/her name, login ID and password, address, email address, phone number, age, gender, date of birth, country of residence, nationality, education level and work experience that is/are not otherwise publicly available. Occasionally, PaysJob dot com may also collect additional personal information and/or data from a User in connection with contests, surveys, or special offers.</p>\r\n<p>Only duly authorized staff of PaysJob dot com will be permitted to access Users&rsquo; personal information and data, and PaysJob dot com shall not release such personal information and data to any third parties save and except for the circumstances listed out under the section entitled &ldquo;Disclosure or Transfer of Data&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Disclosure or Transfer of Data</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>PaysJob dot com agrees to take all practicable steps to keep all personal information and data of Users confidential and/or undisclosed, subject to the following.</p>\r\n<p>Generally speaking, PaysJob dot com will only disclose and/or transfer Users&rsquo; personal information and/or data to PaysJob dot com&rsquo;s personnel and staff for the purpose of providing services to Users and corporate clients of PaysJob dot com who have made specific requests for such information and/or data with Users&rsquo; prior consent. However, PaysJob dot com may disclose and/or transfer such information and/or data to third parties under the following circumstances:</p>\r\n<p>(a) where the information and/or data is disclosed and/or transferred to any third party suppliers or external service providers who have been duly authorized by PaysJob dot com to use such information and/or data and who will facilitate the services on the Site, under a duty of confidentiality including but not limited to data analytics service providers, data storage and cloud service providers;</p>\r\n<p>(b) where the information and/or data is disclosed and/or transferred to any agents, affiliates or associates of PaysJob dot com who have been duly authorized by PaysJob dot com to use such information and/or data;</p>\r\n<p>(c) where permitted under the &ldquo;Terms and Conditions&rdquo; including the &ldquo;Talent Search Terms and Conditions&rdquo; (see the Profiles Section below);</p>\r\n<p>(d) where PaysJob dot com needs to protect and defend its rights and property;</p>\r\n<p>(e) where PaysJob dot com considers necessary to do so in order to comply with the applicable laws and regulations, including without limitation compliance with a judicial proceeding, court order, or legal process served on the Site;</p>\r\n<p>(f) where PaysJob dot com deems necessary in order to deliver the products and services that we offer and cultivate a positive user experience; and</p>\r\n<p>(g) where PaysJob dot com deems necessary in order to maintain and improve the services on the Site.</p>\r\n<p>Personal data collected via the Site may be transferred, stored and processed in any country in which PaysJob dot com or any member of the PaysJob Group operates. By using the Site, Users are deemed to have agreed to, consented to and authorized PaysJob dot com to disclose and/or transfer their personal information and data under the circumstances stated above, as well as to any transfer of information (including the Information) outside of the Users&rsquo; country.</p>\r\n<p><strong>PaysJob Profile</strong></p>\r\n<p>PaysJob dot com provides all Users with the option of creating a personal PaysJob Profiles (&ldquo;Profile&rdquo;). These Profiles can be used for the purpose of creating advertisements to be posted by an Advertiser or for the purpose of an Applicant applying for products, services or employment opportunities offered by an Advertiser. A Profile can include personal information, such as a cv and contact details.</p>\r\n<p>Where you have replied to an advertisement posted by an Advertiser using its Profile or you have applied for products, services or employment opportunities directly on the Site using your Profile, that Advertiser will have access to your data including your contact details.</p>\r\n<p>Where you create a Profile on the Site you consent to your data being viewed and/or accessed by Applicants and Advertisers which may result in the transfer of your personal data by the Applicant and Advertiser to other members of their respective groups. The use of your information (personal or otherwise) by these Applicants and Advertisers is not within the control of PaysJob and we cannot accept responsibility for the conduct of these persons and companies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Storing your resume</strong></p>\r\n<p>Registered Users may elect to store up to 10 resumes in their PaysJob account, and use those resumes when applying for a job.</p>\r\n<p>In order to provide advertiser with the most relevant information about you (and depending on your PaysJob Profile privacy setting), the primary resume attached to your PaysJob Profile will also be scanned by PaysJob dot com and relevant content may be displayed to advertisers in the PaysJob advertiser database. If you do not want content from your resume to be displayed to advertisers do not attach a resume or do not select &ldquo;Standard&rdquo; privacy. For more information on how your resume will be used, see above under the heading &ldquo;PaysJob Profile&rdquo;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Links to Other Websites&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Site may provide links to other websites which are not owned or controlled by PaysJob dot com. Personal information and data from Users may be collected on these other websites when Users visit such websites and make use of the services provided therein. Where and when Users decide to click on any advertisement or hyperlink on the Site which grants Users access to another website, the protection of Users&rsquo; personal information and data which are deemed to be private and confidential may be exposed in these other websites.</p>\r\n<p>Non-registered Users who gain access to the Site via their accounts in online social networking tools (including but not limited to Facebook, Twitter and LinkedIn) are deemed to have consented to the terms of this Privacy Statement, and such Users&rsquo; personal data which they have provided to those networking tools may be obtained by PaysJob dot com and be used by PaysJob dot com and its authorized persons in and outside of the User&rsquo;s country for the purpose of providing services and marketing materials to the Users. PaysJob and its authorized personnel may gain access and use the personal data of such Users so obtained, subject to the other provisions of this Privacy Statement.</p>\r\n<p>This Privacy Statement is only applicable to the Site. Users are reminded that this Privacy Statement grants no protection to Users&rsquo; personal information and data that may be exposed on websites other than the Site, and PaysJob dot com is not responsible for the privacy practices of such other websites. Users are strongly recommended to refer to the privacy policies of such other websites before using those websites.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Security</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The security of Users&rsquo; personal information and data is important to PaysJob dot com. PaysJob dot com will always strive to ensure that Users&rsquo; personal information and data will be protected against unauthorized access. PaysJob dot com has implemented appropriate electronic and managerial measures in order to safeguard, protect and secure Users&rsquo; personal information and data.</p>\r\n<p>All personal information and data provided by Users are only accessible by the authorized personnel of PaysJob dot com or its authorized third parties, and such personnel shall be instructed to observe the terms of this Privacy Statement when accessing such personal information and data. Users may rest assured that their personal information and data will only be kept for as long as is necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it is collected. Registered User should safeguard his/her unique Username and Password by keeping it secret and confidential and never share these details with anyone.</p>\r\n<p>PaysJob dot com uses a third party service provider to facilitate the electronic payment transactions on the Site.</p>\r\n<p>PaysJob dot com follows generally accepted industry standards to protect the personal information and data submitted by Users to the Site, both during transmission and once PaysJob dot com receives it. However, no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. Therefore, while PaysJob dot com strives to protect Users&rsquo; personal information and data against unauthorized access, PaysJob dot com cannot guarantee its absolute security.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Retention of Personal Data</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Once PaysJob dot com has obtained a User&rsquo;s personal information and/or data, it will be maintained securely in PaysJob dot com&rsquo;s system for the period necessary to fulfill the purposes for which the data was collected as set out under the section headed &ldquo;Purpose of Collection of Personal Data&rdquo;. Once registered, Users may terminate his/her membership of the Site by contacting the Customer Service Executive of PaysJob, whose contact details are set out under the section headed &ldquo;Enquiries&rdquo;. PaysJob dot com may retain User&rsquo;s personal information even after User has closed his/her account if retention is reasonably necessary to comply with our legal obligations, meet regulatory requirements, resolve disputes between Users, prevent fraud and abuse, or enforce this Privacy Statement and the Terms and Conditions.</p>\r\n<p>Enquiries</p>\r\n<p>Should you have any enquiries relating to this Privacy Statement, please email at job@paysjob.com or paysjob@gmail.com, telephone at (+885) 70 900 928 or (+855) 97 807 73 73.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2020-05-25 15:21:52','2020-05-27 17:07:31'),
